Umubare w'ubwandu bushya bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu by'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi na UK kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020
Umubare w'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza, ugaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyateye imbere mu bihugu byose, nubwo byatandukaniye bitewe n'ibihugu.
Dukurikije ibyabaye mu Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bwa none bigomba kurushaho kwitegura kwakira ubwiyongere bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho mu buvuzi, cyane cyane mu by'indembe.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, itsinda ry'abarwayi b'indwara z'ibicurane zitamenyekana ryamenyekanye i Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura no gukumira indwara mu Bushinwa cyatangaje ko icyorezo cya Koronavirusi, ubu cyiswe icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 (Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome Coronavirus 2).
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara iterwa n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 yitwa indwara iterwa na koronavirusi (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, 80% by'abanduye COVID-19 barwaye byoroheje, ni ukuvuga ko barwaye indwara z'ubuhumekero zirimo umusonga cyangwa ntawo, kandi abenshi muri bo barakira.
Mu bantu 14%, COVID-19 ihinduka indwara ikomeye cyane igomba kujyanwa mu bitaro, mu gihe abandi 6% bagaragaza ko barwaye cyane bigasaba kwitabwaho mu buryo bwihariye.
Imibare yo gupfa ku barwayi ba COVID-19 bari mu bitaro igera kuri 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, turareba uko ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwifashe muri buri gihugu cyo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi (EU/EEA) no mu Bwongereza (UK) tukagereranya n'uko byifashe mu Ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Turagereranya umubare w'abamaze kwandura COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza n'uw'abo mu Butaliyani kuva ku wa 31 Mutarama kugeza ku wa 15 Werurwe 2020.
Abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu by'Ubumwe bw'Ibihugu by'I Burayi (EU/EEA) no mu Bwongereza
Nyuma y'Ubushinwa, COVID-19 yakomeje gukwirakwira mu turere dutandukanye, ndetse ubu ni cyo gihugu cy'isi cyibasiwe cyane n'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Abemejwe bwa mbere ko muri Burayi habonetse umuntu wa COVID-19 nk'uko byasobanuwe na OMS mu nyandiko yo ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020 ya Eurosurveillance, Spiteri et al.
Muri EU/EEA, u Bufaransa bwatangaje ko ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020 bwagize abarwayi batatu ba mbere bemejwe mu bantu bari bagarutse bavuye mu Bushinwa mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei.
Kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, ibihugu byose 30 bigize EU/EEA hamwe n'Ubwongereza (UK) byagize abantu banduye COVID-19, aho hagati y'itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 n'iyo tariki, havugwa abantu 39,768 banduye COVID-19 n'abapfuye 1,727 mu Butaliyani gusa, hakaba hari abantu 17,750 banduye na 1,441 bahitanywe na yo.
Kubara umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 no kubara umubare w'abantu banduye
Mu kigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC), imibare y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bayibarizwa mu bihugu byose ku isi igenda iheruka guhera saa munani za mu gitondo, ivuye ku masoko yemewe nk'uko bitangazwa na Minisiteri y'ubuzima y'ibihugu, inzego z'ubuzima z'ibihugu n'iz'uturere ndetse na OMS.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gusuzuma icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, no kugereranya n'icyorezo cyabaye mu Butaliyani.
Nk'uko tugiye kubona mu buryo bw'imiterere y'uko COVID-19 ikwirakwira, twabakusanyirije iminsi 14 y'ubwandu bushya bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza mu gihe cy'ukwezi kwa mbere kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Twerekanye kandi umubare w'abamaze kwandura muri buri gihugu kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani z'amanywa, ugereranyije n'abamaze kwandura mu Butaliyani mu gihe cy'ukwezi kwa mbere kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Uko COVID-19 igenda yiyongera mu bihugu byo mu muryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Igereranya ry'iminsi 14 y'ubwiyongere bw'ubwandu bw'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bihugu byo muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, rikurikiza mu buryo busanzwe icyorezo cy'intara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Igishushanyo 1).
Muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza hose, ubwiyongere bw'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwatangiye kwiyongera ahagana ku ya 21 Gashyantare, buzamuka cyane ahagana ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (Ibisobanuro by'inyongera).
Ibi byatewe ahanini n'ubwiyongere bukabije bw'umubare w'abatangajweho amakuru mu Butaliyani, ariko ibindi bihugu byose bigize EU/EEA ndetse n'u Bwongereza na byo byabonye ko ubwiyongere bwa COVID-19 bwiyongereye (Amafoto)
Igishushanyo cya 2 cyerekana umubare w'abarwaye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki 31 Mutarama - 15 Werurwe 2020.
Ibi byerekana ko ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani, ibindi bihugu 15 by'ibihugu bigize EU/EEA na UK byari byamaze gutangaza umubare w'abamaze kwandura ugereranyije n'abo mu Butaliyani mu byumweru 3 gusa mbere cyangwa nyuma.
Ibisubizo byacu byerekana ko umubare w'abantu bandura COVID-19 wiyongera cyane mu bihugu by'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Imiterere igaragara mu kwiyongera kwa COVID-19 igaragaza ko icyorezo cyugarije isi cyateye imbere mu bihugu byose mu buryo buhuriye.
Ibi ni ko biri nubwo ibihugu biri mu byiciro bitandukanye, mu buryo butandukanye bwo gusubiza ibibazo mu rwego rw'ubuzima rusange, ndetse n'uko ibihugu bishobora kuba bifite ibisobanuro bitandukanye by'uko indwara iteye n'uburyo bwo guhitamo abarwayi bagomba gupimwa kugira ngo hamenyekane ko bafite COVID-19, harimo no kubaga.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu turere twibasiwe n'iki cyorezo mu Butaliyani bavuze ko 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane, kandi itangazamakuru ryatanze amakuru ko ibitaro n'ibyumba by'abaganga bita ku barwaye cyane muri utwo turere byari byamaze kugera ku bubasha bwabyo.
Imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 bajyanywe mu bitaro cyangwa mu cyumba cy'indembe, ubu iboneka ku rwego rw'ibihugu by'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi na EAC ku bantu 6% na 1% by'abanduye gusa (imibare ntiriho).
Ariko kandi, zigomba gukusanywa buhoro buhoro kugira ngo zihuze n'imibare y'ubugenzuzi, yibanda ku mubare w'abarwayi n'abapfa.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2010 - 2011 bwagaragaje ko ku mugabane w'u Burayi, ibitanda byo mu bitaro by'indembe n'ibyo mu bitaro by'indembe byihariye, byari ku kigero cy'ibitanda 29.2 ku baturage 100.000 mu Budage, naho mu Butaliyani byari 4.2.
Ibyo bisobanura ko ibihugu bishobora kuba bifite amikoro menshi cyangwa make ugereranyije n'ay'u Butaliyani (12.5 ku bantu 100.000 mu mwaka wa 2010-2011, mu bitaro by'indembe n'iby'ubuvuzi).
Imyiteguro y'ibipimo by'ubuvuzi by'ibitaro by'abarwayi bari mu bitaro bifite ubushobozi bwo kuryama mu bitaro by'indembe z'indembe, bigera kuri 90% by'ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19 byatanzwe mu iheruka gusesengura icya gatandatu cy'igenzura ry'ibyago ry'indwara ya COVID-19 ryakozwe na ECDC, aho buri gihugu cyo muri EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza bipimirwa.
Kubera ko kugeza ubu abarwayi bakomeje kuba benshi mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA no mu duce tumwe tw'u Bwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'ibyumba by'indembe bikita ku baturage bo mu turere runaka, amakuru ajyanye n'abarwayi n'ibitanda by'indembe agomba gutangirwa ku rwego rwa Nomenclature of Territorial Unit for Statistics 2 (NUTS-2).
Ubuhanga bw'Ubutaliyani n'imiterere y'ibindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyakomeje kwiyongera cyane muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo nderabuzima bikwiye kwitegura guhangana n'iki cyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 gikomeje gukwirakwira mu baturage, ndetse n'umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi bw'imbabare, cyane cyane mu turere twibasiwe n'iki cyorezo mu Butaliyani.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe mu isuzuma ry'ibyago ryihutirwa ry'ikigo ECDC riherutse gukora, guhinduranya uburyo bwo kurwanya icyorezo ukajya ku bugabanya, bisaba uburyo bwihuse, burimo ibikorwa byinshi kandi bwihuse, kugira ngo ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2 rigabanuke, kuko mu gihe bidakoreshejwe hakiri kare, kwiyongera kwihuse kw'umubare w'abarwayi bishobora kudahita bihagije abafata ibyemezo n'ibitaro kugira ngo bumve, bemere kandi bajye mu buryo bukwiriye.
Ibarurishamibare ry'ibyago ryihutirwa kandi rigaragaza ingamba za leta zo kurwanya icyorezo.
Ibihugu bifite amahirwe make yo kongera ingamba zo kurwanya no kugabanya umuvuduko w'ubuvuzi mu rwego rwo kugabanya ikwirakwizwa rya SARS-CoV-2.
Iyo ibyo bitabaye, birashoboka cyane ko mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere, gahunda z'ubuvuzi z'ibindi bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi na Aziya (EU/EEA) zishobora guhura n'ubwiyongere bukabije bw'abarwayi bakeneye ubutabazi bukabije.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) cyatewe na SARS-CoV-2 (Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome) Coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) cyahitanye abantu barenga 3000 kugeza ubu, kandi cyandura abarenga 80,000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu ku isi, biviramo ibyago ku bantu.
Kimwe na virusi ya SARS-CoV, yateye SARS mu bantu babarirwa mu bihumbi mu mwaka wa 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba yaturutse ku ducurama kandi ikagaragaza ibimenyetso nk'ibyo.
Nubwo COVID-19 ifite ubukana n'umubare w'abapfa ari bike ugereranyije na SARS, ni indwara yandura cyane kandi yibasira abantu bakuze cyane kurusha urubyiruko, abagabo kurusha abagore.
Mu gusubiza umubare munini w'ibyagiye byandikwa ku ndwara zigenda zigaragara, iyi nyandiko yihatira gutanga isesengura ry'igihe kandi ryimbitse ku kibazo cy'ubushakashatsi bugenda bwiyongera.
Tuzasuzuma ibintu by'ibanze ku byerekeye indwara, indwara z'ibyorezo, impamvu z'indwara, virusi, gusuzuma, kuvura, kubara no kwirinda.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bikiri mu nzira, twizeye ko iri sesengura rizadufasha gusobanukirwa no kurandura iyi ndwara.
Umunsi mukuru w'Umuseke wabaye ku itariki ya 25 Mutarama 2020 kubera icyorezo cy'indwara ya Novel Viral, wabaye urwibutso rutangaje kandi rutazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose basabwe kuguma mu rugo mu gihe cy'iminsi mikuru no mu byumweru byakurikiyeho.
Iyi virusi isa cyane na coronavirus (CoV) yateje icyorezo cya SARS mu 2003; niyo mpamvu ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020 Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (WHO) ryise SARS-CoV-2 ndetse n'indwara ifitanye isano nayo yitwa CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiriye i Wuhan mu Bushinwa, gikwirakwira mu gihugu hose ndetse no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi.
Kugeza ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, hari hamaze kuboneka abantu barenga 80.000 banduye COVID-19, abasaga 40.000 bakaba baraye bavuye mu bitaro ndetse n'abarenga 3.000 bapfuye bazize iyi virusi.
OMS yaburiye ko COVID-19 ari umwanzi wa mbere w'abaturage kandi ko ishobora kuba ikomeye kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko byatangajwe na PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), nyuma y'amezi abiri gusa raporo ya mbere itangiye tariki ya 7 Mutarama 2020, inyandiko zirenga 200 ku byerekeye COVID-19 zagiye zandikwa, harimo izerekeranye n'ubwandu, indwara z'ibyorezo, imiterere y'indwara, gusuzuma no kuvura, ibyo bikaba byaratumye abantu benshi barokoka, maze bakamenya uko virusi yagiye ikurikirana.
Iki giterane kigamije kugaragaza uko ubushakashatsi bugeze ku rwego rushya kandi buteye imbere.
Igihe cyose bishoboka, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 n'izindi ndwara ziterwa na SARS na CoV, zirimo n'indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo hagati (MERS, 2012).
Tuzasuzuma ibyo twize kugeza ubu ku birebana no kwirinda no gusuzuma indwara, ndetse no ku bindi bibazo by'ingenzi.
CoVs mu buryo busanzwe zafatwa nk'indwara zitari iz'ubukana ku bantu, cyane cyane izitera imbeho n'ibicurane bigera kuri 15% by'ibicurane bisanzwe 4.
Nyamara muri iki kinyejana, twahuye n'indwara ebyiri z'abantu ziterwa na virusi ya CoV, ari zo SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, byibasira cyane cyane mu Bushinwa mu 2003 no muri Arabiya Saoudite mu 2012, kandi bidatinze byatangiye gukwirakwira mu bindi bihugu byinshi, bituma abantu benshi barwara kandi bagapfa.
Bityo, COVID-19 iriho ubu ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya CoV cyabayeho mu mateka y'abantu.
Nk'uko bigaragara ku ishusho ya 1.1, ibibunda by'indwara y'ubuhumyi, ituruka ku nkomoko itaramenyekana, byamenyeshejwe bwa mbere Komisiyo y'ubuzima y'u Bushinwa ivuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, hasohotse urutonde rw'ibimenyetso bya CoV.
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020, nibwo havuzwe bwa mbere umuntu umwe wapfuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Muri icyo gihe, icyorezo cyahise cyakwira mu mijyi, intara n'ibihugu byo hafi aho.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, abaganga batanze amakuru y'uko abantu banduye, byerekana ko abantu bashobora kwandura.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, umujyi wa Wuhan washyizwe muri gahunda ya guma mu rugo, imodoka zose ziva mu mujyi zifunga.
Ku ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere ku ndwara bwerekanye ko mu barwayi 41 bemejwe ko banduye, 21 bonyine ari bo bari bafite aho bahuriye n'isoko ry'ibiribwa by'inyanja ry'i Wuhan, aho byemezwa ko bakomeretse ku isoko ritamenyekanye.
Ku ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo ari icy'ingutu ku isi.
Kugeza igihe iyi raporo yandikiwe, iyi virusi yari imaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa hose no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi (Ifoto (Ifoto ya 2). 2).
Kubera ko iki cyorezo kiri kwiyongera cyane, ntiharatangazwa uko kizakwira hose cyangwa uko kizakomera.
Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, inyigo y'imyanya myinshi ku barwayi 8,866 harimo 4,021 bafite icyorezo cya COVID-19 yatanzweho ishusho y'icyorezo iheruka gukorwa (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
Abantu bafite imyaka yose banduye SARS-CoV-2, ariko cyane cyane abari hagati y'imyaka 30 na 65.
Hafi kimwe cya kabiri (47.7%) cy'abanduye bari bafite imyaka 50 n'iyirenga, bake cyane bari munsi y'imyaka 20 naho 14 gusa bari munsi y'imyaka 10.
