Ni yo mpamvu ubufasha bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero ari ingenzi cyane mu guhangana n'indwara no kurokora ubuzima, harimo uburyo bwo gutanga umwuka wa oxygène muri rusange, guhumeka mu buryo bufite umwuka mwinshi, guhumeka mu buryo budafite umuyoboro mwinshi, no guhumeka mu buryo bufite imashini, bitewe n'uburwayi umuntu arwaye.
