Birazwi ko cytocaine Storm iterwa n'uko abarwayi ba SARS na MERS bagira abasirikare b'umubiri benshi cyane.
Igitutu cya cytokine ni ubwoko bw'imikorere y'indwara y'ubuhumekero, irangwa no kurekura uturemangingo twa cytokine harimo TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, na MCP-1.
Ibyo bituma ingirabuzima fatizo z'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri zisohora umubare munini w'imisemburo ya cytocaine, ikaba ari yo ntandaro y'indwara ya ARDS n'indwara yo kunanirwa kw'ingingo z'umubiri.
Immunosuppression ni ingenzi mu kuvura cytocaine, cyane cyane ku barwayi barembye.
Kortikosteroide na tosylizumab, ni imiti yo mu bwoko bwa monoclonal antibody, igabanya ubushobozi bwa IL6, yagiye ikoreshwa mu kuvura cytocaine.
Iyindi miti ya immunosuppressive ya cytoquinine Storm ni ukuhindura igisubizo cy'ubwirinzi cyayobowe na T-cell; gukumira IFN-γ, IL-1, na TNF; gukumira JAK; blinatumob; gukumira cytocinine signaling 4; na HDAC inhibitors.
Steroids, nk'imiti igabanya ubwirinzi bw'umubiri, zakoreshwaga cyane mu kuvura SARS mu rwego rwo kugabanya ubukana bw'ingaruka z'uburwayi.
Ariko, ingero zo hejuru za steroide ntizafashije mu barwayi ba SARS na COVID-19 bafite ikibazo gikomeye cy'imyakura.
Ahubwo, zishobora gutera ingaruka zikomeye, cyane cyane iz'ubuhumekero, bigira ingaruka zikomeye ku gusuzuma indwara.
Nyamara, kortikosteroide z'igihe gito ku bipimo bito cyangwa biciriritse, zigomba gukoreshwa mu buryo bwitondewe ku barwayi ba COVID-19 barembye.
Kugeza ubu, nta muti wa virusi uremeza ko ugira ingaruka.
Ariko, Remdesivir, ikoreshwa mu gutera intanga uruvange rw'imiterere ya nucleotide, yagaragaye ko ifite akamaro mu murwayi wo muri Amerika wanduye COVID-19.
Remdesivir ni umuti mushya uvura virusi, wabanje gukorwa na Gilead mu rwego rwo kuvura indwara ziterwa na virusi ya Ebola na Malburg.
Nyuma, Remdesivir yagaragaje ko ishobora kubuza izindi virusi z'imiterere ya RNA zidakira, harimo na virusi za MERS na SARS.
Hagati aho, Gilead yahaye u Bushinwa ibi bikoresho byo gupima abantu babiri banduye SARS-CoV-2 kandi ibisubizo by'ibizamini birategerejwe cyane.
Muri ubwo buryo, baricitinib, interferon -α, iopinavir/ritonavir, na ribavirin, byatanzwe nk'imiti ishobora gukoreshwa mu kuvura abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso bikomeye byo guhumeka.
Iyo umuntu yongeye iopinavir/ritonavir, ashobora kurwara iseru, kuribwa, kugira isesemi, kugira ikibazo cy' impyiko, ndetse n' ibindi bibazo.
Imikorere y'imiti ikoreshwa muri ubu buryo bwo kuvura igomba gukurikiranwa cyane.
Gukora poroteyine z'amaraso n'umubiri w'umuntu wanduye
Hari amateka maremare yo gukusanya amaraso y'abarwayi barwaye indwara y'icyorezo kugira ngo bajye kuvura abandi barwaye indwara nk'iyo, cyangwa se kugira ngo barinde abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza kwandura indwara.
Mu by'ukuri, amaraso y'abarwayi bavuye mu bitaro aba afite ubwirinzi buhambaye ku byerekeye virusi.
Igisibo ni immunoglobuline (Ig) z'ubwirinzi zikorwa n'ingirabuzimafatizo za B z'indwara z'amaraso, kugira ngo zirwanye indwara n'ibindi bintu by'inyamahanga, kandi zihita zimenya uturemangingo tutari utw'inzoka kandi zikaba ari zo zigira ingaruka ku ndwara.
Hashingiwe kuri ibyo, amaraso y'abantu barwaye COVID-19 mu itsinda ry'abarwayi barwaye COVID-19 bakusanyijwe, maze bayashyirwa mu barwayi 10 bari barembye cyane.
Ibimenyetso bye byaragabanutse mu gihe cy'amasaha 24, bitewe n'uko yari afite ibyago bike byo kurwara no kurwara virusi, kandi amaraso ye akaba afite umwuka mwiza.
Ariko kandi, kugeza igihe hazakororerwa imiti yihariye, hagomba kuba hari ibihamya n'ibisobanuro kugira ngo ubwo buryo bukoreshwe mu rwego rwo hejuru.
Byongeye kandi, nubwo hari ingaruka zo kuvura, hari ingaruka zimwe na zimwe zo gukoresha plasma zigomba kwitabwaho cyane.
Urugero, abasirikare b'umubiri bashobora gutuma ubwirinzi bw'umubiri bugabanuka cyane, bigatuma umuntu agira ikibazo cyo kureka sitokine, ibyo bikaba byamutera uburwayi.
Ubusanzwe, amaraso aba afite umubare muto w'abasirikare b'umubiri, kandi hakenewe cyane plasma mu kuvura abarwayi barembye.
Biragoye cyane ko hakorwa vuba kandi hakorwa inkingo zihariye zo kurwanya icyorezo cyugarije isi.
Niyo mpamvu ari ngombwa kandi ari ingirakamaro gutandukanya B cells z'abarwayi bakize no kumenya kode y'ibanga y'umubiri ihindura ubudahangarwa cyangwa gusuzuma ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri ku bimenyetso by'ingenzi by'iyi virusi.
Muri ubwo buryo, dushobora kongera vuba vuba umusaruro w'ubwirinzi.
TCM yakoreshejwe mu kuvura indwara zitandukanye mu Bushinwa mu gihe cy'imyaka ibihumbi.
Icyakora, ingaruka zabyo ziba zishingiye ku buryo ibintu bitandukanye bikoramo, cyane cyane mu buryo butandukanye bitewe n'uko indwara runaka ishobora kuba yaragaragajwe hakurikijwe amahame ya TCM.
Ibyinshi mu bintu by'ingenzi by'ingenzi mu byo bakoresha, biracyari ibitazwi cyangwa se nta cyo bimaze, kubera ko bigoye kubirondora no kubisuzuma.
Kugeza ubu, TCM yabaye bumwe mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze ku barwayi bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa barwaye cyane, cyangwa se abakize icyorezo cya COVID-19, bitewe n'uko nta miti ihwitse kandi yihariye ihari.
Urugero, shyu feng ji du capsules na Lian Hua Qing wen capsules byagaragaye ko bifite akamaro mu kuvura COVID-19.
Mu ntara nyinshi zo mu Bushinwa, harimo Gansu (63.7%), Ninxia (50%) na Hunan (50%) zagaragaje ko abarwayi 87% bakoresheje TCM ari bo bagize ibyago byinshi byo gukira mu gihe mu ntara ya Hubei, aho abarwayi 30% gusa bakoresheje TCM, abarwayi bari bake (13%).
Icyakora, ibi ni ugupima cyane kuko hari izindi ngengabitekerezo, urugero nk'umubare w'abarwayi n'uburemere bw'indwara, bigomba kugenzurwa mu gusuzuma.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Boley Zheng na bagenzi be basohoye inyigo yagereranyaga uburyo bwo kuvura bw'imiti yo mu Burengerazuba bwonyine (WM) n'uburyo bwo kuvura bw'imiti yo mu Burengerazuba bw'isi (WM) buvanze n'ubuvuzi bwa TCM.
Basanze igihe cyo kugeza ubushyuhe ku rwego rusanzwe, kugaragaza ibimenyetso no kujya mu bitaro mu itsinda rya WM+TCM, cyari gito cyane ugereranyije n'itsinda rya WM gusa.
Icy'ingenzi cyane, ni uko ikigereranyo cy'indwara (kuva ku ndwara ntoya kugeza ku ndwara ikomeye) cy'itsinda rya WM+TCM cyari kiri hasi cyane (7.4% vs 46.2%) n'umubare w'abapfuye wari hasi cyane (8.8% vs. 39%) ugereranyije n'itsinda rya WM+TCM gusa.
Ariko kandi, hakirindiriye ko hakorwa ubushakashatsi ku rwego rwo hejuru, ku kigero cyo hejuru no mu bigo byinshi kugira ngo hagaragare ko TCM ifite akamaro kandi ko nta ngaruka igira.
Byaba ari ingirakamaro kumenya uburyo bw'ibikorwa, kandi niba bishoboka, tukagaragaza neza ibice by'ingenzi bigize uburyo bwo kuvura bwa TCM cyangwa uburyo bwo kubishyira hamwe.
Abarwayi bakekwaho cyangwa bemejwe ko bafite COVID-19 bagira ubwoba bwinshi bw'uburwayi bwandura cyane kandi buhitana, kandi abantu bashyizwe mu kato na bo bagira umujinya, bakagira irungu n'umujinya.
Byongeye kandi, ibimenyetso by'ubwandu nk'umuriro, ubwiyongere bw'imyakura n'inkorora, ndetse n'ingaruka mbi z'ubuvuzi, urugero nko kudasinzira biterwa na kortikosteroid, bishobora gutuma umuntu arushaho kugira impungenge n'imibabaro yo mu mutwe.
Mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya SARS, abantu benshi bari bafite ibibazo byo mu mutwe, harimo guhora bahangayitse, guhangayika, guhangayika bikabije, guhangayika bikabije, kugaragaza ibimenyetso by'uburwayi bwo mu mutwe, kurota, ndetse no kwiyahura.
Gushyiraho uburyo bwo guhura no kwitarura abantu mu rwego rw'ubutabazi bwa leta mu rwego rwo guhangana n'icyorezo cya COVID-19, bishobora gutuma abantu barushaho guhangayika no kwiheba kubera ingaruka z'ubwandu, kwitarura abantu no guharabika imiryango yabo n'inshuti zabo.
Ni yo mpamvu, abarwayi ba COVID-19, abakekwaho kwibasirwa na yo n'ababa bari mu biganza byabo, ndetse n'abaturage muri rusange, bagomba kwitabwaho mu bijyanye n'ubuzima bwo mu mutwe.
Ubufasha mu by'imitekerereze bugomba kuba burimo gushyiraho amatsinda y'ubuzima bwo mu mutwe mu byiciro binyuranye, itumanaho ryumvikana neza, amakuru arambuye kandi y'ukuri ku birebana n'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 n'ingamba zo gukemura iki cyorezo, no gukoresha ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga n'imikorere kugira ngo abantu birinde guhura.
Inkingo zikora neza ni ngombwa kugira ngo umuntu atagera ku ndwara z'ibyorezo, haba mu mikorobe cyangwa mu bantu banduye, kandi akenshi zikoreshwa mu rwego rwo kurwanya indwara ziterwa n'indwara z'ibyorezo.
Hari hashyizweho ingamba zo gukora inkingo zishingiye kuri S-proteine kugira ngo haboneke ubwirinzi n'ubwirinzi birinda SARS-CoV mu gihe kirekire kandi bikagabanya ubushobozi bwo kuyirwanya.
Inkingo z'ubwoko butandukanye bwa SARS zashyizwe mu byiciro by'ubwoko bw'ibinyabuzima.
Icyakora, ubuziranenge bw'inkingo zitezweho gukwirakwizwa mu bantu bageze mu zabukuru no mu bantu bafite uburwayi bwa virusi itera indwara y'impiswi, ndetse n'ubuziranenge bwazo mu kwandura virusi itera impiswi, bigomba kubanza kumenyekana mbere y'uko hagira inyigo y'ubuvuzi itangira.
Birashoboka ko ari yo mpamvu SARS yaje gucika mu myaka 17 ishize kandi kuva icyo gihe nta bundi burwayi bushya bwigeze buboneka.
Ibinyuranye n'ibyo, kubera ko mu turere turimo icyorezo, haba hari ibikomoka kuri zoonotic, abantu bake na bo bakomeje kwandura MERS kandi igakomeza gukwirakwira mu bindi bice by'Afurika.
Uburyo bwo gukingira MERS bwakoreshejwe hakoreshejwe virusi idakora, ADN plazmide, virusi z'ubwoko butandukanye, nanoparticles, uduce tumeze nka virusi n'uduce duto tw'ubwoko bw'imikorere y'intanga z'ubwoko bwa virusi, zimwe muri zo zikaba zarageragejwe mu mikoro.
Gushyiraho urukingo rukomeye kandi rwiringirwa rwa SARS-CoV-2 ku bantu badafite ubwirinzi ni kimwe mu bintu by'ingenzi mu guhangana n'icyorezo.
Ariko, kubera ko gukwirakwiza urukingo bisaba igihe kirekire (muri rusange kigera ku mezi 18), no kubera ko ubwoko bwa CoV buhinduka bugahinduka, biragoye cyane gutsinda.
Nk'indwara nshya, COVID-19 yatangiye kugaragaza imiterere yayo yose mu barwayi ibihumbi mu minsi ishize.
Mu bihe byinshi, abarwayi bashobora gukira buhoro buhoro nta bimenyetso by'izindi ndwara.
Nyamara, kimwe na SARS na MERS, COVID-19 nayo ifitanye isano n'uburwayi bukabije ndetse n'urupfu rw'abarwayi barwaye cyane.
Ni yo mpamvu ari ngombwa ko inzego z'ubuzima zashinga uburyo bwo gusuzuma indwara kugira ngo zishyireho gahunda z'ibanze z'ibikorwa, cyane cyane mu turere dufite amikoro make.
Dukurikije ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi, ibi bikurikira bishobora kugira uruhare cyangwa bigira aho bihuriye n'ibimenyetso byo gusuzuma abarwayi ba COVID-19 (Imeza (Imeza ya 33)):
Imyaka: Imyaka ni yo yari ikintu cy'ingenzi cyane mu gusuzuma SARS, nk'uko ari na ko bimeze kuri COVID-19.
Mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi 8,866, COVID-19 yibanze cyane ku bantu bari hagati y'imyaka 30 na 65, aho 47.7% bari hejuru y'imyaka 50 nk'uko byasobanuwe haruguru.
Abarwayi bakeneye ubuvuzi bw'isuku bari bafite ibyago byinshi byo kugira ibibazo by'uburwayi n'ubumuga, kandi bari bafite imyaka myinshi ugereranyije n'abatarayifuza (ku kigereranyo cy'imyaka 51 kuri 66) bivuga ko imyaka ari yo igena ingaruka z'abarwayi ba COVID-19.
Gender: Abagabo banduye SARS-CoV-2 baruta abagore cyane (0.31/100,000 vs 0.27/100,000), nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru.
Ibyago n'ibibazo: Abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara umutima no kurwara umutima.
Indwara z'umutima nazo zari zimwe mu mpamvu z'ingenzi z'urupfu mu barwayi ba SARS.
Biravugwa ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no kwihuza na cholangiocytes ifite ubwandu bwa ACE2 ishobora gutera indwara y'umwijima mu barwayi ba COVID-19.
Ni byiza kumenya ko imyaka n'indwara umuntu afite bifitanye isano kandi bishobora guhura.
Ibimenyetso bidasanzwe byo muri laboratwari: igipimo cya C - reactive protein (CRP) mu maraso kigaragaza uburemere bw'indwara cyangwa kwangirika kw'imyanya, kandi byatangajwe ko ari kimwe mu bishobora kugenga uburwayi, uko umuntu azitabira imiti, ndetse n'uko azabasha gukira.
Hari kandi isano hagati y'igipimo cya CRP n'ubukana bwa COVID-19 ndetse n'uburyo umuntu yafashwe.
Byongeye kandi, kongera lactate hydrogénase (LDH), aspartate aminotransferase (AST), alanine aminotransferase (ALT) na creatine kinase (CK) nabyo bishobora gufasha mu gusesengura ibisubizo.
Izi enzymes zigaragara cyane mu ngingo zinyuranye, cyane cyane mu mutima no mu mwijima, kandi zirekurwa mu gihe imitsi yangiritse.
Bityo rero, ni ibimenyetso bisanzwe by'indwara y'umutima cyangwa iy'umwijima.
Ibimenyetso by'ingenzi: Radiographie y'agatuza n'ibindi bibazo bigomba kwitabwaho mu gihe cy'uburwayi bwa COVID-19 n'ingaruka zayo.
Gukoresha Steroids: Nk'uko twabivuze haruguru, Steroids ni immunodeficiency zikoreshwa nk'ubuvuzi buhuza mu ndwara z'ibyorezo, mu rwego rwo kugabanya ubukana bw'indwara z'ibyorezo.
Kubera ko imiti ya kortikosteroide yariho ku gipimo cyo hejuru yakoreshwaga cyane mu barwayi barwaye SARS, abantu benshi barokotse barwaye indwara yo mu bwonko, bakagira ubumuga bw'igihe kirekire kandi ntibagire ubuzima bwiza.
Ni yo mpamvu, niba ari ngombwa, bakwiriye gukoresha steroid mu barwayi bafite COVID-19 mu bipimo by'amaraso biri hasi kandi mu gihe gito.
Umunaniro wo mu mutwe: Nk'uko twabivuze haruguru, abarwayi benshi bagize umunaniro udasanzwe mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19, kuko bakomeje kwihanganira igihe kirekire cy'akato n'amakuba menshi, kandi babonye impfu z'abagize imiryango ya hafi n'abarwayi bagenzi babo.
Ni ngombwa ko habaho ubufasha bw'imiti n'ubufasha bw'igihe kirekire kugira ngo aba bantu bashobore kuva mu mihangayiko no gusubira mu buzima busanzwe.
Nk'uko bigaragazwa n'ubushakashatsi ku mibare y'abaturage, COVID-19 igaragaza ibimenyetso by'icyorezo bitandukanye n'ibya SARS.
