Igishushanyo cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19 ugereranyije na SARS na MERS ni ibi bikurikira (Igishushanyo cya 55):
SARS-CoV-2 yandura cyane cyane binyuze mu gukorora cyangwa guhumeka ndetse no guhura n'ibintu bishobora kuba byanduye virusi.
Nanone kandi, virusi y'agakoko ishobora no kwandurira mu muriro, ibyo bikaba byumvikanisha ko hashobora kubaho uburyo bushya bwo kwandurira mu kanwa hakoreshejwe umuriro.
Ubushakashatsi buherutse gukorwa ku bantu 138 bwerekanye ko 41% by'abarwayi, harimo 17 bari bafite izindi ndwara n'abandi 40 bari bavuye kwa muganga, bashobora kuba baranduye indwara zo mu bitaro.
Ni yo mpamvu hakwiye gushyirwaho ingamba zikomeye zo kurinda abantu, by'umwihariko abatanga serivisi z'ubuzima, abakozi mu miryango, abagize umuryango, abo bakorana n'abarwayi, abagiye kuba hafi y'abo bantu cyangwa abahuye n'abo bantu.
Uburyo bwa mbere bwo kwirinda bw'ingenzi cyane mu kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura ni ukwambara udupfukamunwa; gukoresha udupfukamunwa two mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi n'udupfukamunwa two mu bwoko bwa N95 (series #1860) bifasha mu kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi.
Udupfukamunwa two mu maso tuvura turinda udutonyanga tw'amazi gutambuka mu kirere cyangwa ku bintu bishobora kwandura umuntu ufite ubwandu, aho bishobora kwanduza abandi.
Ariko, ni udupfukamunwa twa N95 (series # 1860s) gusa dushobora kurinda udupfukamunwa duto cyane nka 10 na 80 nm, kuko 5% by'utwo dupfukamunwa ari two tubasha kurenga burundu; SARS-CoV-2 isa na SARS-CoV mu bunini kandi yombi ifite 85 nm.
Kubera ko utuntu dushobora no kwambuka udupfukamunwa dutanu dushyizwe hejuru, abatanga ubuvuzi bahuye n'abarwayi bagomba kwambara udupfukamunwa twa N95 (series # 1860s), ariko ntabwo ari udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi.
Hamwe n'udupfukamunwa, abashinzwe ubuzima bagomba kwambara imyenda yo kwitarura abandi kugira ngo barinde kwandura virusi.
Virusi ishobora no kwandurira umuntu amaso.
Ku ya 22 Mutarama 2020, umuganga umwe yanduye SARS-CoV-2, nubwo yari yambaye agapfukamunwa ka N95; virusi ishobora kuba yarinjiye mu mubiri we binyuze mu maso ye yanduye.
Ku bw'ibyo, abatanga serivisi z'ubuzima bagomba kwambara udupfukamunwa cyangwa amadarubindi igihe bakorana n'abarwayi.
