Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatewe n'agakoko gashya ka SARS-CoV-2, cyatangiye mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019.
Mu gihe kitageze ku mezi abiri, iki cyorezo cyakwiriye mu Bushinwa hose no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi yose mu gihe iyi nkuru yandikwaga.
Kubera ko virusi isa cyane na SARS-CoV kandi ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 na SARS bikaba ari bimwe, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatumye SARS igaruka kenshi.
Ariko, hari itandukaniro rikomeye riri hagati ya COVID-19 na SARS, rikenewe kugira ngo icyorezo kigabanuke no kugira ngo abarwayi bavurwe.
COVID-19 yibasira abantu bakuze cyane kurusha abakiri bato, abagabo kurusha abagore, kandi abageze mu zabukuru bafite umubare munini w'uburwayi n'abapfa kurusha abakiri bato.
SARS ifite igipimo cyo guhitana kiruta icy'icy' COVID-19 (10.91% vs 1.44%).
Abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakwirakwiza virusi nubwo baba nta bimenyetso bagaragaza, mu gihe abarwayi ba SARS bo bakwirakwiza iyo barwaye cyane, ibyo bikaba bituma gukwirakwiza COVID-19 bigorana cyane kuruta SARS.
Ibi bisobanuye igice kimwe cy'impamvu SARS-CoV-2 yandura vuba kandi ku buryo bwagutse kurusha SARS-CoV.
Ibizamini bya RNA bisanzwe bya SARS-CoV-2 bishobora kuba bibi ku barwayi bamwe na bamwe ba COVID-19.
