Ibyo ni ngombwa, ariko bishobora gufata igihe runaka kugira ngo tubone ibisubizo by'ibyo bibazo hamwe n'ibindi byinshi.
Ariko kandi, uko igiciro cyaba kiri kose, nta yandi mahitamo dufite uretse guhagarika icyorezo vuba uko bishoboka kose, no gusubiza ubuzima bwacu mu buryo busanzwe.
Igikoresho cyo kuvura cya virusi ya corona cy'abantu
Koronavirusi (CoVs) n'izindi virusi zibarirwamo (z'abantu) zabayeho mu gihe cy'imyaka ibihumbi byinshi bitewe n'impinduka no kwihuza.
Mbere y'umwaka wa 2003, hari homoni ebyiri z'abantu (HCoVs) ebyiri zari zizwiho gutera indwara zoroheje nk'ibicurane.
Icyorezo cya SARS n'icya Middle East Respiratory Syndrome (MERS) byahinduye ibintu, byerekana ubukana bw'icyorezo cya HCoV.
Mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2019, icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 cyadutse mu Bushinwa bwo hagati, cyongeye gutuma CoVs zigaragara, kandi cyadutangaje kubera ko ifite ubushobozi bwo kwanduza kurusha SARS-CoV yacyo, ariko ikaba ifite ubushobozi bwo gutera indwara bugabanutse.
Indwara ya HCoV ni indwara yandurira mu nyamaswa kandi gusobanukirwa inkomoko ya HCoVs mu nyamaswa byadufasha.
HCoVs nyinshi zaturutse mu mikere, aho usanga zitandura.
Hari n'amakuru ajyanye n'ibinyabuzima by'ibanze bya HCoVs.
Kumenya ibyokurya bituruka ku matungo bigira uruhare mu kwirinda indwara z'abantu.
Gusuzuma imikoranire y'utubingo n'utundi turimo CoV mu nyamaswa bishobora gutanga amakuru y'ingenzi ku bijyanye n'imiterere y'ubwandu bwa CoV mu bantu.
Muri iyi nkuru, turatanga amakuru y'ibanze ku byerekeye za HCoVs ndwi, tureba amateka y'ubushakashatsi, ndetse n'amakuru ariho ubu, tureba ku nkomoko y'ibinyabuzima no ku kwanduzanya mu bwoko.
Icy'ingenzi cyane, ni ugukorera ubushakashatsi ku mikorobe zitandukanye za HCoVs no kureba aho zitandukaniye, mu rwego rw'ihindagurika ry'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima n'uko zongera guhuriramo imiterere y'ingirabuzimafatizo.
Iki cyorezo cya COVID-19 kivugwamo muri iyi nteruro.
Nanone, hakigaragaza ko hakenewe guhinduka mu buryo bw'ibanze mu miterere y'ibyokurya, kandi hagaragaza ko iterambere rya virusi rifite ingaruka ku burwayi.
Virusi ya Corona (CoVs) ni izo mu muryango wa Coronaviridae, zigizwe n'itsinda ry'uducurama twitwa enveloped, positive-sensed, single-stranded RNA.
Izo virusi z'ubwoko bwa CoVs, zifite genom nini cyane iri hagati ya 26 na 32 mu za RNA, ziswe CoVs kubera imiterere yazo imeze nk'ikamba ry'igishushanyo munsi ya mikorosikopi ya elegitoroniki.
Mu buryo bw'imiterere, CoVs zifite genomes zidashobora kuboneka zifite imiterere isa.
Hafi 2/3 bya genome z'umuntu ziba zifite ibice bibiri by'ibanze (ORF1a na ORF1b) by'ibanze byandika mu buryo bw'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima, bigasimburwa na pp1a na pp1ab.
Iyo poroteyine y'amabara menshi ikorwa mu buryo bw'inyongera kugira ngo haboneke poroteyine 16 z'udutubumbano zitwa nsp1 - 16.
Ibindi bice bigize genome, biba bifite ORF zigenga iby'imikorere y'ingirabuzimafatizo, harimo spike (S), envelope (E), membrane (M) na nucleoproteine (N).
Imiryango itandukanye ya CoVs na yo ifite poroteyine nyinshi z'imiterere.
Hakurikijwe itandukaniro ry'urukurikirane rw'ibinyabuzima, CoV igabanyijemo amoko ane (alfa-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV na delta-CoV), aho beta-CoV ifite HCoVs nyinshi, kandi igabanwa mu moko ane (A, B, C na D).
Ibihamya by'ubwoko bw'ibinyabuzima byerekanye ko ibiganza n'ibinyonyi ari byo soko y'ibinyabuzima bya alpha-CoVs na beta-CoVs, mu gihe inyoni ari zo soko y'ibinyabuzima bya gamma-CoVs na delta-CoVs.
Mu gihe cy'imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi, CoVs yagiye ikomeza kurenga inzitizi z'ubwoko runaka, ndetse igera ku rwego rwo kuba zimwe mu ndwara zikomeye ku bantu.
Kugeza ubu, hamaze kumenyekana virusi zirindwi z'abantu zanduza virusi ya korona (HCoVs).
Muri zo harimo HCoV-229E na HCoV-NL63 alpha-CoVs.
Izindi beta-CoV eshanu ni HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, koronavirusi itera indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero ikaze (SARS-CoV), koronavirusi yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS-CoV) na SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63 akenshi ziteza ibimenyetso byoroheje nk'ibicurane na diyabete.
Ibinyuranye n'ibyo, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 nshya, ni indwara zandura cyane, zikaba zishobora gutera indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye cyane mu barwayi bafite indwara z'ubuhumekero (ARDS) kandi bafite ibyago byinshi byo kugaragaza ibimenyetso by'ibicurane.
HCoV-229E ya mbere, B814, yatandukanyijwe n'imvubura z'amagufa z'abarwayi bari bafite ibicurane mu myaka ya za 1960.
Kuva icyo gihe, amakuru menshi yakusanyijwe binyuze mu bushakashatsi bwagutse bwakozwe kuri HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, byombi byerekana ibimenyetso by'ubwigenge.
Mu by'ukuri, mbere y'icyorezo cya SARS, abantu benshi bari bazi ko ubwandu bwa virusi ya HCoVs nta ngaruka bubagira.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyateye mu mwaka wa 2003 cyatumye abantu barenga 8000 bahitanwa n'icyorezo, kandi abamaze guhitanwa nacyo bari hafi 10%, ni kimwe mu byorezo by'ingutu cyane byabayeho mu mateka y'isi.
Nyuma y'imyaka icumi, icyorezo cya MERS cyadutse mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, cyandura cyane mu gice cy'Abarabu, ndetse no mu bindi bice by'isi.
2019 Novel HCoV (2019-nCoV), nyuma y'aho yaje kwitwa SARS-CoV-2, ni cyo cyorezo cyateye icyorezo cya Koronavirusi y'indwara ya 2019 (COVID-19), kikaba cyahitanye abantu 3,120 n'abarenga 91,000 kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020.
Impanvu zo kugabisha zirimo zirumvikana kandi isi igomba kwitegura icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 kigiye kuza.
Zose uko ari 7 za HCoV zifite inkomoko ku ducurama, ku ducurama cyangwa ku nyamaswa zo mu ngo.
Ibihamya byinshi bishyigikira iterambere ry'udutsiko tw'amababa tw'ubwoko bwose bwa HCoVs, aho virusi zisanzwe kandi zitandura, ariko zigaragaza itandukaniro rikomeye ry'imiterere.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyateje ibibazo bikomeye mu buvuzi, mu bumenyi, mu mibanire no mu mahame y'isi mu Bushinwa no ku isi hose.
Gushakisha inkomoko y'ubwoko bwa HCoVs bitanga urwego rwo gusobanukirwa amateka y'ubwoko bw'ibinyabuzima, imbaraga z'ubwoko n'ibimenyetso by'ubwandu.
Ibi bishobora kuyobora cyangwa korohereza ubushakashatsi ku binyabuzima by'ibanze, iby'imbere n'ibinyongera mu mubiri bya SARS-CoV-2, mu rwego rwo kugira ingaruka zikomeye ku gukwirakwira kw'indwara mu gihe kizaza.
Muri iyi nyandiko, turagaragaza inkomoko y'ibinyabuzima, ikwirakwizwa mu bantu no kurwara kw'indwara z'ubwoko bwa HCoVs.
By'umwihariko, turagaragaza kandi tukaganira ku ngingo rusange y'uko virusi z'ababyeyi ba HCoVs zidakunda kwandura mu mikorobe zisanzwe, ariko zikaba zanduza nyuma yo kwanduza izindi mikorobe.
Tuzasuzuma kandi imiterere y'ubwiyongere bw'ubwandu bwa HCoV, aho ubwandu bw'ubwandu buzamuka akenshi buherekejwe no kugabanuka kw'ubwandu.
Muri iyi nkuru kandi havugwamo ingaruka z'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 gikomeje.
CoVs zo mu nyamaswa zari zizwi kuva mu mpera za 1930.
Mbere y'ubwoko bwa HCoV-229E bw'abantu bwa mbere bwatowe mu myanya y'imyanya y'ubuhumekero y'abarwayi barwaye ibicurane, hari izindi CoVs zitandukanye zaturutse ku nyamaswa zanduye nyinshi harimo inkoko, imbeba, inka, ingurube, amakoti n'imbwa.
Mu myaka icumi ishize, hamaze kuvumburwa za HCoV zirindwi.
Igisobanuro kigufi cy'amateka y'ubushakashatsi ku mikorobe (Imbonerahamwe ya 1) kizatanga amakuru kandi gitange inyigisho.
Ubwoko bwa mbere bwa HCoV-229E bwabonetse mu 1966 mu nzira y'ubuhumekero bw'abarwayi bafite ubwandu bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yo hejuru, nyuma buza guhinduka bukura mu misemburo y'ingirabuzimafatizo yo mu bihaha ya WI-38.
Mu barwayi banduwe na HCoV-229E, hagati ya 10 na 20% bagaragayeho ibimenyetso by'ibicurane birimo kubabara umutwe, kurira, kuribwa mu muhogo no kuribwa mu muhogo.
Nyuma yaho mu 1967, HCoV-OC43 yaje gutandukanywa n'uburyo bw'imiterere y'ubwonko bw'imbeba zikamwa, n'uburyo bw'imiterere y'ibice by'umubiri.
Imirongo ngenderwaho y'indwara ya HCoV-OC43 isa n'iy'indwara ya HCoV-229E, kandi mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo, ntaho ihuriye n'indwara y'ibicurane y'izindi ndwara z'ubuhumekero, urugero nka virusi ya Influenza A na rhinovirus.
HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43 byombi birakwirakwiriye ku isi hose kandi birashoboka ko byandurira cyane cyane mu gihe cy'ubukonje n'ikirere cy'imberabyombi.
Ubusanzwe, iyo virusi zombi zigenda zikurikirana, igihe cy'uburwayi kimara kiba munsi y'icyumweru, nyuma y'ibyo hakaba habaho ibyumweru bibiri by'uburwayi.
Nk'uko bigaragazwa n'ubushakashatsi ku bantu b'abakorerabushake, abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza banduye HCoV-229E bagize ikibazo cy'ibicurane byoroheje.
Abarwayi bake bafite ubwirinzi bw'umubiri, ni bo bonyine bagaragaza ubwandu bukabije bw'ubuhumekero.
SARS, nanone izwi ku izina rya "Atipical Pneumonia", ni cyo cyorezo cya mbere cyanditswe mu mateka y'abantu cyatewe na HCoV, kandi SARS-CoV ni yo ya gatatu yanduye.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyabonetse bwa mbere mu Bushinwa mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2002 mu ntara ya Guangdong.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyakwirakwije mu bihugu byinshi no ku migabane, kigahitana abantu 774 n'ubwandu bushya bwa 8,096.
Uretse abafite ubwandu bwinshi, byemejwe ko buri murwayi ashobora kuba afite nibura abarwayi babiri b'icyiciro cya kabiri, bitewe n'uko habaho igihe cy'ubwiyongere cy'iminsi 4 kugeza kuri 7 kandi virusi igaragara cyane ku munsi wa 10 w'uburwayi.
Abanduye SARS-CoV bagaragaza ku ikubitiro ibimenyetso birimo kubabara mu myanya, kuribwa umutwe, kugira umuriro, kugira isesemi no guhinda umushyitsi, nyuma y'aho bagaragaza guhumeka nabi, gukorora no guhumeka nabi.
Indwara ya Lymphopenia, indwara y'umwijima udakora neza, ndetse no kwiyongera kw'indwara ya creatine kinase, ni bimwe mu bibazo by'umwihariko by'indwara ya SARS.
Ibyangijwe n'uko habaho kwangirika kw'umusokoro w'umwuka, ikwirakwira ry'insoro z'uruhu no kwiyongera kwa za macrophages nabyo biraboneka mu barwayi ba SARS.
Hafi 20% - 30% by'abarwayi nyuma yaho bakenera kwitabwaho cyane no guhumeka hakoreshejwe imashini.
Uretse inzira y'ubuhumekero yo hasi, ubusanzwe harimo inzira y'umwijima, impyiko n'impyiko, harimo n'izindi ngingo zishobora kwandura mu gihe bikomeye, cyane cyane ku barwayi bafite ubwirinzi buke.
Iyi virusi yabonetse bwa mbere mu gupima umuntu w'igitsina gabo mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'ubuvuzi bw'ibihaha, mu gihe uwo muntu yari avuye muri Guangzhou akajya muri Hong Kong.
Kuva icyo gihe, ubushakashatsi ku bwoko bwa HCoV bwakozwe mu buryo bwimbitse.
HCoV-NL63 yabonetse mu bana bo mu Buholandi mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2004 bafite amezi 7.
Mu ntangiriro, byagaragaye ko yageze no ku bana bato, ku bantu bageze mu za bukuru no ku barwayi bafite ubwirinzi bw'umubiri budahagije bafite indwara z'ubuhumekero.
Indwara ziterwa na HCoV-NL63 zikunze kugaragaramo ibicurane, ubukana, umuriro, n'uburwayi bw'imitsi.
Ubundi bushakashatsi bwigenga, bwasobanuye ibyo gutandukanya virusi imwe n'imwe mu cyuma cy'umwana w'amezi 8 wo mu Buholandi urwaye umusonga.
Nubwo byavumbuwe mu Buholandi, mu by'ukuri byatangiye gukwirakwira hirya no hino ku isi.
Bivugwa ko HCoV-NL63 iteza hafi 4.7% by'indwara z'ubuhumekero, kandi ko iboneka cyane mu mpeshyi, mu itumba no mu gihe cy'itumba.
HCoV-NL63 ifitanye isano n'indwara y'ubuhumekero, nanone izwi ku izina rya Krup.
Muri uwo mwaka, HCoV-HKU1 yabonetse mu muntu w'umusaza w'imyaka 71 wari wararwaye nimoniya na bronchiolitis, akaba yari yarahawe imiti mu bitaro byo muri Hong Kong.
Uretse guhangana n'indwara z'ubuhumekero n'ubuhumekero, HCoV-HKU1 na yo bivugwa ko ifite aho ihuriye n'indwara ikomeye ya asthma.
Kimwe na HCoV-NL63, HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 yagaragaye ku isi yose, ikaba iteza indwara z'ubuhumekero bworoheje.
Izo HCoVs zose uko ari enye zaturutse mu baturage, zarahindutse cyane mu bantu kandi ntizishobora guhinduka ngo zitere indwara zikomeye, nubwo hari igihe habayeho impanuka ziturutse ku mpamvu zitazwi, nk'uko byagenze ku bwoko bwa HCoV-NL63, bwagaragaye mu gihe gito, buherutse guterwa n'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero mu Bushinwa.
Ubusanzwe, iyo HCoV zigejeje ubushobozi bwo gushobora gukwirakwira neza no gukwirakwira mu bantu, ziba zidakunda kwanduza cyangwa guteza indwara.
MERS-CoV yatandukanyijwe bwa mbere mu 2012 mu bihaha by'umurwayi w'imyaka 60 wo muri Arabiya Sawudite, wagize ibibazo bikomeye by'impiswi n'indwara y'impyiko.
Nubwo abenshi mu barwayi bemejwe na laboratwari bakomoka mu Burasirazuba bwo hagati, hari abamaze kwandura mu bihugu byinshi by'i Burayi no muri Tuniziya, rimwe na rimwe bakandukira abafitanye isano ya hafi.
Mu mwaka wa 2015, mu gihugu cya Koreya y'Epfo habayeho ikindi cyorezo cya kabiri, kiza kubarurwaho abarwayi 186.
Imigaragarire y'indwara ya MERS, igaragara nk'indwara y'umwijima ikomeye, ihwanye n'iy'indwara ya SARS.
Abantu benshi barwaye MERS barwaye indwara z'impyiko z'ubuhumyi, bitandukanye n'abafite SARS, indwara z'ubwandu bwa HCoV zigeze kuboneka muri MERS gusa.
Abarenga 30% bagaragaza ibimenyetso by'indwara y'umwijima, urugero nk'isukari no gufungana.
Kugeza ku ya 14 Gashyantare 2020, abamaze kwandura MERS-CoV ni 2500 mu gihe umubare w'abahitanwa na yo uri hejuru ya 34.4%, bituma iyi virusi iba imwe mu zangiza cyane abantu.
Mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019 hagati, umwimbu w'abarwayi b'indwara y'ibicurane by'ibyorezo bya SARS-CoV-2 wabonetse mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryemeje ko icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 ari icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero, ari ikibazo cy'ihungabana ry'ubuzima rusange rihangayikishije amahanga, ndetse ryemeza ko icyorezo ari COVID-19.
Kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020, ku isi hose hamaze kwandura 90,053 mu gihe ubwandu bushya bwa COVID-19 bwanduye abantu 3,4 ku ijana.
Igitangaje ni uko mu mujyi wa Hubei mu Bushinwa, umubare w'abamaze kwandura ari 4.2%, mu gihe hanze yawo ari 1.2%.
SARS-CoV-2 iteza indwara zikomeye z'ubuhumekero, nk'uko SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV ziboneka mu gihe umuntu afite umuriro, gukorora no kugira ububabare mu gihe ahumeka.
Hari abarwayi bamwe na bamwe bajya bagira igifu.
Indwara y'umusonga ni kimwe mu bimenyetso bikomeye cyane kandi ishobora kwiyongera cyane ikagira indi ndwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze.
Nubwo SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 zisa cyane bitewe n'uko zisa cyane, bitewe n'uko zisa cyane ku kigero cya 82% mu miterere ya za nucleotide, zigira amoko atandukanye.
SARS-CoV-2 igaragaza uburwayi buke ariko ikaba ishobora kwandura cyane kurusha SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV.
Abantu bafite ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 byatangiye kugaragara kandi bishobora gutuma ikwirakwira ku isi mu buryo bwihuse.
Kugereranya SARS-CoV-2 n'izindi virusi esheshatu za HCoV no kureba aho zihuriye, byerekanye ibintu byinshi bihambaye.
Icya mbere, igihe cyo kwandura n'igihe cy'imikorere y'indwara ya HCoV ni kimwe.
Muri ibyo, SARS-CoV-2 ikurikiza icyitegererezo cya HCoVs esheshatu.
Icya kabiri, ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bifite uburemere nk'ubw'indwara ya SARS-CoV na za HCoVs enye zaturutse mu baturage (izo zikaba ari HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63).
Ku ruhande rumwe, ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bugaragaza ibimenyetso bikunze kugaragara mu kwandura HCoVs zanduye mu baturage, harimo kuba zidakora ku bantu, zidakomeye cyangwa zitatanga ibimenyetso.
Ku rundi ruhande, hari n'uduce duto tw'abantu barwaye cyane bagaragaza ko bafite COVID-19, nk'uko bimeze ku ndwara ya SARS-CoV, nubwo umubare ari muto.
Icya gatatu, ni uko SARS-CoV-2 yandura mu buryo butandukanye n'ubw'ubwoko bwa HCoVs na SARS-CoV zanduye mu baturage.
Ku ruhande rumwe, ubukana bwa SARS-CoV-2 buri hejuru ugereranyije n'ubw'izindi HCoVs zo mu bwoko bw'abantu.
Ku rundi ruhande, haracyari gushakishwa niba ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bugabanuka nyuma yo kwandurira abantu, nk'uko byagenze ku barwayi ba SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV.
Amaherezo, kimwe n'izindi HCoVs, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugenzurwa mu bipimo by'imyanda.
Niba SARS-CoV-2 ifite uruhare mu kwanduza abantu mu myanya y'ibanga, nibura mu bihe bimwe na bimwe nk'uko SARS-CoV yari imeze, bizasobanurwa n'ubushakashatsi buzakorwa mu gihe kizaza.
Birashimishije cyane cyane kureba niba SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugira imyitwarire nk'iy'abantu, nk'uko bimeze ku bindi byorezo bya HCoVs.
Nyamara, imiterere ya SARS-CoV-2 harimo ubukana, ubwandu n'ubukana bw'ubwandu nyuma yo kwanduza abantu, bishobora kugira ingaruka ku ngaruka z'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
HCoVs zaturutse mu miryango ine yose, zirangwa n'ibimenyetso byoroheje, kandi zahindutse mu bantu.
Ku rundi ruhande, birashoboka ko abantu bashobora kuba baramenyereye iyi mikorobe uko ari enye.
Mu yandi magambo, izo virusi zombi za HCoV zishobora kuba ari izariho mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya kera.
HCoVs zitera uburwayi bukomeye mu bantu n'abantu bahura n'uburwayi bukomeye buterwa na HCoVs zarakuweho.
Kugira ngo ibyo bishoboke, hakenewe ko haboneka impinduka zihinduka mu buryo bw'umubiri zibuza abantu kurya imboga, kugira ngo HCoVs zishobore kwigana mu bantu.
Muri ubwo buryo, uko igihe SARS-CoV-2 izamara ikomeje kwibasira abantu ari kinini, ni ko izarushaho kuba ishobora kwihuza n'abantu.
Iyo iyi virusi itavanyweho, gukwirakwiza mu bantu bizagorana cyane mu gihe umuntu yaba ari mu kato cyangwa mu yandi mabwiriza yo kurwanya ubwandu.
Mu myaka myinshi ishize, CoVs enye zaturutse mu baturage zagiye zikwirakwira mu bantu, zigatera imvune mu barwayi bafite ubwirinzi buke.
Izo virusi ntizikeneye inyamaswa.
