Ni ngombwa ko hagira ibikubiye mu buryo bw'isuzumwa bw' "ibikekwaho" n' "ibishobora kuba" ko COVID-19 yagaragaye.
Ku ya 6 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda ryacu ryashyize ahagaragara amabwiriza yihutirwa yo gusuzuma no kuvura ubwandu bw'icyorezo cya Koronavirusi gishya 2019 (2019-nCoV), kandi ayo mabwiriza atanga isomo rikomeye ku bumenyi dufite no ku rwego rw'isi mu kurwanya iki cyorezo.
Nubwo icyorezo cya Koronavirusi 2019 (COVID-19) ari icyorezo gishya, ubumenyi bwacu buzamuka buhoro buhoro dushingiye ku bushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'ubunararibonye mu bikorwa by'ubuvuzi; niyo mpamvu, ingamba zo gusuzuma no kuvura zikomeza kuvugururwa.
Muri iyi baruwa, twasubije ku gitekerezo cyo mu mabwiriza yacu kandi dutanga ibipimo by'ubuvuzi biheruka "abakekwaho" n' "abemejwe" mu mabwiriza mashya yo gusuzuma no kuvura COVID-19 (Icyegeranyo cya karindwi) yatangajwe na Komite y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima mu Bushinwa.
Mu Ukuboza 2019, habonetse icyorezo cya Koronavirusi nshya (2019-nCoV), ubu ikaba yitwa byemewe ko ari icyorezo cya Koronavirusi 2019 (COVID-19), maze iyo virusi ihabwa izina rya Koronavirusi yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero ikomeye cyane 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, OMS yemeje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu rwego rwo guhangana n'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2, itsinda ryacu ryateguye amabwiriza yihutirwa yo kugisha inama, yashyizwe ku rubuga rwa interineti mu kinyamakuru cy'ubushakashatsi mu by'ubuvuzi mu gisirikare, tariki 06 Gashyantare 2020.
Kuva yasohoka, byagiye bitangazwa cyane.
Ariko kandi, twibuke ko COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, ubumenyi bwacu buzamuka buhoro buhoro, bushingiye ku bushakashatsi bukorwa n'ubunararibonye mu mikorere y'ubuvuzi; ni yo mpamvu, ingamba zo gusuzuma no kuvura nazo zigenda zisubizwa.
Urugero, hagati y'itariki ya 16 Mutarama 2020 n'iya 3 Werurwe 2020, amabwiriza y'ubuvuzi y'ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima cya Repubulika y'abaturage y'u Bushinwa, ku bijyanye no gusuzuma no kuvura COVID-19 (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/) yasohoye impapuro zirindwi, zimwe muri zo zifite impinduka zikomeye.
Ubu tumaze kubona igitekerezo cya Zhou et al. ku mabwiriza yacu, batanze igitekerezo cyoroshye cyo gushyiraho ibimenyetso gishingiye ku byo babonye mu bushakashatsi bakoze.
Umurimo we wongeyeho ibimenyetso bishya mu mabwiriza yacu kandi utanga n'ingero z'agaciro kuri iki cyorezo ku isi.
Dushyigikiye umurimo wabo w'ingenzi kandi turabashimira.
Ariko kandi, ibikorwa byabo bigomba kuvugururwa hakurikijwe amabwiriza mashya yo gusuzuma no kuvura COVID-19 (Icyiciro cya karindwi cy'igeragezwa) n'ubushakashatsi buherutse gukorwa.
Nk'uko byasobanuwe mu gitabo cya karindwi (Mar 3, 2020), kugira ngo umuntu asuzume neza ko hari umuntu urwaye, biba ngombwa ko asuzuma buri kintu cyose mu mateka y'icyorezo, akareba niba hari ibimenyetso bibiri by'indwara, cyangwa se akareba niba nta bimenyetso bifatika by'icyorezo, akareba niba hari ibimenyetso bitatu by'indwara by'indwara byamaze kugaragara.
Amateka y'icyorezo: (1) Amateka y'urugendo cyangwa gutura mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu turere tuwukikije, cyangwa mu tundi duce aho COVID-19 yagaragaye mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira; (2) Amateka y'ubwandu bw'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 (bwizewe n'ibipimo by'ubushakashatsi bw'amasezerano y'ubwandu bwa aside aside ya nucleike); (3) Amateka y'ubwandu bw'ibyorezo by'ubuhumekero ku barwayi bafite ibicurane cyangwa ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu turere tuwukikije, cyangwa mu tundi duce aho COVID-19 yagaragaye mu minsi 14 mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira; (4) Amateka y'ubwandu bw'ibyorezo by'ubuhumekero ku itsinda ry'abamaze kwandura (ibicurane by'ubuhumekero byibero bigomba kuba 2 cyangwa birengaho) no mu turere duto nko mu rugo, mu biro, mu cyumba cy'ishuri, mu ishuri, n'ahandi.
Imibare y'ubuvuzi: (1) impumuro n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso byo guhumeka; (2) n'ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19; (3) umubare w'uduhimba tw'umweru mu maraso ugaragaza impumuro, ubwandu bwa lymphocyte bugabanutse cyangwa bugabanutse mu cyiciro cya mbere.
Gupima umuntu byemejwe ko arwaye bigomba gushingira ku kimenyetso kimwe mu bimenyetso by'uburwayi cyangwa ku cyemezo cy'uko arwaye ari: (1) kuba PCR yo mu gihe nyacyo yagaragaje ko arwaye SARS-CoV-2; (2) kuba urutonde rw'ibinyabuzima byose bya virusi rugaragaza ko ruhuje cyane n'izindi koronavirusi nshya zizwi; (3) kuba igisubizo cy'uburwayi bwa SARS-CoV-2 cyagaragaje ko ifite IgM yihariye n'igisubizo cya IgG; cyangwa kuba IgG yihariye ya SARS-CoV-2 yarahindutse igisubizo cya IgG kiriho, cyangwa se igisubizo cya IgG cy'uburwayi cyagaragaje ko gifite IgG yihariye cyiyongereyeho inshuro ≥4 mu cyiciro cy'ubudahangarwa ugereranyije n'icy'indwara ikomeye.
Dushobora kubona ko ibizamini bya PCR mu gihe nyacyo bya nucleic acid mu bipimo by'ubuhumekero cyangwa mu maraso byongerewe mu byiciro bya kabiri (18 Mutarama 2020) n'icya gatatu (22 Mutarama 2020).
Ikimenyetso cya virusi cyabonetse mu bipimo by'amaraso cyongereweho mu cyiciro cya kane (27 Mutarama 2020) n'icya gatanu (8 Gashyantare 2020); hanyuma mu cyiciro cya karindwi hashyirwaho ibimenyetso by'ubwoko.
Ubu bushakashatsi bwashingiye ku kazi gakomeje gukorwa n'abashakashatsi mu gushakisha ibikoresho byiza byo gupima aside ya nucleic acid kugira ngo hamenyekane vuba, ndetse no mu gushakisha ibipimo by'ubuhumekero harimo n'iby'amaraso, byatumye haboneka ibipimo bitandukanye, kandi bigatuma habaho icyuho cyo kwemeza ko umuntu afite virusi.
