Uburyo bw'ibanze bwo kuvura ni ubufasha kandi bugasuzuma ibimenyetso. Ingamba z'ubutabazi zasabwe ni: gukaraba intoki, guhisha mu maso igihe ukorora, kwirinda kwegerana n'abandi bantu no gukurikirana no kwigenga ku bantu bakekwaho kuba baranduye.
