Ku wa 31 Ukuboza 2019, inzego z'ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan (umurwa mukuru w'intara ya Hubei) mu Bushinwa, zatangaje ko habonetse abantu benshi banduye indwara y'ibicurane ku mpamvu zitamenyekanye, maze hatangira iperereza mu ntangiriro za Mutarama 2020.
Abenshi mu banduye bagaragaye mu masoko y'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja yo muri Hunan, bityo iyi virusi ikaba ari iyo mu bwoko bw'ibinyabuzima.
