Umubare nyawo w'abahitanywe na COVID-19 ushobora kuba munini cyane, kuko ushobora kuba utajyana n'abapfuye batakorewe ibizamini nk'abo bapfiriye mu rugo, mu bigo by'ubuvuzi n'ibindi.
