Iyi mibare itandukana bitewe n'akarere n'igihe, kandi iterwa n'ubwinshi bw'abashyizwe mu bipimo, ireme ry'urwego rw'ubuvuzi, uburyo bwo kuvura, igihe cy'ubwandu bwa mbere, n'ibintu biranga umubare w'abaturage nk'imyaka, igitsina n'ubuzima muri rusange. Igipimo cy'umubare w'abapfuye kigaragaza umubare w'abapfuye ugabanyije umubare w'abanduye mu gihe runaka.
Dukurikije ibipimo by'ikigo cya Johns Hopkins University, umubare w'abapfuye ku isi hose ugereranyije n'umubare w'abanduye ni 6.0% (97,039/1,617,204) kugeza ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020.
Uwo mubare ushobora gutandukana bitewe n'akarere.
Mu Bushinwa, igipimo cy'umubare w'abahitanwa n'iyo ndwara cyaragabanutse kiva kuri 17.3% (ku bantu bagaragaje ibimenyetso hagati y'itariki ya 1-10 Mutarama 2020) kigera kuri 0.7% (ku bagaragaje ibimenyetso nyuma y'itariki ya 1 Gashyantare 2020). Mu bindi bipimo harimo igipimo cy'umubare w'abahitanwa n'iyo ndwara (CFR), kigaragaza umubare w'abantu bapimwe n'iyo ndwara bapfuye, n'igipimo cy'umubare w'abahitanwa n'iyo ndwara (IFR), kigaragaza umubare w'abanduye n'abapfuye (bafite iyo ndwara n'abatayigaragaje).
Iyi mibare ntabwo ishingiye ku gihe kandi ikurikirana abantu batandukanye kuva igihe umuntu yanduriye kugeza igihe akize.
Abahanga benshi mu by'amashuri bagerageje kumenya imibare y'abantu runaka.
Ikigo cya Kaminuza ya Oxford gikora ubushakashatsi ku buvuzi bushingiye ku bimenyetso, cyagaragaje ko muri rusange, ubwandu bwa virusi bwaba buri hagati ya 0.1% na 0.39%.
Igiteranyo cyo hejuru cy'uyu mubare gihuye n'ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bw'imibare bwasuzumye ingaruka z'igerageza ku igeragezwa rya mbere ry'impanuka rya COVID-19 mu Budage n'igereranyo cya CFR.
OMS ivuga ko icyorezo gishobora kugenzurwa.
Igihe cy'icyorezo kiba kimaze kugera ku ndunduro n'igihe kizarangiriraho ntikizwi neza kandi gishobora gutandukana bitewe n'aho cyageze.
McKeeze Bonney wo muri Penn State University yagize ati "iyo indwara z'ibyorezo zishize mu nzira, ubusanzwe zirakomera, kandi zitangira kugabanuka iyo nta bikoresho birimo ibinyabuzima byongera ibinyabuzima byongera kurinda indwara.
Ariko ubu biragoye kumenya neza igihe bizabera".
Umujyanama mukuru mu by'ubuvuzi muri leta y'u Bushinwa, Zhong Nanchan, yavuze ko "byaba birangiye mu kwezi kwa gatandatu" mu gihe ibihugu byose byakurikiza inama za OMS ku ngamba zo kwirinda ikwirakwizwa ry'iyi virusi.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, Adam Kucharski wo mu ishuri ry'i Londres ryigisha ubuziranenge n'ubuvuzi bw'ibishyuhe yavuze ko SARS-CoV-2 "ishobora kumara umwaka umwe cyangwa ibiri ikwirakwizwa".
Nk'uko ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo cya Imperial College, cyayobowe na Neil Ferguson, kwirinda no gufata izindi ngamba bizakomeza "kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rubonetse (bishobora kumara amezi 18 cyangwa arenga)".
William Schaffner wo muri Kaminuza ya Vanderbilt yagize ati "Ntekereza ko coronavirus idashobora kuzimangana burundu, kubera ko yandura mu buryo bworoshye" kandi "ishobora kuba indwara y'igihe cy'impeshyi, igaruka buri mwaka".
Ibyago byo kugaruka bizaterwa n'ubwirinzi bw'itsinda n'urugero urwego rw'ubwandu.
Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bishobora kuba bidafite icyo bisobanuye, kandi abantu bayanduye bashobora kuba bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara.
Ibimenyetso bibiri bikunze kugaragara ni umuriro (88%) n'inkorora y'uruhu (68%).
Ibimenyetso bisanzwe birimo: umunaniro, gusohora kw'umusatsi (kugwa), guhumeka nabi, guhumeka nabi, kubabara mu myanya y'umubiri no mu ngingo, kuribwa mu muhogo, kuribwa umutwe, kuribwa n'imbeho, kuruka, kurira, kurwara amaraso, kurwara mu nda cyangwa mu nda. Nk'uko bitangazwa na OMS, umuntu umwe kuri batandatu arwara cyane kandi akagira ikibazo cyo guhumeka.
Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kugenzura no gukumira indwara (CDC) cyanditse ibimenyetso by'indwara z'ihungabana nk'ubuhumekero budahagije, kubabara cyangwa guhinda umushyitsi mu gatuza, guhindagurika mu buryo butunguranye, kubura umwuka, kubura ibitotsi, no guhinduka uruhu cyangwa iminwa; iyo ibyo bimenyetso bibonetse, umuntu aba agomba kwihutira kujya kwa muganga. Iyo indwara ikomeje, ishobora gutera indwara ikomeye y'umutsi, indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero, sepsis, guhumeka nabi mu myanya y'ubwonko n'urupfu.
Bamwe mu banduye bashobora kuba bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara, nta bimenyetso by'indwara bagaragaje, ariko ibipimo byemeza ko banduye, ni yo mpamvu abashakashatsi batanze inama ko abantu bahuye n'abanduye bakagenzurwa kandi bagasuzumwa kugira ngo birinde kwandura.
Abashinwa bavuga ko igipimo cy'indwara z'indwara z'umutima kiri hagati ya 44% na 44%.
Igihe cyo kwisana (igihe hagati y'ubwandu n'intangiriro y'ibimenyetso) ni iminsi iri hagati y'umunsi umwe na 14; akenshi ni iminsi itanu. Urugero rw'ikintu kitari cyitezwe, ni uko umubare w'abantu bafite COVID-19 batakaje ubushobozi bwo guhumeka wari 30% mbere, nyuma ukagabanuka ugera kuri 15%.
Hari ibintu bimwe na bimwe birimo bigomba gusobanuka ku birebana n'uburyo iyi ndwara yandura.
Iyi ndwara yibasira cyane cyane abantu bahuye hafi, hakoreshejwe utuntu duto two mu maso, mu gihe umuntu akoresha agakoko gatera indwara, mu gihe umuntu akoroye, ashimuse cyangwa se avuze; iyo abantu bahuye hafi cyane bari muri metero 1 cyangwa 2 (3 cyangwa 6 ft).
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko umuntu wakorora atagose, ashobora kurohama afite uburebure bwa metero 4,5 (metero 15 z'uburebure) na metero 8.2 (metero 27 z'uburebure).
Bamwe batanze igitekerezo ko virusi ishobora no kwandura mu gihe umuntu avuga, ikandururwa n'udutonyanga duto cyane, tuzamara igihe kirekire mu kirere. Udutonyanga two mu mwuka dushobora no kuvamo mu gihe umuntu ahumeka, harimo n'igihe umuntu avuga, nubwo virusi idakunze guhumeka.
Ayo matembabuzi ashobora kujya mu kanwa cyangwa mu mazuru y'abantu bari hafi, cyangwa se akaba ashobora kujya mu bihaha binyuze mu guhumeka.
Bimwe mu bikorwa byo kwa muganga, urugero nk'ubuvuzi bw'imitsi n'ubuvuzi bw'imitsi bw'umutima (CPR), bishobora gutuma umwuka utagenda neza mu gihe umuntu ari mu kirere, bityo bikaba byatuma umwuka utambuka.
Ishobora kandi gukwirakwizwa n'umuntu ukora ku kintu cyanduye harimo uruhu, hanyuma agakora ku maso, izuru cyangwa umunwa.
Nubwo hari impungenge ko ishobora kwandura binyuze mu muhogo, nta gihangayikishije cyane.
Guverinoma y'u Bushinwa yahakanye ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwandurira mu kanwa binyuze mu musarani. Iyi virusi yandura cyane mu minsi itatu ya mbere nyuma y'uko umuntu agaragaza ibimenyetso, nubwo bishoboka ko ishobora kwandura mbere y'uko umuntu agaragaza ibimenyetso no mu gihe cy'uburwayi.
Abantu bagiye bagaragaza ko banduye mu gihe cy'iminsi itatu mbere y'uko ibimenyetso by'indwara bitangira kugaragara, bikaba bigaragaza ko kwandura bishobora kubaho mbere y'uko umuntu agaragaza ibimenyetso bikomeye.
Hari raporo nke z'abantu banduye indwara z'ibyorezo zemejwe muri laboratwari, ariko hari ibihugu bimwe na bimwe byabonye abantu banduye mu gihe cyo gupima abantu bahuye n'abandi.
Nk'uko ikigo cy'u Burayi cyo kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC) kibivuga, nubwo bitamenyekanye neza uko indwara yandura mu buryo bworoshye, umuntu umwe yandurira abandi bantu babiri cyangwa batatu.
By'umwihariko, virusi yagaragaye ku bikoresho bya pulasitiki (polypropylene) na 304 ibyuma bitagira ingano, mu gihe cy'iminsi itatu, ku ikarito mu gihe cy'umunsi umwe, no mu gihe cy'amasaha ane ku cyuma.
Ariko, ibi biratandukanye bitewe n'ubuhehere n'ubushyuhe. Inzu zo mu ngo n'izindi nyamaswa byagiye byemezwa ko byazize COVID-19.
Nta gihamya kigaragaza ko virusi ishobora kwandura mu nyamaswa ikagera ku bantu, nubwo abayobozi bo mu Bwongereza batanga inama yo gukaraba intoki nyuma yo kugirana imishyikirano n'inyamaswa, kimwe n'uko bakaraba nyuma yo gukora ku bindi bintu byakoranyweho n'umuntu wanduye.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus yo mu bwoko bwa SARS-CoV-2 (Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome Coronavirus 2) ni virusi nshya, yabonetse bwa mbere mu bantu batatu bafite nimoniya, mu itsinda ry'abarwaye indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero ryagaragaye mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Ibintu byose biranga virusi nshya ya SARS-CoV-2 biboneka muri koronavirusi zisanzwe. Hanze y'umubiri w'umuntu, virusi ihitanwa n'isabune yo mu rugo, ikambura ubwirinzi bwayo. SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano rya bugufi na SARS-CoV y'umwimerere.
Birashoboka ko iyi virusi ari iyo mu nyamaswa.
Isesengura ry'imiterere y'umubiri rigaragaza ko coronavirus ari ubwoko bw'ubwoko bwa betacoronaviruses, subfamily ya serbecoviruses (clan B), hamwe na genotype ebyiri z'inzoka zikomoka ku nguge.
Iyi virusi ifite ibice 96% by'izindi virusi za koronavirusi zo mu bwoko bw'inguge (BatCov RaTG13) ku rwego rwa genome.
Muri Gashyantare 2020, abashakashatsi bo mu Bushinwa bavumbuye ko hari itandukaniro ry'amoko ya amino acide mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'inkomoko ya genome hagati y'indwara zo mu bwoko bwa pangolin n'izindi zo mu bwoko bw'abantu.
Mu kugereranya ingirabuzimafatizo zose kugeza ubu, habonetse ko ingirabuzimafatizo rusange hagati ya virusi ya pangolin na SARS-CoV-2 zigera kuri 92%, ibyo bikaba bidakwiye kugira ngo ingirabuzimafatizo z'ingingo z'ingirabuzima zijye hagati.
Kurwara virusi bishobora kugenzurwa by'agateganyo hashingiwe ku bimenyetso, nubwo byemezwa n'ibisubizo by'ubushakashatsi bw'ubwoko bw'ibinyabutabire (rRT-PCR) cyangwa se amashusho ya CT y'ibinyabutabire byanduye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe i Wuhan bugereranya PCR na CT, bwagaragaje ko CT ari yo ifite ubushobozi bwo kugenzura neza kurusha PCR, nubwo ifite ibiranga byinshi bisa n'iby'izindi ndwara z'ubuhumekero n'izindi ndwara z'ubuhumekero.
Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, ikigo cy'Abanyamerika gishinzwe ibijyanye n'imikorere y'urumuri cyatanze inama ko "CT idakwiye gukoreshwa nk'uburyo bw'ibanze bwo gupima cyangwa gusuzuma COVID-19".
OMS yasohoye porotoke nyinshi zo gupima RNA za SARS-CoV-2, aho igice cya mbere cyasohotse ku ya 17 Mutarama.
Iki cyemezo gikoresha uburyo bw'igihe nyacyo bwo gusubiramo (Reverse Transcription Polymerase chain reaction) (rRT-PCR).
Isuzuma rishobora gukorwa ku bipimo by'umwuka cyangwa amaraso.
Ibisubizo ubusanzwe biboneka mu gihe cy'amasaha cyangwa iminsi mike.
Ubusanzwe, ibizamini bikorerwa mu mazuru, ariko nanone umuntu ashobora gukoresha izuru ry'intoki. Laboratwari nyinshi n'amasosiyete arimo arakora ibizamini by'ibipimo by'amaraso bishobora kugaragaza ko umuntu afite ubwandu.
Kugeza ku ya 6 Mata 2020, nta na kimwe muri ibyo cyakozwe kigaragaza ko ari ukuri ku buryo cyemererwa gukoreshwa mu buryo bwagutse.
Ikigero cyo gupima indwara cyakozwe na Cellex muri Amerika cyemewe gusa gukoreshwa mu bihe by'impanuka na laboratwari zemewe.
Amashusho agaragaza abantu bafite ibimenyetso by'iyo ndwara mu buryo bw'amashusho yafashwe na za radiographs na za tomographie za computéoscopie (CT) harimo n'ibimenyetso by'ibura ry'ibirahuri by'ibishushanyo by'ibirahuri byo hasi, n'ibura ry'ibisebe by'umwotsi.
Ishyirahamwe ry'ubuvuzi bw'imirasire mu Butaliyani (Italian Radiological Society) riri gukora urutonde mpuzamahanga rw'amakuru y'ibyavuye mu isuzuma ry'imirasire y'imirasire y'ibinyabuzima, ku bantu bemejwe ko banduye iyo ndwara.
Kubera ko ifite ibyo ihuriyeho n'izindi ndwara nka adenovirus, ikimonyo gifite umwihariko mu kumenya COVID-19 mu buryo buciriritse, nta gihamya cyatanzwe na PCR.
Ubushakashatsi bukomeye bwakozwe mu Bushinwa, bwagereranyije ibipimo bya CT byo mu gatuza n'ibya PCR, bwerekana ko nubwo ibipimo by'isura y'ibere ari bike cyane ku ndwara, ari byihuta kandi ko byoroshye kugenzura, ibyo bikaba byerekana ko ari uburyo bwo gusuzuma indwara mu turere dutuwe n'icyorezo.
Hakozwe kandi n'ubumenyi bw'ikoranabuhanga bushingiye ku ikoranabuhanga (Artificial Knowledge-based Curved Neural Networks) mu rwego rwo kumenya imiterere y'uduhimba tw'iyo virusi hakoreshejwe uburyo bw'ikoranabuhanga (radiograph) na CT.
Uburyo bwo kwirinda kwanduza indwara, harimo kugira isuku nziza, gukaraba intoki, kwirinda gukora ku maso, izuru cyangwa umunwa intoki zidakarabye, gukorora cyangwa gusama mu matembabuzi no gushyira utwo tubyimba mu ijerekani.
Abantu bashobora kuba baranduye mbere, bagirwa inama yo kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe bari ahantu hahurira abantu benshi.
Gukurikirana intera hagati y'abantu mu rwego rwo kwirinda kwanduzanya, nabyo birasabwa. Guverinoma nyinshi zahagaritse cyangwa zasabye ko abantu bose bajya mu bihugu n'uturere twibasiwe n'icyorezo, mu gihe bitaba ngombwa.
Nyamara, virusi yageze mu cyiciro cy'ubwandu bw'abantu benshi ku isi.
Ibi bivuze ko virusi ikomeje gukwirakwira mu baturage, kandi ko bamwe mu bagize uyu muryango batazi aho bayanduye n'uko bayanduye. Abashinzwe ubuzima bita ku muntu wanduye, basabwa gukurikiza amabwiriza yo kwirinda, kwirinda guhura n'umuntu no kurinda amaso. Gukurikirana abahuye n'umuntu ni uburyo bw'ingenzi bw'abayobozi b'ubuzima bwo kumenya aho yanduye yaturutse no kwirinda ko yakwirakwira.
Gukoresha amakuru y'ahantu telefone zigera kuri buri muntu ku giti cye, byateje impungenge z'ibanga, ari na yo mpamvu Amnesty International n'indi miryango isaga 100 yasohoye itangazo rigamije gushyiraho imipaka yo kugenzura.
Hari porogaramu zitandukanye za terefone zashyizweho cyangwa zashyizweho ku bushake, kandi kugeza ku ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda y'inzobere arenga icumi yakoraga ku bikemura ibibazo by'ibanga, nko gukoresha Bluetooth kugira ngo umukozi amenye aho ari hafi n'izindi telefoni.
Abakoresha uru rubuga bahabwa ubutumwa mu gihe baba bari hafi y'umuntu wafashwe na COVID-19. Hari imyumvire itari yo ku buryo bwo kwirinda ubwandu; urugero nko gukorora amazuru no gukaraba mu kanwa ntibikora.
Nta rukingo rwa COVID-19 ruraboneka, nubwo hari imiryango myinshi irimo gukora ku buryo haboneka urukingo.
Gukaraba intoki ni ingenzi mu kwirinda ko indwara zikwirakwira.
CDC isaba abantu gukaraba intoki kenshi n'isabune n'amazi mu gihe cy'amasegonda 20, cyane cyane nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero cyangwa igihe intoki zisa n'izanduye; mbere yo kurya; na nyuma yo kwitsamura, gukorora cyangwa kwitsamura.
Ibyo biterwa n'uko iyo virusi ivuye mu mubiri w'umuntu, iba yaciwe n'imiti y'isabune yo mu rugo, igaca mu mwuka wayo uyirinda.
CDC kandi yongeyeho ko hakwiriye gukoreshwa imiti isukura intoki irimo nibura 60% bya alcool mu gihe amazi n'isabune bitagaragara.
OMS iragira abantu inama yo kwirinda gukora ku maso, ku mazuru cyangwa ku munwa n'amaboko yabo adahanaguwe.
Ubuso bushobora guterwa umuti w'imyanda myinshi, harimo 6271% bya ethanol, 50100% bya isopropanol, 0.1% bya sodium hypochlorite, 0.5% bya hydrogen peroxide, na 0.27.5% bya povidone-iodine (mu minota imwe gusa yo kwanduza umuti w'imyanda ku gice cy'icyuma kidakora).
Izindi miti, nka benzalkonium chloride na crohexidine gluconate, ntizikora cyane.
CDC isaba ko mu gihe hari icyorezo cya COVID gikekwa cyangwa cyemejwe mu biro cyangwa ahantu runaka nko mu kigo nderabuzima, ahantu hose nko mu biro, mu bwiherero, ahantu hahurira abantu benshi, ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki bakoresha nk'ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki bakoresha, nk'utwuma dufata amajwi, udukingirizo, amakarita, ibyuma bikoresha amafaranga, na ATM zikoreshwa n'abantu barwaye, bigomba gukurwa mu buryo bw'imiti.
Amashyirahamwe y'ubuzima asaba abantu gukorora no kwitsamura bakagaragaza ko bakorora cyangwa bagakosora mu kanwa no mu mazuru bakoresheje inkokora cyangwa agafuka, hanyuma bagakuramo ako gakingirizo ako ari ko kose.
Imyenda yo mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi ni ingirakamaro ku bantu bashobora kwandura, kubera ko kwambara imyenda bishobora kugabanya umubare w'amatembabuzi aturuka mu mwuka wanduye, kandi bigatuma habaho intera yo kugabanya, ndetse n'umubare w'amatembabuzi aturuka mu mwuka wanduye, ashobora gukwirakwira mu gihe umuntu avuze, asuzuma cyangwa akoroye.
OMS yashyizeho amabwiriza agaragaza igihe n'uburyo umuntu agomba gukoresha udupfukamunwa.
Stephen Griffin, umuhanga mu by'ibyorezo by'indwara zo mu mutwe muri Kaminuza ya Leeds, yagize ati "kwambara udupfukamunwa bishobora kugabanya abantu gukora ku maso, isoko y'ubwandu rikomeye, iyo batagize isuku nziza y'intoki". Gukoresha udupfukamunwa byasabwe n'abita ku muntu urwaye.
OMS isaba abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza kwambara agapfukamunwa gusa mu gihe bari mu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura, urugero nk'abafite COVID-19, ariko kandi yemeza ko kwambara agapfukamunwa bishobora gufasha abantu kwirinda gukora ku maso.
Ibihugu byinshi byatangiye gushishikariza abantu gukoresha udupfukamunwa.
Muri Amerika, CDC isaba ko abantu bambara udupfukamunwa tw'ibanze dukoreshwa mu buvuzi, ariko udupfukamunwa tw'ibanze tw'ibanze dukoreshwa mu buvuzi, ni imyenda. Ubushinwa bwasabye ko abantu bose bafite ubuzima bwiza bakoresha udupfukamunwa tw'ibanze, cyane cyane iyo bari kumwe n'abandi bantu (1 metero (3 amaguru) cyangwa munsi yayo).
Hong Kong irasaba ko mu gihe uri mu modoka rusange cyangwa ahantu hari abantu benshi, ugomba kwambara agapfukamunwa.
Abategetsi bo mu nzego z'ubuzima muri Thailand barimo batera abantu inkunga yo gukora udupfukamunwa tw'imyenda mu ngo zabo kandi bakajya babyoza buri munsi.
Repubulika ya Czech na Slovakia zabujije abantu kujya mu ruhame batambaye udupfukamunwa cyangwa batitwikiriye izuru n'amaso.
Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Vietnam yasabye abantu bose kwambara udupfukamunwa mu maso igihe bari mu duce rusange kugira ngo birinde bo ubwabo ndetse n'abandi.
Leta ya Otirishiya yasabye abantu bose binjira mu iduka rya kijyambere kwambara agapfukamunwa.
Isiraheli yasabye abaturage bose kwambara agapfukamunwa mu gihe bari mu ruhame.
Kuva mu kwezi kwa gatatu, Taiwan, ihanga ry'amasakoshi angana na miriyoni icumi ku munsi, ku itariki ya 1 Mata, yasabye abagenzi kwambara agapfukamunwa mu magare no mu bisi.
Panama yasabye ko abantu bambara agapfukamunwa igihe bari hanze, ndetse inasaba ko abantu badashobora kugura agapfukamunwa bakagakorera mu rugo.
Ipfuka zo mu maso zakoreshejwe cyane mu Buyapani, Koreya y'Epfo, Maleziya na Singapuru.
Gukurikirana mu buryo bwa rusange (n'ubundi bita gutandukana ku mubiri) bikubiyemo ibikorwa byo kwirinda ubwandu, bigamije kugabanya ubwandu bw'indwara binyuze mu kugabanya imikoranire ya bugufi hagati y'abantu.
Bimwe mu byo bakora harimo gushyira abantu mu kato, guhagarika ingendo, gufunga amashuri, aho bakorera, za sitade, za sitade z'imikino, cyangwa amaduka.
Abantu bashobora gushyira mu bikorwa uburyo bwo kwirinda mu mibanire yabo baguma mu rugo, bagahagarika ingendo, bakirinda kujya mu duce dutuwe n'abantu benshi, bakoresha uburyo bwo guhana mu buryo bw'ibanga, kandi bakirinda kwegerana n'abandi.
Ubu leta nyinshi zirimo gushyiraho amabwiriza cyangwa zisaba ko abantu bakwirinda kwegerana mu gihe bari mu duce twibasiwe n'icyorezo.
Mu rwego rwo kugabanya umubare w'abantu benshi batemerewe kujya mu mihango, umubare w'abantu bari mu mihango wagabanyijwe ku buryo bwihuse, aho abayobozi ba Leta zunze ubumwe za Amerika n'imiryango y'ubuzima bari batanze amabwiriza yo kugabanya umubare w'abantu batemerewe kujya mu mihango, bakava ku bantu 250 (niba nta bwandu bwa COVID-19 buzwi mu gace runaka) bagera kuri 50, nyuma baza kugabanya umubare w'abantu 10.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe 2020, u Budage bwahagaritse imikoranire y'abantu benshi irenga babiri. Abantu bageze mu za bukuru n'abafite ibibazo by'ubuvuzi nka diyabete, indwara z'umutima, indwara z'ubuhumekero, umuvuduko w'amaraso, n'abasirikare b'umubiri bafite ubwirinzi buke bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara zikomeye no kugira ibibazo kandi bagirwa inama na CDC yo kuguma mu rugo uko bishoboka kose mu duce turimo icyorezo cyugarije abantu benshi. Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, OMS n'izindi nzego z'ubuzima zatangiye guhindura ikoreshwa ry'ijambo "gusiga intera" rikisimbuza "kwirinda, kugira ngo bisobanuke neza ko intego y'imikoranire ari ukugabanya imbonankubone cyangwa gukabura mu buryo bw'umubiri.
Gukoresha ijambo "gukurana intera" byumvikanisha ko abantu bagomba kwirinda kugirana imibonano mpuzabitsina burundu, aho gushishikariza abantu kugirana imishyikirano n'abandi bakoresheje ubundi buryo. Hari inzego zimwe na zimwe zashyizeho amabwiriza ajyanye n'ubuzima bw'imyororokere mu gihe cy'icyorezo.
Harimo inama z'uko wakorana imibonano mpuzabitsina n'umuntu mubana gusa udafite virusi cyangwa ibimenyetso byayo.
Abantu basuzumwe COVID-19 ndetse n'abandi bakekwaho kuba baranduye, basabwe kwicungira mu rugo.
Inzego z'ubuzima zatanze amabwiriza arambuye yo kwitarura abantu mu buryo buboneye. Guverinoma nyinshi zashyizeho amabwiriza yo kwitarura abantu bose mu duce twibasiwe n'icyorezo.
Amategeko akomeye yo kwishyira mu kato yashyizweho mu matsinda y'abantu bafite ibyago byinshi.
Abantu bashobora kuba barahuye n'umuntu wanduye COVID-19 ndetse n'abaheruka kujya mu gihugu cyangwa akarere kanduye, bagirwa inama yo kwishyira mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 uhereye igihe baherukaga kwandura.
Uburyo bwo guhashya icyorezo ni ukucyirinda, cyangwa kucyirinda, no kucyirinda.
Gukingira indwara mu gihe cy'icyorezo ni igikorwa cyo gupima abantu banduye no gushyiraho izindi ngamba zo kurwanya ubwandu no kubakingira kugira ngo indwara itagera ku bandi bantu.
Iyo bidashoboka guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'indwara, ingamba zo kuyirinda zirakorwa: hashyirwaho ingamba zo kugabanya ikwirakwira ryayo no kugabanya ingaruka zayo ku nzego z'ubuzima no ku muryango.
Gukoresha uburyo bubiri bwo guhagarika no kugabanya ububabare bishobora gukorwa icyarimwe.
Gukumira bisaba ingamba zikomeye, kugirango umubare w'ababyeyi ba mbere ba mbere bagabanuke na 1. Igice cyo guhangana n'icyorezo cy'indwara zandura ni ukugerageza kugabanya igihe cy'icyorezo, cyitwa kugabanya icyorezo.
Ibyo bigabanya ibyago byo kuremereza serivisi z'ubuzima, kandi bigatanga igihe gihagije cyo gukora inkingo n'imiti.
Mu ngamba zidafite aho zihuriye n'imiti zishobora gukemura iki cyorezo harimo ingamba zo kwirinda buri wese ku giti cye, nko kwirinda umwanda, kwambara udupfukamunwa no kwishyira mu kato; ingamba zo mu rwego rw'abaturage, nko gufunga amashuri no guhagarika guteranira hamwe; ingamba zo mu rwego rw'abaturage, kugira ngo abantu bemere kandi bitabire izo ngamba; ingamba z'ibidukikije, nko gusukura imbuga. Mu Bushinwa, ingamba zikarishye zo kwirinda iki cyorezo, zashyizweho mu gihe hari ibimenyetso by'uko iki cyorezo giteye, nko gushyira mu kato imijyi yose no guhagarika ingendo.
Ibindi bihugu na byo byashyizeho ingamba zigamije kugabanya ikwirakwizwa ry'iyi virusi.
Koreya y'Epfo yatangije iperereza ku bantu benshi no gushyira mu kato abantu bo mu gace runaka, kandi itanga imiburo ku gutambuka kw'abanduye.
Singapore yatanze inkunga y'amafaranga ku bantu banduye bakomeje kwishyira mu kato, kandi ihana bikomeye abatarabishoboye.
Taïwan yongereye umubare w'udupfukamunwa ikora ndetse inashyiraho ibihano ku bantu babika ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi. Ingero z'u Bwongereza na Amerika zigaragaza ko guhangana n'icyorezo (gukomeza icyorezo ariko ntikigabanuke) no kugihashya (guhindura icyorezo) ari imbogamizi zikomeye.
Imigambi yo kurwanya indwara ishobora kugabanya umubare w'abantu bivuza cyane ku kigero cya 2/3 n'umubare w'abapfa ukagabanukaho kimwe cya kabiri, ariko na nyuma y'ibyo, abantu babarirwa mu magana baracyapfa, kandi gahunda z'ubuvuzi zigenda zikendera.
Guhashya bishobora kuba ikintu cy'ibanze, ariko bigomba gukomeza igihe cyose virusi ikomeje gukwirakwira mu bantu (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rubonetse, niba ari mbere), bitaba ibyo, guhora mu ngamba bishobora gutuma ubwandu bwiyongera.
Gukumira icyorezo mu gihe kirekire bigira ingaruka ku mibereho y'abantu no ku bukungu.
Nta miti ya virusi itera COVID-19 yemewe, ariko hari ibikorwa byo kuyikuraho birimo gukorwa, harimo no gupima imiti ihari.
Kunywa imiti yo kwivura ibicurane, kunywa amazi no kuruhuka bishobora kugufasha kugabanya ibimenyetso.
Bitewe n'uburemere bw'iki cyorezo, umuntu ashobora gukenera imiti ya oxygene, imiti yo mu maraso no gufasha guhumeka.
Iyo umuntu afashe imiti ya 'steroid' bishobora kumugiraho ingaruka mbi kurushaho.
Hari imiti myinshi yamaze kwemezwa ko ishobora kuvura izindi ndwara z'ibyorezo irimo gusuzumwa kugira ngo ikoreshwe mu kuvura COVID-19.
OMS ivuga ko hari "imiti gakondo n'imiti yo mu rugo" ishobora koroshya ibimenyetso by'indwara ya SARS-CoV-19.
WHO ivuga ko kongera ubushobozi no guhuza ibikorwa by'ubuvuzi n'ibyo abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye, ari ingamba z'ingenzi zo guhangana n'icyorezo.
ECDC n'ibiro by'akarere ka OMS by'i Burayi byatanze amabwiriza yo kwimura umutungo ku bitaro no ku bigo by'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze mu byiciro byinshi, birimo: gushyira imbaraga mu gupima COVID-19, guhagarika ibikorwa by'isiganwa igihe cyose bishoboka, gushyira mu kato no mu kato abarwayi banduye COVID-19, kongera ubushobozi bwo kwita ku barwayi cyane cyane binyuze mu gutoza abakozi no kongera umubare w'amazu yo kwifashisha n'ibyumba by'indembe.
Hari ibitekerezo byinshi ku birebana n'aho umuntu wa mbere wanduye (uwitwa Patient Zero) ashobora kuba yaraturutse.
Umuntu wa mbere uzwiho kuba afite coronavirus nshya yamenyekanye ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 mu mujyi wa Wuhan, muri leta ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Mu gihe cy'ukwezi kumwe, umubare w'abanduye icyorezo cya koronavirusi muri Hubei wakomeje kwiyongera.
Abenshi muri bo bari bafite aho bahuriye n'isoko rinini ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Hunan, aho bagurishaga inyamaswa, kandi hari abavuga ko virusi yaturutse ku nyamaswa nk'izo; cyangwa se ko ifite inkomoko ku nyamaswa. Itsinda ry'indwara y'umwijima y'impamvu idatangajwe ryatahuwe ku ya 26 Ukuboza, rivurwa n'umuganga witwa Jiang Jixian wo mu bitaro by'intara bya Hubei, ari na we wabimenyesheje CDC y'i Wuhan ku ya 27 Ukuboza.
Ku ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan baburiye bagenzi babo ku bijyanye n'ubwandu bwa "Coronavirus imeze nka SARS".
Abaganga umunani, barimo na Li Wenliang, bahawe imiburo na polisi ko bakwirakwije ibihuha, undi muganga witwa Yi Feng nawe ahanwa n'abo bakoranaga.
Nyuma yaho, ku ya 31 Ukuboza, Komisiyo y'Umujyi wa Wuhan ishinzwe ubuzima yasohoye itangazo rusange maze imenyesha OMS.
Mu ntangiriro z'iki cyorezo, umubare w'abanduye iki cyorezo wariyongereye cyane, ku buryo mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa mbere, umubare w'abanduye iki cyorezo wiyongeraga kabiri mu minsi irindwi n'igice.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati mu kwezi kwa Mutarama 2020, virusi yageze mu zindi ntara zo mu Bushinwa, kubera ko mu Bushinwa umwaka mushya watumye habaho urujya n'uruza rw'abantu, kandi Wuhan ikaba ari ihuriro ry'ubwikorezi n'ihuriro ry'imihanda ya gari ya moshi.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwatanze raporo y'abantu bashya bagera ku 140 banduye mu munsi umwe, barimo babiri i Beijing n'undi umwe muri Shenzhen.
Kugeza ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020, imibare yemewe igaragaza ko abantu 6,174 bari bamaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso. Kugeza ku ya 26 Werurwe, Amerika yarushije Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani kugira umubare munini w'abamaze kwandura ku isi.
Hari nibura umuntu umwe gusa mu bihugu bigera kuri 200 no mu turere.
Kubera icyorezo kiri mu Burayi, ibihugu byinshi byo mu karere ka Schengen byafashe ingamba zo guhagarika urujya n'uruza rw'abantu no gushyiraho uburyo bwo kugenzura imipaka.
Mu buryo bw'igihugu, hakozwe ingamba zo kwirinda nk'akato (kwirinda kuguma mu rugo, kwishyiriraho aho umuntu aba, cyangwa gufunga), hamwe n'amasaha ya guma mu rugo. Ku ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 300 muri Amerika, cyangwa hafi 90% by'abaturage, bari mu buryo runaka bwa guma mu rugo, abantu barenga miliyoni 50 muri Filipine bari muri Guma mu rugo, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 59 muri Afurika y'Epfo bari mu kato, naho mu Buhinde hari abantu bagera kuri miliyari 1.3.
Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, abantu bagera kuri miliyari 1.7 ku isi bari mu bihe by'ingamba za guma mu rugo, nyuma y'iminsi ibiri bariyongereye bagera kuri miliyari 2.6 - ni ukuvuga hafi kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wanduye COVID-19 yagaragaye i Wuhan ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019; raporo itagenzuwe igaragaza ko umuntu wa mbere wanduye yagaragaye ku ya 17 Ugushyingo 2019.
Muganga Zhang Jixian yabonye itsinda ry'abantu barwaye nimoniya ku itariki 26 Ukuboza bafite impamvu zitazwi, nyuma y'aho ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza ibitaro yabagamo byabimenyesheje Wuhan Jiangnan CDC.
Ku ya 27 Ukuboza 2019, ibizamini by'ibanze by'imiterere y'ibipimo by'umurwayi byerekanye ko hari coronavirus imeze nka SARS.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza, Komisiyo y'Ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan yatanze itangazo rusange.
OMS yahawe amakuru kuri uwo munsi.
Nyuma y'iyi nkuru, abapolisi bo muri Wuhan bahise baburira abaganga "kujya bakwirakwiza ibihuha" ku byerekeye iki cyorezo.
Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima mu Bushinwa yari yabanje kuvuga ko nta "bihamya bifatika" by'ikwirakwizwa ry'iyo virusi mu bantu.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, leta y'Ubushinwa yatangiye ubukangurambaga bukomeye bwo guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi, byiswe "Intambara y'abaturage" n'umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'Abashinwa, Xi Jinping.
Mu cyiswe "gereza nini mu mateka y'abantu", ku ya 23 Mutarama, hatangajwe ko akarere ka Wuhan kagomba gufunga abantu, kagabanywa kugera mu mijyi 15 yo mu ntara ya Hubei, aho abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 57 bari mu kato.
Gukoresha imodoka bwite byari byarabujijwe muri uwo mujyi.
Ibirori byo kwizihiza umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa (Nyakanga 25) byakuweho mu duce twinshi.
Abayobozi kandi batangaje ko hagiye kubakwa ibitaro by'agateganyo, Howsenson Hospital, byubatswe mu minsi 10.
Nyuma yaho, hari irindi bitaro ryitwa Lycensens Hospital ryubatswe kugira ngo ryiteho abarwayi benshi.
Usibye ibitaro bishya, Ubushinwa bwahinduye ibindi bigo 14 mu mujyi wa Wuhan, birimo amazu y'amakoraniro n'ibibuga, bihinduka ibitaro by'agateganyo. Ku ya 26 Mutarama, leta yashyizeho izindi ngamba zo gukumira icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo gutanga imenyesha ryerekeye ubuzima ku bagenzi no kongera ikiruhuko cy'umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi.
Kaminuza n'amashuri mu gihugu hose na byo byari byarafunzwe.
Intara ya Hong Kong na Macau zashyizeho ingamba nyinshi, cyane cyane mu bijyanye n'amashuri na za kaminuza.
Mu duce twinshi tw'Ubushinwa, hashyizweho uburyo bwo gukorera mu birometero byinshi.
Mu gihe cya nyuma, ingendo mu mujyi wa Hubei no hanze yawo byari byarahagaritswe.
Ingendo mu modoka zahagaritswe, kandi ingoro z'ibyaremwe mu Bushinwa hose zifunze by'agateganyo.
Imijyi myinshi yashyizeho ingamba zo guhagarika urujya n'uruza rw'abantu, kandi byagiye bigereranywa ko abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 760 (abasaga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage) bahanganye n'ingamba zo gufunga imiryango. Nyuma y'uko iki cyorezo kigera ku rwego rw'isi muri Werurwe, abayobozi b'u Bushinwa bafashe ingamba zikomeye zo gukumira ko virusi "injira" mu bindi bihugu.
Urugero, Beijing yashyizeho gahunda yo gushyira mu kato abinjira mu mujyi bose mu minsi 14. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, mu minsi itanu ishize mu Bushinwa, hari umuntu umwe gusa wanduye mu gihugu, muri iki gihe ni umugenzi wavuye muri Istanbul agaruka i Guangzhou.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'u Bushinwa, Li Keqiang, yatangaje ko icyorezo cy'indwara z'ubwandu bw'ibyorezo byandurira mu gihugu imbere cyahagaritswe, kandi ko icyorezo cyamaze kugenzurwa mu Bushinwa.
Nyuma y'amezi abiri hashyizweho gahunda yo guhagarika ingendo, muri uwo munsi, mu mujyi wa Wuhan na Hubei, ingendo zari zarabujijwe. Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'u Bushinwa yatangaje ko kwinjira kw'abafite viza cyangwa uruhushya rwo gutura bizasubikwa guhera ku ya 28 Werurwe, nta makuru y'umwihariko atanga ku gihe iryo tegeko rizarangirira.
Abantu bashaka kwinjira mu Bushinwa bagomba gusaba viza muri ambasade cyangwa konsili z'u Bushinwa.
Guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yashishikarije ubucuruzi n'inganda kongera gufungura kuri 30 Werurwe, ndetse inatanga inkunga y'ubukungu ku bucuruzi. Inama ya Leta yatangaje umunsi w'icyunamo ku ya 4 Mata, itangira saa 10:00 z'ijoro, hakorwa iminota itatu yo guceceka ku rwego rw'igihugu, mu gihe cy'umunsi mukuru wa Qingming, nubwo Guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yasabye imiryango gukurikiza gahunda yo kwirinda mu buryo bw'umubiri, no kujya mu mihango y'icyunamo kuri interineti kugira ngo birinde icyorezo gishya cya COVID-19.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyemejwe ko cyaturutse mu Bushinwa kigera muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima cyatangaje ko umubare w'abamaze kwandura iki cyorezo wiyongereye cyane ku ya 20 Gashyantare, bitewe ahanini n'imbaga y'abantu benshi bari mu idini rishya ryitwa Shincheonji Church of Jesus.
Abashinjacyaha ba Shinchyo, abantu baturukaga i Wuhan bakaza i Daigu, bakekwaho kuba ari bo bari bafite uruhare muri iki cyorezo.
Kugeza ku ya 22 Gashyantare, abantu 1,261 cyangwa hafi 13% by'abayoboke 9,336 b'iri torero batanze ibimenyetso. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko yabonye icyorezo cyo ku rwego rwo hejuru ku ya 23 Gashyantare 2020.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, Koreya yageze ku barwayi b'indwara z'icyorezo barenga 2,000, kuri 29 Gashyantare bari bamaze kugera ku 3,150.
Inzego zose za gisirikare za Koreya y'Epfo zahawe akato nyuma y'uko ibizamini byemeza ko abasirikare batatu banduye virusi.
Porogaramu ya Koreya y'Epfo, yagaragaye ko ari yo gahunda nini kandi nziza ku isi yo gupima abaturage virusi no gushyira mu kato abantu bayanduye, ndetse no kumenya no gushyira mu kato abahuye nabo.
Uburyo bwo gupima bwari bukubiyemo ko abamaze kugera mu mahanga bashyiraho uburyo bwo kwipimisha ibimenyetso bakoresheje porogaramu za telefoni, gupima vuba bakamenya ko banduye uwo mugera, kandi bakabona ibisubizo mu munsi ukurikira, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu 20,000 ku munsi.
Porogaramu yo muri Koreya y'Epfo ifatwa nk'intsinzi mu guhashya icyorezo nubwo imijyi yose itarashyirwamo inganda.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zisaba ko Moon ashyigikirwa mu gihe bavuga ko leta yayobotse nabi iki cyorezo, cyangwa bashimagiza uburyo yakiriye.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Koreya y'Epfo ari yo ifite umubare muto w'abanduye mu minsi ine mu byumweru bine.
Ku ya 29 Werurwe, byamenyeshejwe ko guhera ku ya 1 Mata, abavuye mu bindi bihugu bose bazajya bashyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Nkuko byatangajwe n'itangazamakuru ku ya 1 Mata, Koreya y'Epfo yakiriye ubusabe bw'imfashanyo mu gupima virusi ivuye mu bihugu 121.
Iran yatangaje ko abantu bayo ba mbere bemejwe ko banduye SARS-CoV-2 muri Qom ku ya 19 Gashyantare, aho abantu babiri bapfuye nyuma y'uwo munsi, nk'uko byatangajwe na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi.
Mu ngamba za mbere leta yatangaje harimo gufunga ibiterane by'ibitaramo n'ibindi bikorwa by'umuco, imikino, amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu, n'amashuri makuru, amashuri makuru n'amashuri.
Irani yashyizeho miriyari eshanu z'amanyarwanda zo kurwanya virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani ku wa 26 Gashyantare 2020 yavuze ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato ibice byibasiwe n'iki cyorezo kandi ko abantu ari bo bonyine bazajya bashyirwa mu kato.
Gahunda yo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imijyi yatangajwe muri Werurwe, nubwo ingendo hagati y'imijyi yakomeje kwiyongera mbere y'uko Pasika igera.
Kugeza ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020, insengero za Shia mu mujyi wa Qom zari zifunguye ku basenga. Muri Gashyantare, Iran yabaye ihuriro ry'ubwandu bw'icyorezo cya virusi nyuma y'Ubushinwa.
Mu gihe hari hari abiyemeza ko Iran ihishe umubare w'abanduye, ibihugu birenga icumi byabonye ko hari isano hagati y'ibiri muri ibyo bihugu na Irani kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare, bikaba bigaragaza ko umubare w'abanduye ushobora kuba ari munini cyane ugereranyije n'abantu 388 leta ya Irani yari imaze kubona kuri uwo munsi.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yafunzwe nyuma y'uko ku ya 3 Werurwe, 23 mu bayigize 290 bapimweho virusi.
Ku itariki ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch yasabye abayobozi ba gereza za Irani kurekura ku gahato abarwanashyaka b'uburenganzira bwa muntu bafunzwe bazira kwigaragambya mu mahoro, ndetse bakanarekura by'agateganyo imfungwa zose zikwiriye.
Rwavuze ko ibigo bifunze, nk'ibigo by'ubutabazi, bifite ibyago byinshi byo gukwirakwiza virusi, kandi ko bidafite ubuvuzi buhagije.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye ku munsi umwe, umubare munini w'abantu bapfuye mu gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe, nibura hari abanyapolitiki n'abakozi ba leta 12 bariho cyangwa bahoze muri iki gihugu, bari baranduwe n'iyi ndwara.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, muri Irani, abantu bashya 50 bagaragaye buri saha, kandi umuntu umwe yahitanwe na coronavirus buri minota icumi.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umukozi wa WHO, Iran ishobora kuba ifite umubare w'abanduye wikubye inshuro eshanu umubare w'abarizwayo.
Hari n'abavuga ko ibihano Amerika yafatiye Irani bishobora kuba byaratumye igihugu kidashobora guhangana n'icyorezo cya virusi.
Umukuru w'umuryango w'abibumbye ushinzwe uburenganzira bwa muntu yasabye ko ibihugu byazahajwe cyane n'icyorezo harimo na Irani, byoroherezwa mu byemezo by'ubukungu.
Icyorezo cyemejwe ko cyatangiriye mu Butaliyani ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubwo abakerarugendo babiri b'Abashinwa bari i Roma bagaragazaga ko banduye SARS-CoV-2.
