Guhera ku barwayi 16 bemejwe ko banduye COVID-19 muri Lombardy ku ya 21 Gashyantare, havumbuwe abantu benshi batari bahuye. Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, Inama y'Abaminisitiri yatangaje itegeko rishya rigenga ubutabera rigamije gukumira iki cyorezo, aho abantu barenga 50,000 bari mu kato baturutse mu mijyi 11 itandukanye yo mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani.
Minisitiri w'Intebe, Giuseppe Conte, yagize ati "Mu turere turimo ubwandu, kwinjira no gusohoka ntibizaba bihawe.
Ku ya 4 Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yategetse ko amashuri yose na za kaminuza mu gihugu hose zifungwa burundu, nyuma y'uko mu Butaliyani hishwe abantu 100.
Byari biteganyijwe ko imikino yose ikomeye, harimo n'umupira w'amaguru wa Serie A, izaba ikinwa nta bantu bayirebye kugeza muri Mata, ariko ku ya 9 Werurwe, imikino yose yasubitswe burundu mu gihe cy'ukwezi.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Conte yategetse ko ibikorwa byose by'ubucuruzi bihagarikwa, uretse ibicuruzwa by'ubucuruzi no mu mafarumasi. Ku ya 6 Werurwe, Ikigo cy'Ubutaliyani cy'Ibigo by'Ubuvuzi, Ububabare, Ubuvuzi n'Ubuvuzi Bukomeye (SIAARTI) cyasohoye amabwiriza y'umuco mu by'ubuvuzi, ku bijyanye n'uburyo bwo kugenzura abarwayi barembye bashobora kwivuza.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe, u Butaliyani bwatsinze u Bushinwa mu bantu benshi cyane bapfuye bazize Coronavirus ku isi, nyuma yo gutangaza ko abantu 3,405 bishwe n'icyorezo.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Uburusiya bwohereje mu Butaliyani indege icyenda z'intambara zirimo ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Kugeza ku ya 5 Mata, mu Butaliyani hari abantu 128,948 bamaze kwandura, 15,887 barapfa naho 21,815 barakira, mu gihe abenshi muri bo bari mu karere ka Lombardy.
Raporo ya CNN yagaragaje ko kuba mu Butaliyani hari abantu bageze mu za bukuru benshi kandi bakaba batari bashoboye gupima abantu bari bafite virusi, bishobora kuba ari byo byatumye umubare w'abapfa ugabanuka.
Ubwongereza ni cyo gihugu cya mbere cyakiriye virusi itera SIDA mu buryo buciriritse kurusha ibindi byose, kandi kugeza ku ya 18 Werurwe 2020, leta y'Ubwongereza ntiyari yarashyizeho ingamba zo gukumira abantu kugendera kure cyangwa kwirinda kwegereza abandi.
Byatumye guverinoma inengwa ko itagira umuvuduko n'imbaraga mu guhangana n'impungenge abaturage bahura nazo. Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yagiriye inama abantu kwirinda ingendo n'imiyoborere idakenewe, abantu bagasabwa gukorera mu rugo aho bishoboka, no kwirinda kujya ahantu hahurira abantu benshi, nko mu tubari, muri resitora no mu tubyiniro.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, leta yatangaje ko ibigo by'imyidagaduro byose, nk'utubyi n'amazu y'imikino, bigomba gufungwa vuba bishoboka, kandi isezeranya ko izishyura abakozi 80% by'umushahara wabo, ku giciro cy'amapawundi 2,500 ku kwezi, kugira ngo hirindwe ubushomeri mu bihe by'amakuba. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe yatangaje ingamba zo gushyiraho ihanahanahana rigari, harimo no kubuza abantu guterana ari benshi, no kugabanya ingendo n'ibikorwa byo hanze ku bikorwa by'ingenzi.
Mu buryo butandukanye n'uko byari bimeze mbere, ayo mategeko yashyirwagaho hakoreshejwe amande ya polisi n'uburyo bwo gukwirakwiza imbaga.
Ubucuruzi hafi ya bwose bwasabwe gufunga, uretse ubucuruzi "bw'ingenzi" burimo supermarket, farumasi, banki, amaduka y'ibyuma, za sitasiyo za peteroli na gare.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, umurwayi wa mbere uzwi wa COVID-19 wemejwe muri leta ya Washington mu majyaruguru ashyira inyanja ya Pacific, yanduye umuntu wari wavuye i Wuhan ku ya 15 Mutarama.
Itsinda ry'abashinzwe kurwanya icyorezo cya Coronavirus ryo mu biro by'Umukuru w'Igihugu (White House Coronavirus Task Force) ryashyizweho ku ya 29 Mutarama.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubuyobozi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko ari ikibazo cy'ubuzima bw'abaturage, kandi buhagarika ingendo z'abinjira mu gihugu bavuye mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020, ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara - ari na cyo kigo cya mbere muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe ubuzima - cyatangaje ko cyatangije ibikoresho byacyo by'ubushakashatsi.
Nubwo Amerika yabigenje ityo, yatangiye igerageza buhoro, bituma bigorana kumenya ubukana nyakuri bw'icyorezo icyo gihe.
Gupima byasuzumwe n'ibikoresho by'ubushakashatsi byatewe n'ibyaha byakozwe na leta muri Gashyantare, kubura kwemerwa na leta y'u Rwanda mu gikoresho cy'ubushakashatsi cyakozwe n'abatabifitiye uburenganzira (abashakashatsi, ibigo n'ibitaro) kugeza mu mpera za Gashyantare, ndetse n'amabwiriza y'abantu bagomba kuba bafite ibyangombwa by'ubushakashatsi (nyuma yo guhabwa icyemezo n'umuganga) kugeza mu ntangiriro za Werurwe.
Kugeza ku ya 27 Gashyantare, The Washington Post yatangaje ko hari abageragezwa batarenga 4,000 muri Amerika.
Kugeza ku ya 13 Werurwe, ikinyamakuru The Atlantic cyavuze ko hari abantu batageze ku 14,000 bamaze gukorerwa ibizamini.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, The Associated Press yagize iti "abantu benshi bafite ibimenyetso kandi bafite imiti ya muganga, bategereje amasaha cyangwa iminsi kugira ngo bapimwe". Guverineri Jay Inslee yatangaje ko igihugu kiri mu bihe bidasanzwe nyuma y'uko muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika hatangajwe ko umuntu wa mbere yishwe muri Leta ya Washington ku ya 29 Gashyantare, igikorwa cyahise gikurikirwa n'ibindi bihugu.
Amashuri yo mu karere ka Seattle yahagaritse amasomo ku ya 3 Werurwe, kandi kugeza mu kwezi kwa Werurwe hagati, amashuri mu gihugu hose yari yarafunzwe. Ku ya 6 Werurwe 2020, Amerika yagiriwe inama n'itsinda ry'inzobere mu by'indwara z'ibyorezo muri kaminuza ya Imperial College London ku bijyanye n'ingaruka z'icyorezo cya coronavirus ku gihugu.
Kuri uwo munsi, Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko rigena imisanzu y'inyongera yo guhangana n'icyorezo cya Koronavirusi, ryatanze miliyari 8.3 z'amadolari yo mu rwego rw'ubutabazi ku bigo by'igihugu byo guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Amashyirahamwe yafashe ingamba zo kubuza abakozi gukora, yahagaritse amakoraniro kandi ashishikariza abakozi gukorera mu rugo.
Imikino n'amarushanwa byasibijwe. Ku ya 11 Werurwe, byatangiye gukurikizwa ku ya 13 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko yahagaritse ingendo mu Burayi bwose mu gihe cy'iminsi 30, usibye mu Bwongereza.
Ku munsi wakurikiyeho, yongereye ibyo bihano mu Bwongereza no muri Irilande.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje ko igihugu kiri mu bihe bidasanzwe, bituma haboneka amafaranga y'igihugu yo guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Guhera ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, ubucuruzi bwinshi bwahagaritse imirimo cyangwa bugabanya amasaha y'akazi muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, mu rwego rwo kugerageza kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi.
Kugeza ku ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyari cyemejwe mu bihugu byose 50 no mu ntara ya Columbia. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko mu mujyi wa New York hari abantu 10,700 banduye coronavirus, baruta umubare w'abanduye muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 25 Werurwe, guverineri yavuze ko guhana intera hagati y'abantu byatangiye gukora, kuko umubare w'abandura wagabanutse ukava ku minsi 2.0 ugera ku minsi 4.7.
Kugeza ku ya 28 Werurwe, umujyi wa New York wari umaze kugira abantu 32,308 bagaragaweho ko banduye, naho 672 bakaba barishwe n'iyo virusi. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Amerika yatangaje abantu benshi banduye coronavirus kurusha ikindi gihugu icyo ari cyo cyose ku isi, harimo u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Kugeza ku ya 8 Mata, Amerika yari imaze kugira abantu 400,335 banduye, naho abantu 12,841 bakaba barapfuye.
Amakuru dukesha itangazamakuru, avuga ko ku itariki ya 30 y'ukwezi kwa gatatu, Perezida Trump wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera amabwiriza yo kwirinda mu buryo bw'imibereho y'abantu kugeza ku ya 30 y'ukwezi kwa kane.
Kuri uwo munsi, ubwato bwitwa The USNS Comfort, bwari iherekeje i New York, bwari ubwato bw'ibitaro bw'ibitanda bigera ku 1000.
Ku ya 3 Mata, umubare w'abantu bapfuye bishwe na coronavirus muri Amerika wari 884 mu gihe cy'amasaha 24.
Kuri uyu wa 3 Mata, umubare w'abanduye warenze 100,000 muri leta ya New York. White House yanenzwe kuba yarapfobyaga ibyago no kuba yaragenzuraga ubutumwa butangwa n'abayobozi b'ubuzima n'abahanga mu bya siyansi, kugira ngo bahuze n'ibiro bya Visi Perezida Mike Pence mu gutangaza ibyavuye mu itangazamakuru n'ibyavuzwe n'abaturage ku bijyanye n'icyorezo.
Uburyo Trump yakoresheje mu gukemura ibibazo, mu buryo bugaragara, bwaciyemo ibice.
Bamwe mu bayobozi ba Amerika n'abanyamakuru banenze uburyo Amerika ikomeza kwishingikiriza ku Bushinwa mu kugura ibintu by'ingenzi birimo n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Igishushanyo mbonera cy'ubwiteganyirize bw'ingendo zo mu kirere gikoreshejwe mu gupima no guhanura uko indwara y'icyorezo yagaragaye, cyasohotse mu kwezi kwa mbere hagati mu mwaka wa 2020 mu kinyamakuru The Journal of Travel Medicine.
Hashingiwe ku makuru yo mu 2018 yatanzwe n'Ishyirahamwe Mpuzamahanga ry'Ingendo zo mu Kirere, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei ni byo byari bifite abagenzi benshi bavuye i Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne na byo byatangajwe ko ari byo byamamare ku bantu bava muri Wuhan.
Umujyi wa Bali ni wo wa mbere mu mijyi 20 ikunzwe cyane, mu gihe imijyi yo muri Ositaraliya yo yashyizwe ku mwanya wa mbere.
Bivuze ko nta byinshi bizwi kuri COVID-19, kandi ko Australia izashyira imbaraga mu gucunga imipaka no gutumanaho mu guhangana n'icyorezo.
Ku ya 21 Werurwe, muri Ositaraliya hatangajwe ko hadutse ikibazo cy'umutekano w'abantu.
Kubera ko mu mujyi wa Wuhan na Hubei hashyizweho gahunda yo gushyira mu kato ingendo rusange, ibihugu byinshi byateguye gahunda yo gucyura abaturage babyo n'abakozi ba dipolomasi muri utwo duce, cyane cyane hakoreshejwe ingendo z'indege z'ibihugu byabo, byemewe n'ubutegetsi bw'u Bushinwa.
Canada, Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, Ubufaransa, Argentine, Ubudage na Thailande ni byo bihugu bya mbere byatangiye gahunda yo gucyura abaturage babyo.
Pakistan yavuze ko nta muturage wayo uzaturuka mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 7 Gashyantare, Burezili yavanye abantu 34 b'Abanya-Burezili cyangwa abagize imiryango yabo, usibye abapolisi bane, Umunya-Shayina n'Umuhinde.
Abagenzi b'abapolisi bo muri Polonye, u Bushinwa n'u Buhinde, bavuye mu ndege yari ivuye muri Polonye, aho indege yari ivuye muri Brezili yari igeze i Brazil.
Aba baturage ba Brazil bari baragiye i Wuhan, bashyizwe mu kato mu kigo cya gisirikare kiri hafi ya Brasilia.
Kuri uwo munsi, abantu 215 b'Abanyakanada (176 bari mu ndege ya mbere, 39 bari mu yindi ndege yari yaragenewe Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika) bavuye i Wuhan berekezwa ahitwa CFB Trenton, bashyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege yari itwaye abaturage 185 b'Abanyakanada yahagurutse i Wuhan igera kuri CFB Trenton.
Ku itariki ya 3 na 4 Gashyantare, abategetsi ba Ositaraliya bafashe abaturage 277 babajyana mu kigo cya Christmas Island Detention Centre, cyari cyarongeye kubakwa ngo kibe ahantu ho gukingirwa, aho bamaze iminsi 14.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, indege ya New Zealand yageze muri Auckland; abagenzi bayo (harimo bamwe baturutse muri Ositaraliya no mu nyanja ya Pasifika) bari bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare cy'ingabo za Amerika i Whangaparoa, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangaje ko zigiye gucyura Abanyamerika bari mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess.
Ku ya 21 Gashyantare, indege ya Canada yageze i Trenton, Ontario irimo abantu 129 bari bavuye muri Diamond Princess.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, Guverinoma y'u Buhinde yatangiye kuvana abaturage bayo muri Irani. Ku ya 14 Werurwe, indege ya South African Airways yari ifite icyemezo cya leta y'Afurika y'Epfo, yasubijeyo abaturage 112 b'Afurika y'Epfo.
Mbere yo kugenda, abaganga barabasuzumye, kandi bane muri bo bo bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya coronavirus, basigaye inyuma kugira ngo bagabanye ibyago.
Abanyafurika y'Epfo bajyanywe gusa ni uko basuzumwe bakanga.
Ibisubizo by'igeragezwa byemeje ko nta bwandu bwabonetse muri buri wese mu banyarwanda, harimo abakoze mu butumwa bw'ubutabazi, abapilote, abakozi bo muri hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare, bose bari mu kato mu rwego rwo kwirinda, bashyizwe mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 muri The Ranch Resort.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, Amerika yatangiye gukuraho igice cy'ingabo zayo muri Iraq kubera icyorezo.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'Ubushinwa yavuze ko ibihugu 21 (harimo Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Irani) byohereje inkunga mu Bushinwa.
Bamwe mu banyeshuri b'Abashinwa bo muri kaminuza zo muri Amerika bahurije hamwe kugira ngo bafashe mu kohereza imfashanyo mu bice by'Ubushinwa byibasiwe n'iyo virusi, aho bivugwa ko itsinda ry'abibumbye mu karere ka Chicago ryohereje udupfukamunwa 50.000 twa N95 mu bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei ku ya 30 Mutarama. Ishyirahamwe ry'ubutabazi mu rwego rw'abantu Direct Relief, rifatanyije na FedEx, ryatwaye udupfukamunwa 200.000, hamwe n'ibindi bikoresho birinda abantu, birimo n'utwambaro n'imyenda, mu bitaro bya Wuhan Union mu buryo bw'ubutabazi, mu ndege yoherejwe ku ya 30 Mutarama.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko bagiye gutanga miliyoni 100 z'amadolari kuri OMS mu rwego rwo kurengera "abaturage bari mu kaga muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Amajyepfo", ndetse no gushyigikira ubushakashatsi ku rukingo no kwivuza.
Interactions yatangaje ko ku ya 6 Gashyantare, leta y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 200,000 muri Filipine, mu gihe Senateri Richard Gordon yohereje udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 i Wuhan.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Croix Rouge ya Singapour yatangaje ko izohereza u Bushinwa miliyoni $2.26 z'inkunga.
U Buyapani bwatanze udupfukamunwa miliyoni imwe muri Wuhan, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, Uburusiya bwohereje toni zirenga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Wuhan, Maleziya yatangaje ko izatanga miliyoni 18 z'udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, Ubudage bwatanze toni 10,000 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bitandukanye birimo n'imyenda ya Hazmat, ndetse na Amerika yatanze toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa ndetse n'inyongera y'inkunga y'amadolari ya miliyoni 100 mu gufasha ibihugu byugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'abahanga mu by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani kugira ngo bufashe mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya koronavirusi.
Umushoramari Jack Ma yohereje ibikoresho byo gupima miliyoni 1,1, udupfukamunwa miliyoni 6, n'imyambaro 60,000 yo kwikingira muri Addis Ababa, Ethiopia, kugira ngo bihabwe n'Umuryango wa Afurika Yunze Ubumwe.
Nyuma yo kohereza ibikoresho byo gupima 5,000, udupfukamunwa 100,000 na ventilateri 5 muri Panama.
Ma yanashyikirije Canada ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi. Ubuholandi, Esipanye, Turukiya, Jeworujiya na Repubulika ya Tchèque na byo byagaragaje impungenge ku masike n'ibikoresho byo gupima byakozwe n'Abashinwa.
Urugero, Espagne yasubijeho ibikoresho 58000 byo gupima coronavirus byakorewe mu Bushinwa bifite igipimo cyo kwipimisha 30% gusa, mu gihe u Buholandi bwo bwasabye gusubizaho udupfukamunwa 600000 tw'Abashinwa twari twarabonetse ko dufite inenge.
U Bubiligi bwagaruye udupfukamunwa 100,000 twakoreshwaga nabi twibwira ko twavuye mu Bushinwa ariko mu by'ukuri twavuye muri Kolombiya.
Ku rundi ruhande, inkunga z'u Bushinwa zagiye zikoreshwa neza mu bice bimwe na bimwe bya Amerika y'Epfo na Afurika. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije gahunda yo gutanga inkunga yihutirwa ku bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yashimye abayobozi b'u Bushinwa ku mbaraga bakoresheje mu kurwanya iki cyorezo.
OMS yagaragaje itandukaniro riri hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004, aho abategetsi b'u Bushinwa bashinjwa ubwirinzi bwatumye ingamba zo gukumira no kurwanya icyorezo zitagenda neza, n'ikibazo cy'ubu aho leta y'u Bushinwa "yahoraga itanga amakuru kugira ngo ihangane n'ubwoba mbere y'iminsi mikuru y'Ubunani".
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu gusubiza ku cyemezo cy'ubuyobozi bw'ikigo cyo gushyiraho ingendo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, Gauden Galia, uhagarariye OMS, yavuze ko nubwo "nta gushidikanya ko OMS itabyemeye", ariko ko "ari ikimenyetso gikomeye cyane cyo kwiyemeza gukumira icyorezo aho cyibasiye cyane" ndetse ko "nta kindi gihe cyabayeho mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange". Ku ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari icyorezo cy'indwara z'indwara z'ibyorezo (PHEIC) zihangayikishije amahanga yose, nyuma y'uko abantu bo mu Bushinwa bemeje ko abantu banduye abandi kandi umubare w'abanduye uzamutse, iki cyorezo cyabaye icya gatandatu cy'icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube kuva mu 2009 ubwo ibi byemezo byafashwe.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, yavuze ko PHEIC yari "itewe n'ibyago byo gukwirakwira ku isi, cyane cyane mu bihugu bikennye n'ibifite ubukungu buciriritse bidafite gahunda z'ubuvuzi zikomeye".
Mu gusubiza ku ishyirwa mu bikorwa ry'ibihano by'ingendo, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo gufata ingamba zangiza by'agateganyo ingendo n'ubucuruzi mpuzamahanga" kandi ko "OMS idashishikariza guhagarika ingendo n'ubucuruzi".
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga gutanga miliyoni 675 z'amadolari yo gufasha ibihugu bifite amikoro make kwitegura, ivuga ko bikeneye gufasha ibihugu "bitagira uburyo bwo kumenya abantu banduye virusi, n'ubwo yaba igomba kuba igaragara".
Tedros yakomeje atangaza mu magambo ye ko "dufite imbaraga zingana n'iz'intege nke zacu" kandi asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "gushora imari uyu munsi cyangwa kuzishyura menshi nyuma". Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, OMS yatangije ikiganiro n'abanyamakuru mu kiganiro cyiswe "Kwibuka ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 ari cyo cyateye iyo ndwara".
Ku munsi umwe, Tedros yavuze ko Umunyamabanga mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye Antonio Guterres yemeye gutanga "imbaraga z'Umuryango w'Abibumbye wose mu gusubiza".
Ibyo byatumye hashyirwaho itsinda ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye rishinzwe kurwanya ibyago, rihuza ibikorwa byose by'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, ibyo bikaba byari gutuma "bashyira imbaraga mu guhangana n'ikibazo cy'ubuzima, mu gihe izindi nzego zo zakoresha ubuhanga bwazo mu guhangana n'ingaruka z'icyorezo mu rwego rw'imibereho y'abantu, ubukungu n'iterambere".
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'abahanga batandukanye ba OMS n'u Bushinwa bari kumwe mu butumwa, ryaje gusura u Bushinwa kugira ngo ryongere gutanga amakuru y'ibyabaye ku butaka, kugira ngo rifashe mu miyoborere y'igihugu no kwakira inama z'inama n'ibigo bikuru byo ku rwego rw'igihugu, kugira ngo harebwe "uburemere bw'icyorezo n'ubwandu" no "kugira ingaruka z'ibikorwa by'ubutabazi ku rwego rw'intara n'uturere, harimo n'imijyi". Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, OMS yatangaje ko "isi igomba gushyiraho ingufu nyinshi mu kwitegura icyorezo cya coronavirus gishobora kubaho", ivuga ko nubwo byaba ari uguhubuka, ibihugu bigomba "gukomeza kwitegura".
Mu rwego rwo gusubiza icyorezo cyazahaye muri Irani, OMS yohereje itsinda ry'ubutumwa rusange kugira ngo isuzume uko ibintu byifashe. Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS bavuze ko ingamba zo kugenzura icyorezo cya koronavirusi ku isi zigiye kuva ku rwego rwo hejuru kugeza ku rwego rwo hejuru, ari rwo rwego rwo hejuru rw'ubudahangarwa n'ibyago.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi ushinzwe ibikorwa by'ubutabazi muri gahunda y'ubutabazi bw'ubuzima ya OMS, yatanze umuburo muri aya magambo: "Iki ni cyo kigeragezo cya buri butegetsi ku isi: igihe kirageze cyo gukanguka.
Asobanura ko ingamba zo guhangana n'iki cyorezo zishobora gutuma isi itarushaho "kubabazwa n'ibyabaye".
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko imibare iriho ubu itaremeza inzego z'ubuzima rusange ko icyorezo ari icyorezo ku isi, avuga ko iryo tangazo risobanura ko "buri muntu wese ku isi azagendana n'iyo virusi".
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya koronavirusi ari icyorezo.
