Icyorezo cya koronavirusi cyagiye gishinjwa ko cyatewe n'ingero nyinshi z'ibura ry'ibicuruzwa, byaturutse ku gukoresha ibikoresho byo kurwanya icyorezo ku isi hose, kugura bitewe n'ubwoba no guhungabanya ibikorwa by'inganda n'ibikoresho.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ubuziranenge n'ibiyobyabwenge (FDA) cyatanze umuburo ku ihindagurika ry'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi kubera ko abakiriya biyongereye kandi n'abatanga ibikoresho bakabura.
Mu turere twinshi, habonetse ikibazo cy'ubucuruzi bushingiye ku bwoba, aho abantu benshi babuze ibyo kurya, impapuro z'isuku, n'amazi yo mu macupa, bituma habaho ikibazo cy'ibikoresho by'ibanze.
Ikigo cy'ikoranabuhanga cyihariye cyarahawe umuburo ku bijyanye n'icyuho mu gutwara ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, ibyifuzo by'ibikoresho birinda abantu bikubye inshuro 100.
Ibyo byatumye igiciro cy'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi kizamukaho inshuro zigera kuri makumyabiri, ndetse bituma ibyifashishwa mu buvuzi by'ubuvuzi bitinda, mu gihe cy'amezi ane cyangwa atandatu.
Ibi byatumye habaho ikibazo cy'ibura ry'ibikoresho birinda ubuzima ku isi, aho OMS yaburiye ko bishobora gushyira ubuzima bw'abakozi b'ubuzima mu kaga.
Muri Australia, icyorezo cyatanze amahirwe mashya ku bacuruzi ba DaiGuu yo kugurisha ibicuruzwa bya Australia mu Bushinwa.
Iki gikorwa cyatumye habaho ibura ry'ibiribwa by'abana mu masoko amwe n'amwe, nyuma biza guhagarikwa na leta ya Ositaraliya. Nubwo hari ubwandu bw'abantu benshi banduye COVID-19 mu majyaruguru y'Ubutaliyani no mu gace ka Wuhan, n'ubwo hari ibyifuzo byinshi by'ibiribwa, utwo duce twombi twugarijwe n'ikibazo cy'ibura ry'ibiribwa.
Ingamba zashyizweho n'u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani zo kurwanya ubucuruzi butemewe n'amategeko no kubitsa ibicuruzwa by'ingenzi, zagize icyo zigeraho, bituma habaho ibura ry'ibiribwa ryari ryitezwe mu Burayi no muri Amerika y'Amajyaruguru.
Mu majyaruguru y'Ubutaliyani ntihagaragaye igabanuka rikomeye mu musaruro w'ubuhinzi, ariko ibiciro bishobora kuzamuka nk'uko abahagarariye inganda babivuga.
Mu mujyi wa Wuhan, ibigega by'ibiribwa byashyizwe ku mbuga nkoranyambaga byasohotse mu gihe gito gusa, mu gihe abayobozi ba leta y'Ubushinwa bari bamaze gushyiraho ibigega by'inyama z'inkoko kugira ngo abaturage babone indyo yuzuye.
Mu Butaliyani, amategeko nk'ayo asaba abahinzi b'ibiribwa ko bagomba kugira ibicuruzwa by'ibanze bibaye ngombwa.
Ubukungu bw'isi yose mu Bushinwa bwarahazahariye: Mu kwezi kwa gatatu, raporo y'ibinyamakuru yo ku ya 16 Werurwe, yavuze ko ingamba za leta zo guhagarika ikwirakwira rya virusi, hamwe n'igabanuka rya 20.5% ry'ibicuruzwa ku isoko, byagize ingaruka zikomeye ku bukungu bw'u Bushinwa mu mezi abiri ya mbere y'umwaka wa 2020.
Kubera ko Ubushinwa ari igihugu cy'ingenzi mu bukungu n'ubucuruzi, iki cyorezo cyafashwe nk'icyorezo gikomeye cyugarije ubukungu bw'isi.
Agathe Demaris wo mu itsinda ry'ubushakashatsi bw'ikigo cy'Ubwigenge mu by'Ubukungu, yavuze ko amasoko azakomeza guhindagurika kugeza igihe tuzaba dufite igishushanyo mbonera cy'ingaruka zishoboka.
Muri Mutarama 2020, bamwe mu basesenguzi bavuze ko ingaruka z'icyorezo ku bukungu bw'isi zishobora kuba zikomeye kurusha iz'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004.
Impuguke yo muri kaminuza ya Washington i St. Louis, iteganya ko ingaruka z'amadolari arenga miriyari 300 ku isoko mpuzamahanga ry'ibicuruzwa zizamara imyaka ibiri.
Umuryango w'ibihugu bitumiza peteroli (OPEC) wavuze ko "wagize icyo ukora" nyuma y'uko ibiciro by'ibikomoka kuri peteroli bigabanutse cyane kubera ko ubukungu bw'Ubushinwa bwagabanutse.
Ku ya 24 Gashyantare, amasoko y'imari n'imigabane ku isi yose yaguye kubera ubwiyongere bukabije bw'abanduye COVID-19 hanze y'Ubushinwa.
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare, mu gihe impungenge z'icyorezo cya coronavirus zakomezaga kwiyongera, indege zitandukanye zo muri Amerika zirimo NASDAQ-100, S&amp;P 500 Index, Dow Jones Industrial Average, zagize igihombo gikomeye cyane kuva mu 2008, aho Dow yaguye amanota 1,191, akaba ari ukugabanuka gukomeye cyane mu munsi umwe kuva mu bibazo by'imari mu 2007-08.
Ibipimo byose uko ari bitatu byagabanutseho 10 ku ijana muri icyo cyumweru.
Ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, Scope Ratings GmbH yemeje ko u Bushinwa bufite ubushobozi bwo kwishyura imyenda ya leta, ariko ikomeza kugira icyizere cyo kutagira icyo busaba.
Ibiciro by'imigabane byongeye kumanuka bitewe n'ubwoba bwa coronavirus, ku wa 16 Werurwe nibwo byagabanyutse cyane.
Abantu benshi batekereza ko hashobora kubaho ihungabana ry'ubukungu.
Umuhanga mu by'ubukungu witwa Mohammed Al-Erian yashimye ingamba zafashwe n'amabanki y'ibihugu n'ama leta mu gihe gikwiriye.
Banki nkuru y'igihugu irushaho guhangana n'ibibazo by'ubukungu kurusha uko byagenze mu gihe cy'ihungabana ry'ubukungu ryo mu mwaka wa 2008.
Ingendo ni kimwe mu byorezo byugarije isi, bitewe n'ingamba za leta zo guhagarika ingendo, gufunga ahantu hahurira abantu benshi harimo n'ibishushanyo, ndetse n'inama za leta zo guhagarika ingendo aho ari ho hose ku isi.
Ingaruka zabaye iz'uko indege nyinshi zirimo British Airways, China Eastern Airlines na Qantas zahagaritse ingendo kubera ko abantu bayisabye cyane, mu gihe indege y'akarere yo mu Bwongereza Flybe yaguye.
Ingaruka byagize ku rugendo rwo gutwara abagenzi mu bwato ni zo zari zisigaye zigaragara cyane.
Hari n'ibibuga by'indege n'iby'amato byafunzwe.
Iki cyorezo cyageze mu gihe kimwe n'ikiruhuko cy'umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa, igihe cy'urugendo rukomeye.
Guverinoma y'igihugu n'iy'akarere byakuyeho ibikorwa byinshi birimo ibirori ngarukamwaka by'umwaka mushya, ndetse n'ibigo byigenga bifunga amaduka yabyo n'ahantu nyaburanga hakururwa ba mukerarugendo nka Hong Kong Disneyland na Shanghai Disneyland.
Ibirori byinshi by'Umunsi Mushya w'Ababyeyi n'ahantu nyaburanga hatandukanye mu mujyi wa Beijing, byafunzwe hagamijwe gukumira ibirori rusange birimo I Forbidden City n'ibirori by'urusengero.
Mu ntara 24 muri 31 z'Ubushinwa, umujyi n'intara, abayobozi bongereye ikiruhuko cy'umwaka mushya ku ya 10 Gashyantare, bategeka ibigo byinshi by'akazi kudasubira gukora kugeza icyo gihe.
Ibi byiciro by'ubucuruzi byarebaga 80% by'umusaruro mbumbe w'igihugu na 90% by'ibyoherezwaga hanze.
Hong Kong yazamutse ku gipimo cyo guhangana n'indwara z'ibyorezo, ivuga ko ibihe by'amakuba biri hejuru, ifunga amashuri kugeza mu kwezi kwa Werurwe, kandi ihagarika ibirori by'ubunani. Ubucuruzi ku isi hose bwaragabanyutse, aho amaduka yagabanyije amasaha yayo cyangwa afungwa by'agateganyo.
Mu Burayi no muri Amerika y'Amajyepfo, umubare w'abajya ku iduka waragabanutse ku kigero cya 40%.
Abacuruzi bo muri Amerika y'Amajyaruguru no mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, babonye igabanuka rya 50-60%.
Mu kwezi kwa gatatu, umubare w'abantu bajya mu masoko n'amaguru wagabanutseho 33-43 ku ijana ugereranyije no mu kwezi kwa kabiri.
Abakozi bakorera mu masoko hirya no hino ku isi bafashe ingamba z'inyongera, nko kongera isuku, gushyiraho ibyuma bigenzura ubushyuhe mu maduka, no guhagarika ibikorwa. Nk'uko Komisiyo y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ishinzwe ubukungu muri Amerika y'Epfo ibivuga, igabanuka ry'ubukungu ryatewe n'icyorezo rishobora gutuma abantu bari hagati ya miliyoni 14 na 22 bagwa mu bukene bukabije muri Amerika y'Epfo, abo batari kuba muri iyo mimerere mbere y'icyorezo.
Muri Mutarama na Gashyantare 2020, ubwo icyorezo cyari cyakomeye cyane i Wuhan, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 5 batakaje akazi mu Bushinwa.
Abenshi mu bakozi bo mu cyaro bagera kuri miriyoni 300 bo mu Bushinwa baguye mu mirimo yabo mu ntara zo mu gihugu hagati cyangwa mu ntara ya Hubei. Muri Werurwe 2020, Abanyamerika barenga miriyoni 10 batakaje akazi kandi basaba leta kubashyigikira.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus gishobora gutwara imirimo miliyoni 47 muri Amerika kandi igipimo cy'ubushomeri gishobora kumanukaho 32% nk'uko byatangajwe na Banki y'igihugu y'u Bufaransa. Abakozi b'abimukira babarirwa muri za miriyoni bataye akazi kubera gufunga mu Buhinde (bakorerwa ibihembo buri munsi). Isesengura ryakozwe n'ikigo Angus Reed ryasanze 44% by'imiryango yo muri Kanada yagize ubushomeri.
Mu gice cya kabiri cy'ukwezi kwa gatatu, abakozi bo mu Bufaransa bagera kuri miliyoni 4 basabye ko bahabwa inguzanyo y'ubushomeri bw'igihe gito, naho abakozi bo mu Bwongereza bagera kuri miliyoni 1 basabye inguzanyo y'inguzanyo ya rusange. Mu Budage, hari ibigo by'abakozi bigera kuri miliyoni imwe n'igice byatangiye kohereza abakozi babyo muri gahunda y'akazi y'igihe gito y'inguzanyo ya leta.
Gahunda y'indishyi z'akazi z'igihe gito zo mu Budage, zakurikijwe n'u Bufaransa n'u Bwongereza.
Ibice by'ubugeni n'umurage ndangamuco byahuye n'ingaruka zikomeye z'icyorezo, cyagize ingaruka ku mikorere y'imiryango ku isi hose, ndetse no ku bantu bakora imirimo yabo ku giti cyabo.
Amashyirahamwe y'ubuhanzi n'umuco yagerageje gukomeza (gushyigikira) ubutumwa bwayo (gushyigikira: inkunga y'amafaranga y'abaturage) mu guha abaturage kugera ku murage ndangamuco, kurinda abakozi bayo n'abaturage, no gushyigikira abahanzi aho bishoboka.
Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, hirya no hino ku isi no mu byiciro bitandukanye, inzu ndangamurage, amazu y'ibitabo, aho abantu bakorera, n'ibindi bigo by'umuco byafunzwe by'agateganyo, n'ibitaramo byabo, ibirori n'ibitaramo bivanwaho cyangwa bisubikwa.
