Uburyo bw'u Budage bwashyizwe ahagaragara ku ya 17 Mutarama 2020; porotori yari yashinzwe n'ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika cyita ku ndwara (CDC) ntiyasohotse kugeza ku ya 28 Mutarama, bituma habaho gutinda kw'ibizamini muri Amerika. Mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo, u Bushinwa na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika byari bifite ibibazo ku bwizerezi bw'ibikoresho by'ibizamini kandi ibyo bihugu n'Ubushinwa n'Ubwongereza ntibyashoboye gutanga ibikoresho bihagije byo gukemura ibyifuzo n'amabwiriza by'inzobere mu by'ubuzima.
Ibinyuranye n'ibyo, abahanga bavuga ko kuba muri Koreya y'Epfo hakorwa ibizamini byinshi byafashije mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya coronavirus.
Ubushobozi bwo gupima, cyane cyane mu mavuriro yigenga, bwatangijwe na leta ya Koreya y'Epfo mu gihe cy'imyaka myinshi.
Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryavuze ko kongera gahunda zo gupima ari bwo buryo bwiza bwo kugabanya ubwiyongere bw'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Muri Werurwe 2020, u Bushinwa bwatangaje ko hari ibibazo by'ukuri mu bikoresho by'ubushakashatsi.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, ibikoresho byo gupima byakozwe na CDC byari bike; leta yakurikijeho ikuraho inzitizi z'ibiro by'ubutegetsi zabuzaga kwipimisha ku giti cye. Esipanye yaguze ibikoresho by'ibizamini by'ibizamini biturutse mu kigo cy'Abashinwa cya Shenzhen BioEgy Biotechnology Co., Ltd., ariko isanga ibisubizo bitari byemewe.
Firme yavuze ko ibipimo bitari byo bishobora guturuka ku kuba ibipimo byarakusanyijwe nabi cyangwa se kuba ibikoresho byarakoreshejwe nabi.
Minisiteri y'Ubufaransa yavuze ko izakuraho ibikoresho by'ubushakashatsi byatanze ibisubizo bitari byo, ikabisimbuza ibindi byatanzwe na Shenzhen Biology. 80% by'ibikoresho byavuye mu Bushinwa byaguzwe na Repubulika ya Tchèque byazanye ibisubizo bitari byo.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Matovič yasabye ko izo nkingo zajya mu mazi ya Danube. Ateş Kara wo muri Minisiteri y'Ubuzima ya Turukiya yavuze ko ibikoresho bya Turukiya byazanye mu Bushinwa "bifite amakosa menshi" kandi ko "bitabikoresheje". UK yaguze mu Bushinwa ibikoresho byo gupima miliyoni 3.5 mu ntangiriro za Mata 2020, yatangaje ko bitakoreshejwe.
