Aho abantu ba mbere bishwe na COVID-19 mu Butaliyani, abashakashatsi bakora mu mujyi wa Vò mu Butaliyani, bagenzura inshuro ebyiri abantu bose bagera ku 3,400 mu gihe cy'iminsi icumi.
Hafi kimwe cya kabiri cy'abari basuzumwe bagasanga nta bimenyetso bafite, kandi abantu bose babonetse ko banduye bashyizwe mu kato.
Gahunda yo guhagarika ingendo kuva mu gihugu ujya mu kindi, byagize ingaruka zo kurandura ubwandu bushya.
Icyorezo cya Koronavirusi cya 2020 cyateye imbere mu gihugu cya Singapore ku buryo buhoro cyane ugereranyije n'ibindi bihugu byateye imbere, ariko ntibyabujije abantu guhura n'abandi, bakagirwa abarinzi, bakagenzurwa, bakagirwa abarinzi, ariko ntibyabujije abantu gufunga amazu y'ibiro by'uburiro n'ayo gufungiramo.
Ibikorwa byinshi byarahagaritswe, kandi Singapore yatangiye gusaba abaturage kuguma mu rugo guhera ku ya 28 Werurwe, ariko amashuri yongeye gufungura ku gihe ku ya 23 Werurwe nyuma y'ikiruhuko.
Ibindi bihugu byinshi, nk'Isilande na Koreya y'Epfo, na byo byagiye bigenzura icyorezo mu buryo bukomeye binyuze mu gupimisha, gukumira ingendo, gusuzuma no gushyira abantu mu kato, ariko nta nkomyi.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe bwagaragaje ko mu bihugu byagenzuwe cyane kurusha ibyapfuye, umubare w'abanduye uba muke cyane, wenda bitewe n'uko ibyo bihugu biba bifite ubushobozi bwo gutahura abantu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa badafite ibimenyetso.
OMS isaba ibihugu bidafite ubushobozi bwo gupima no kuba laboratwari zabyo zifite ubumenyi buke kuri COVID-19, ko byajya byohereza mu b'isi mu ma laboratwari 16 ya OMS ibipimo bitanu bya mbere by'abanduye COVID-19 n'icumi bya mbere by'abanduye COVID-19 kugira ngo byemezwe.
Muri laboratwari 16 z'ibanze, 7 ziri muri Aziya, 5 ziri i Burayi, 2 muri Afurika, 1 muri Amerika ya Ruguru na 1 muri Ositaraliya.
Mu mbonerahamwe iri hasi aha, % by'ibipimo by'ubwandu mu bipimo, bigengwa n'amabwiriza y'igihugu.
Mu bindi bintu byose, igihugu kigenzura abantu bari mu bitaro gusa, kigira igipimo cyo hejuru cy'abanduye kurusha igihugu kigenzura abantu bose, baba bagaragaza ibimenyetso cyangwa batabifite.
Gukaraba intoki (cyangwa gukaraba intoki), nanone bizwi nk'isuku y'intoki, ni igikorwa cyo gusukura intoki zawe ugamije gukuraho ibitaka, amavuta, mikorobe cyangwa ibindi bintu bidakenewe.
Gukoresha isabune ukaraba intoki buri gihe mu "bihe bya ngombwa " by'umunsi, bifasha mu kwirinda indwara nyinshi, urugero nk'iseru n'indwara y'igicuri, zandura mu myanya y'urwagasabo.
Abantu bashobora kwandura indwara z'ubuhumekero nk'ibicurane cyangwa ibicurane bisanzwe, urugero, iyo batakarabye intoki mbere yo gukora ku maso, ku mazuru cyangwa ku munwa (ni ukuvuga, ku nkokora z'uruhu).
Ibi ni ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi mu munsi umuntu agomba gukaraba intoki n'isabune: mbere na nyuma yo gukora isuku, nyuma yo guhanagura umwana cyangwa guhindura umwenda w'umwana, mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya no gutegura indyo, mbere na nyuma yo kurya inyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko.
Niba nta mazi n'isabune bihari, intoki zishobora gukoreshwa mu gukaraba umwotsi. OMS itera inkunga abantu gukaraba intoki mu bihe bikurikira:
Mbere yo gutegura amafunguro, mu gihe cyo gutegura no mu gihe amaze gutegurwa.
Mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku murwayi.
Nyuma yo guhanagura umwana ukoresha ubwiherero cyangwa se nyuma yo kumuhanagura.
Nyuma yo kunyara, gukorora cyangwa guhumeka.
Nyuma yo gukora ku matungo, ku matungo cyangwa ku myanda yayo.
Isuku y'intoki irebana n'ibikorwa by'isuku bijyana n'imikorere y'ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gutanga imiti cyangwa ubuvuzi bishobora gukumira cyangwa kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Gukaraba intoki bifite intego yo kuvura indwara (bacteria, virus, cyangwa ubundi bwoko bw'udukoko dushobora guteza indwara) no gukaraba intoki ku bintu bishobora guteza indwara cyangwa kwangiza.
Ni ingenzi cyane cyane ku bantu bakora mu byo kurya cyangwa mu buvuzi, ariko ni ingenzi no ku bantu basanzwe.
Gukaraba intoki bifite akamaro kanini ku buzima, harimo: kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara z'ibicurane, za coronavirus n'izindi ndwara zandura; kwirinda indwara zandura z'iseru; kugabanya ubwandu bw'indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero;
Nanone kandi, mu gihe ababyeyi babyarira mu rugo, bigabanya umubare w'abana bapfa babyara.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2013 bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki byoroheje bishobora gutuma abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu barushaho gukura.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, ihinduka ryoroheje mu myitwarire, nko gukaraba intoki hakoreshejwe isabune, bishobora kugabanya impfu z'abana bavuka bitewe n'indwara z'ubuhumekero n'iz'ubuhumekero.
Iki gikorwa cyoroshye gishobora kugabanya umubare w'abapfa bahitanywe n'iyi ndwara ku kigero cya 50%.
Gushyiraho ingamba zo gukaraba intoki bishobora kugabanya umubare w'abantu barwaye isuku y'amaraso ku kigero cya kimwe cya gatatu, kandi ibyo bifatwa nko kugeza amazi meza mu duce turimo abaturage batishoboye.
Kugabanuka kw'imibare y'abarwaye iseru ku kigero cya 48% bishobora kuba byatewe no gukaraba intoki hakoreshejwe isabune. Gukaraba intoki hakoreshejwe isabune nk'umuco ugendana n'igihe mu ngo, amashuri n'imiryango ku isi hose, ni bwo buryo bwonyine bw'ingirakamaro kandi buhendutse bwo kwirinda iseru n'indwara z'ubuhumekero (ARI).
Imwe mu mpamvu zikomeye zituma abantu bapfa cyane, ni impiswi, aho abana bagera kuri miriyoni 18 bapfa buri mwaka, kandi ikaba ari yo mpamvu y'ibanze ituma abana bapfa batarageza ku myaka itanu.
Abana bagera kuri miriyoni 35 bapfa buri mwaka bazize diyabete na nimoniya.
Nk'uko bitangazwa na UNICEF, kugira akamenyero gakomeye ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune mbere yo kurya no nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero bishobora kurokora ubuzima buruta ubw'urukingo cyangwa uburyo bwo kwivuza ubwo ari bwo bwose, bikaba byagabanya umubare w'abapfa bazize diyabete ku kigero cya kimwe cya kabiri, n'uw'abapfa bazize indwara z'ubuhumekero bukabije ku kigero cya kimwe cya kane.
Gukaraba intoki bikunze kwiyongera ku zindi gahunda zo gusukura nk'uko biri mu bikorwa by'ibigo by'ubuvuzi (WASH).
Gukaraba intoki birinda impyiko zandura mu buryo bw'umubiri.
Kimwe mu ngaruka mbi cyane zo gukaraba intoki ni uko gukaraba intoki kenshi bishobora gutuma uruhu runyunyuka bitewe n'uko rukomeza kumuka.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu gihugu cya Danimarike mu mwaka wa 2012, bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki cyane bishobora gutera uruhu rufite ibisebe, rufite ibisebe byitwa hand eczema cyangwa dermatite, bikaba byiganje cyane mu bakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima.
Gukaraba intoki kenshi cyane na byo bifatwa nk'ikimenyetso cy'indwara y'igicuri.
Hari ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi mu gihe cy'umunsi umuntu agomba gukaraba intoki akoresheje isabune kugira ngo agabanye ubwandu: nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero (gusuka, gusohora), nyuma yo gukoropa umwana (ahindura inkweto), mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya, mbere yo gutegura amafunguro cyangwa mbere yo kurya inyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko.
Indi mpamvu ituma umuntu agomba gukaraba intoki neza kugira ngo adateza indwara ni: mbere yo gukata cyangwa gukira igikomere, nyuma yo kwitsamura, gukorora cyangwa gukorora mu mazuru, nyuma yo gukora ku myanda y'amatungo cyangwa ku matungo, na nyuma yo gukora ku myanda.
Mu bihugu byinshi, ikigero cyo gukaraba intoki kiruta icyo gukoresha isabune.
Mu mwaka wa 2015, ubushakashatsi ku bijyanye no gukaraba intoki mu bihugu 54 bwerekanye ko ku kigereranyo cy'ingo 38.7% ari zo zikoresha isabune mu gukaraba intoki. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2014 bwagaragaje ko Arabia Saudite ifite igipimo cyo hejuru cya 97%; Amerika ifite igipimo kiri hagati cya 77%; naho Ubushinwa bufite igipimo kiri hasi cya 23%. Ubu hari uburyo bwinshi bwo guhindura imyitwarire buhari bwo gukangurira abana gukaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune mu bihe bikomeye.
"Gahunda y'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze" yashyizweho na Minisiteri y'uburezi muri Filipine, ni urugero rw'ibikorwa ku rwego rwo hejuru byo guteza imbere ubuzima n'uburezi bw'abana.
Iyo gahunda y'igihugu, ikubiyemo gukaraba intoki buri munsi hakoreshejwe isabune, gufata imiti yo kuvura ibiheri kabiri mu mwaka, no gukaraba amenyo buri munsi hakoreshejwe fluoride.
Byanatangiye gukoreshwa muri Indoneziya kandi byagenze neza.
Gukoresha isabune cyangwa umuti wo gusukura mu mazi bishobora gutuma mikorobe z'uruhu zikurwaho.
Igikorwa cyingenzi cy'isabune n'isuku ni ukugabanya inzitizi mu mazi, no kongera ubudahangarwa.
Amazi yonyine ni umuti udakora neza ku ruhu kuko ibinure na poroteyine, ari byo bigize ibumba, bidapfa kumeneka mu mazi.
Icyakora, isuku irushaho gukomera iyo amazi menshi akomeje gutemba.
Kubera ko isabune zikoreshwa kenshi, zishobora kuba zirimo udukoko tw'udukoko twashoboraga kuba twarasigaye mu gihe zagiye zikoreshwa.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe na bumwe ku mikorobe zanduye zanduye zagiye zigera ku mwanzuro w'uko nta mikorobe ishobora kwanduza bitewe n'uko zabaga zanduye.
Nyamara, nk'uko CDC ibivuga, "isabune zifite uburyo bwo gukarabaho isabune y'amazi ku ntoki z'abantu, ni nziza kurusha izirimo".
Abantu bafite uburwayi bwo mu mutwe, babwirijwe cyane cyane gukoresha amasabune arinda mikorobe.
Kugeza ubu, nta gihamya igaragaza ko gukoresha imiti yica udukoko cyangwa imiti ikoreshwa mu gupfupfahaza, byateza udukoko tudafite ubushobozi bwo kurwanya imiti.
Ariko kandi, isabune za mikorobe zirimo imiti ya mikorobe, urugero nka triclosan, ifite urutonde rurerure rw'ibinyabuzima by'inzoka.
Ku bw'ibyo, nubwo amasabune arwanya mikorobe ashobora kutagira ingaruka ku mikorobe, ntiyaba afite ingaruka nk'uko abenshi babyemeza.
Usibye imvura n'imiti irinda uruhu, imyitozo ihamye ishobora kuba irimo aside (acide acétique, acide ascorbique, acide lactique) mu rwego rwo kugabanya pH, acide benzoïque ikora mu buryo bwo kurwanya mikorobe no mu bindi bintu byongera ubwiza bw'uruhu (alovera, vitamin, menthol, ibikomoka ku bimera). Isesengura rya kaminuza ya Oregon School of Public Health ryerekanye ko isabune zisanzwe, zirimo na triclosan, zifite ubushobozi kurusha isabune zo mu rwego rw'abakiliya zo ku rwego rwa consumer zirwanya mikorobe.
Amazi ashyushye yo gukaraba intoki ntabwo ashyushye bihagije ngo yice mikorobe.
Bakterie zikura cyane iyo umubiri ufite ubushyuhe bwa dogere 37 z'Cyl.
Icyakora, amazi ashyushye arimo isabune arushaho kuba ingirakamaro mu kuvana amavuta mu butaka hamwe n'utunyabuzima twanduye, kurusha amazi akonje arimo isabune.
Icyakora, mu buryo bunyuranye n'ibyo abantu benshi bizera, ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukoresha amazi ashyushye nta ngaruka bigira ku mikorobe ziba mu biganza.
Umuti wo gusukura intoki cyangwa se umuti wica mikorobi ni umuti wo gusukura intoki udafite amazi.
Mu mpera za 1990 no mu ntangiriro z'ikinyejana cya 21, imiti isukura intoki idafite alcool (ibizwi kandi nka 'alcohol-based hand rubs', 'disinfectant hand rubs' cyangwa 'hand sanitizer') yatangiye kwamamara.
Byinshi muri byo biba bishingiye kuri isopropyl alcohol cyangwa etanol, ikoreshwa mu buryo bworoshye no kugabanya ingaruka zo gukama kwa alcohol, ikoreshwa mu buryo bw'ubwoko bwa carbomore (polymeric ya acrylic acid) muri gel, cyangwa ikoreshwa nk'umuvumba w'amazi, cyangwa ikoreshwa nk'umuvumba w'amazi, ikoreshwa muri glycérine.
Iyo ushyiremo hydrogen peroxide y'amavuta, bikongera ubushobozi bwo kurwanya mikorobe.
Alkoholi ikoreshwa mu gusukura mu ruganda yica za mikorobe, mikorobe z'ubumara bwa MRSA na VRE, za tuberculose na virusi zimwe na zimwe (harimo na virusi z'ibicurane bya SIDA, herpes, RSV, rhinovirus, vaccinia, influenza na hepatite) ndetse n'ibiheri.
Alkoholikeri zikoreshwa mu gukaraba, zirimo 70% by'inzoga, zica 99.97% by'uducurama tw'umubiri nyuma y'amasegonda 30 zitanzwe (bimwe na 3.5 logs, ni ukuvuga 35 decibels) n'inyongera ziri hagati ya 99.99% na 99.999% nyuma y'iminota 1 yo kuzishyiraho (bimwe na 4 cyangwa 5 logs).
Umuti uvura intoki wa alkol ni wo muti w'ingenzi cyane kuko utuma intoki zidakora neza. Ubusanzwe, umuti uvura intoki wa alkol ni wo ukwiriye gukoreshwa kugira ngo intoki zose zimirwe neza.
Ibitoki by'amaboko yombi, imbere n'inyuma, hagati n'ibice by'intoki byose, bikamirwa mu gihe cy'amasegonda 30 kugeza igihe amazi, ikinyagu cyangwa se gel bisukuye.
Nanone, intoki zigomba gukaraba neza, zikagendwa mu biganza byombi. Ikigo cya Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) gitera inkunga abantu gukaraba intoki mu mwanya wo gukaraba sanitizer, cyane cyane iyo bigaragara ko intoki zanduye.
Iterambere ry'ikoreshwa ry'izi ntangabuzima rishingiye ku buryo zikorohereza no ku buryo zikoresha zikarinda udukoko duto cyane; ariko, ntizigomba gusimbura gukaraba intoki mu gihe nta sabune n'amazi bihari.
Gukoresha kenshi imiti isukura intoki irimo inzoga bishobora gutuma uruhu rwumutse, keretse iyo imyenda n'ibyokongera uruhu byongewemo.
Gliserine cyangwa ibindi bikoresho by'isuku bishobora kugabanya cyangwa se kugabanya ingaruka zo gukama kw'inzoga.
Mu bigeragezo byo kwa muganga, isuku y'uruhu n'ubushyuhe byagabanutse cyane bitewe na sanitizer y'intoki ya alcool irimo amavuta yo gukaraba, ugereranyije n'isabune cyangwa imiti yica mikorobe.
Abantu bafite allergies idasanzwe ku binyobwa birimo Alcool cyangwa Alcohol Hand Rubs, ni abantu bafite contact dermatitis, contact urticaria syndrome cyangwa se abafite allergies.
Kuba umuntu yafata ku buryo butera uburibwe, bigatuma arwara indwara y'uruhu, byasaga n'aho ari byiza cyane kuruta gukaraba intoki akoresheje isabune n'amazi.
Nubwo ibyo bikoresho bikora neza, nta bwo bikura ibiyobyabwenge mu ntoki, ahubwo birazikura.
Niyo mpamvu imiti isukura intoki idashobora gukwirakwira neza nk'amazi n'isabune mu gukumira indwara, kuko indwara zikiri mu ntoki.
Ingaruka nziza za sanitizer zitanywa inzoga z'amaboko zishingiye cyane ku bikoresho n'uburyo zashyizweho, kandi mu mateka y'ubuzima bwazo, zagaragaye ko zikora neza cyane kurusha inzoga na rubs.
Vuba aha, mu buryo butandukanye n'inzoga, yagaragaye ko igabanya ubuziranenge nyuma yo gukoreshwa kenshi, wenda bitewe n'ibyago by'indwara z'uruhu, uburyo bwo gukoresha benzalkoniyumu chloride yagaragaye ko ifite ubudahangarwa bwagutse kandi buhagije nyuma yo gukoresha uburyo bwo kurwanya mikorobe.
Abantu benshi bo mu miryango ikennye ntibashobora kugura isabune, ahubwo bakoresha ivu cyangwa ivu.
Ishwagara cyangwa ibumba bishobora kuba ingirakamaro kurusha amazi yonyine, ariko ntibikwiye kuba ingirakamaro cyane nk'isabune.
Bimwe mu byo abantu bahangayikishwa n'uko iyo ibyuya byanduye, bishobora gutuma indwara ikwirakwira cyane.
Kimwe n'isabune, imibu na yo ni umuti wica udukoko kuko iyo ihuye n'amazi, ituma havuka umuti w'umunyu.
OMS isaba ko aho nta sabune iboneka, haboneka ivu cyangwa umucanga.
Uburyo bwiza bwo gukaraba intoki bw'Abanyamerika bwashyizweho n'ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara (CDC) mu rwego rwo kwirinda ko indwara zandura, bukubiyemo ibi bikurikira:
Gukaraba intoki ukoresheje amazi ashyushye cyangwa se akonje.
Amazi atemba ni yo akwiriye kuko amazi atemba ashobora kwanduza, nubwo nta ruhare rw'ubushyuhe bw'amazi bufite.
Shyira isabune ku biganza byawe, harimo n'inyuma y'amaboko, hagati y'intoki n'imbere y'umwobo.
Isahani ikuraho mikorobe ku ruhu, kandi ubushakashatsi bugaragaza ko abantu bakaraba intoki neza iyo bakoresheje isabune kurusha amazi yonyine.
Ujye ubanza ugaragure mu maso mu gihe cy'iminota 20 mbere yo gukaraba.
Gupfukama bituma habaho igitsure, bigatuma udukoko duto duto tuva ku ruhu, kandi iyo umuntu ashubije mu buryo burebure cyane, udukoko duto duto turushaho kuva ku ruhu.
Gukaraba neza munsi y'amazi asukuye.
Gukaraba intoki mu mazi yo mu iriba bishobora kongera kuzanduza intoki.
Ujye ukaraba neza cyangwa se ubireke bihumuke.
Amaboko yanduye kandi yanduye arushaho kwangirika. Ibice byanduye cyane ni ibibero, ibiganza, hagati y'intoki n'amaboko, n'aho munsi y'impyiko.
Amenyo y'imashini n'ipolishe y'imigozi y'imigozi bishobora kuba byarabereye ahantu heza cyane ibinyabuzima byitwa mikorobe.
Imiti yo gusokoza (moisturizing lotions) ikunda gukoreshwa mu kwirinda ko ibiganza byuma; uruhu rwumye rushobora kwangiza uruhu, ibyo bikaba byongera ibyago byo kwanduza.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere aho amazi y'amazi n'isabune bidahari, hakenewe uburyo bworoshye bwo gukaraba intoki, urugero nko gukoresha amazi n'ivu biva mu nkono cyangwa mu nkono zifite imyobo iboneye. Mu bihugu bifite amazi make (nk'amashuri mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere cyangwa mu cyaro), hari uburyo bwo kubungabunga amazi, urugero nk'imashini zikoresha amazi, hamwe n'ubundi buryo bw'ikiguzi gito.
Tippi - tap ni uburyo bworoshye bwo gukoramo, bukoresha imigozi ipfa ku mugozi, hamwe n'uruhago rukoreshwa n'amaguru, kugira ngo umuntu asukemo amazi make cyane ku ntoki no ku gikoresho cy'isabune.
Gukaraba intoki neza ni kimwe mu bintu by'ingenzi mu buryo bwo gusukura intoki, ariko hari impaka ku buryo bwiza bwo gukaraba intoki mu bwogero rusange.
Ubushakashatsi bwinshi bwakozwe bwerekana ko impapuro zikozwe mu mpapuro zitanga isuku irenze cyane iy'amashanyarazi yo kumesa mu bwiherero.
Mu mwaka wa 2008, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Kaminuza ya Westminster, mu mujyi wa Londres, bwashyizweho n'ishyirahamwe ry'imashini zikora impapuro, The European Tissue Symposium, bugamije kugereranya urwego rw'isuku y'impapuro zikora impapuro, ibikoresho by'imyuka isukura intoki n'ibikoresho by'imyuka isukura intoki.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki no kuzamisha mu gikoresho gikamya umwuka ushyushye, umubare w'udukoko twica indwara wiyongereyeho 194% ku mpyiko z'intoki n'ibice by'intoki bya 254%.
Gushira mu gikonoshwa cy'amazi hakoreshejwe ibyuma by'umwuka byongera umubare w'utunyabuzima twanduye ku kigereranyo cya 42% ku minwa y'intoki na 15% ku maboko.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki no kuzigumisha mu rwabya rw'impapuro, umubare w'utwogero tw'udukoko twagabanutseho 76% ku bipfunsi by'intoki no kuri 77% ku bipfunsi by'intoki. Abahanga mu bumenyi bw'ibidukikije bakoze ibizamini kugira ngo bamenye niba buri buryo bwo kuzigama butuma habaho kwanduza abandi bakoresha ubwiherero n'ahandi mu bwiherero.
Imodoka y'ubushyuhe bw'umwuka, ihita ihumeka umwuka uva muri iyo nzu ku muvuduko w'ibirometero 180 mu isaha (ibirometero 650 mu masaha; ibirometero 400 mu masaha), yashoboraga guhumura uturemangingo duto two mu maboko n'utw'inyamaswa, kandi ishobora no kwanduza abandi bantu bakoreshaga iyo nzu, ndetse n'abari muri iyo nzu y'ubushyuhe bari ku metero 2.
Gukoresha imashini isukura intoki ikoresha umwuka ushyushye, byatumye mikorobe zikwirakwira mu metero 0.25 zivuye kuri iyo mashini.
Impapuro z'utwoshyi ntizigaragaza ko za mikorobe zanduye cyane. Mu mwaka wa 2005, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na TÜV Produkt und Umwelt, bwagaragaje uburyo butandukanye bwo kumesa intoki.
Nyuma yo kumisha intoki, hagaragaye impinduka zikurikira mu mibare ya za bagiteri:
Hariho ibigo byinshi by'abakozi bakora mu rwego rwo kumisha intoki, kandi ibyo bikoresho byagereranywa n'imashini zikoresha impapuro.
Gukaraba intoki hakoreshejwe imiti yica udukoko mu gihe nta sabune n'amazi bihari ni amahitamo.
Umuti wica udukoko ukoreshwa mu guhanagura intoki ukoresheje inzoga, ugomba kuba ufite nibura 60% bya alcool.
Gukaraba intoki by'abaganga byabaye ingenzi nyuma y'igihe kirekire umuganga w'Umunyahungiriya Ignaz Semmelweis avumbuye (1846) ko bikora neza mu kwirinda indwara mu bitaro.
Hari ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki bitanga umusanzu ku bakozi bo mu bitaro bibuka ko bagomba gukaraba intoki mu gihe bibagiwe.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe bwagaragaje ko gukoresha imiti igabanya ubukana bw'indwara byagabanyije umubare w'abandura.
Mu buryo bwa muganga, intoki zikwiye gukaraba nibura amasegonda 15, hakoreshejwe isabune n'amazi cyangwa se gel, hakoreshejwe ishu ikwiriye, hanyuma buri gice cy'intoki kigasukwa.
Ibimenyetso by'ibiganza byombi bigomba gufatanya.
Niba hari imyanda munsi y'utwo tubyimba, dushobora gukoresha akazu kagumye kugira ngo tuyikureho.
Kubera ko mikorobe zishobora kuguma mu mazi mu gihe umuntu afashe ku ntoki, ni ngombwa ko umuntu azihanagura neza kandi akazikoresha umwenda usukuye.
Nyuma yo gukama, ugomba gukoresha impenure z' impapuro (kandi niba ari ngombwa, ujye ukingura inzugi zose) kugira ngo amazi atavaho.
Ibyo bituma intoki zongera kwandura.
Mu rwego rw'ubuzima, gukaraba intoki bigamije kurinda indwara ziterwa n'udukoko twanduza indwara (germs) no kuzibura.
Ikinyamakuru The New England Journal of Medicine cyatangaje ko mu bigo byinshi by'ubuvuzi, abantu bakomeje kudakaraba intoki ku buryo bidashoboka, aho abaganga n'abaforomokazi benshi bibagirwa gukaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku barwayi, ibyo bikaba byatuma indwara zandura.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki mu buryo bukwiriye n'izindi ngamba zoroshye bishobora kugabanya umubare w'indwara z'amaraso zifitanye isano n'imiyoboro y'amaraso ku kigero cya 66%. Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (WHO) ryasohoye inyandiko igaragaza uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki no gukaraba intoki mu nzego z'ubuzima.
Inyandiko y'ubuyobozi bw'isuku y'amaboko yatanzwe n'iri shyirahamwe ishobora no kuboneka ku rubuga rwayo kugira ngo rubanda rutangaze ibitekerezo.
Hari n'ibisobanuro byatanzwe na Witby n'abandi.
Ibikoresho by'ubucuruzi bishobora gupima no kwemeza isuku y'intoki mu gihe byaba bikenewe kugira ngo bigaragaze ko byubahirije amategeko.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryashyizeho "ibihe bitanu" byo gukaraba intoki:
Nyuma yo guhura n'amaraso cyangwa imyanda yo mu mubiri
mbere yo gutangiza igikorwa cyo kwanduza, kandi
Nyuma yo kwita ku murwayi. Kwongera imiti yica udukoko ku isabune ("imiti" cyangwa "antibacterial" sabune) byongera ubushobozi bwo kwica ku gikoresho cyo gukaraba intoki.
Kugira ngo umuntu 'asige' intoki ze imbere y'uko abagwa, ni ngombwa kugira akenda gashobora gukingirwa no gufungura intoki, gukaraba hakoreshejwe chlorhexidine cyangwa iodine, impapuro zitanduye zo gukaraba intoki nyuma yo kumesa, no gukoresha akazu gasukuye n'imiti isukura intoki kugira ngo umuntu asukure hasi.
Ibishushanyo byose by'imirimbo bigomba gukurwaho.
Muri rusange, ibi bisaba gukaraba intoki n'ibiganza kugeza ku nkokora mu gihe cy'iminota 2-6.
Si ngombwa ko uterekaho igihe kirekire (iminota 10).
Mu gihe umuntu arimo gukaraba, agomba gukaraba ku nkokora kugira ngo amazi atazagaruka ku biganza.
Iyo umurwayi amaze gukaraba, amaboko ye arashishwa mu mwenda utanduye, hanyuma agashyirwa mu ikanzu y'ubuvuzi.
Kugira ngo udukoko dutera indwara tudabashe gukwirakwira, byaba byiza ubanje gukaraba intoki mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku muntu urwaye cyangwa ukoresheje umuti wica udukoko mu ntoki.
Ku bijyanye no kurwanya indwara ya staphylococcus mu bitaro, byagaragaye ko inyungu nini cyane yo gukaraba intoki yavuye kuri 20% mbere yo gukaraba, kandi ko inyungu nke cyane yongeyeho igihe inshuro yo gukaraba intoki yiyongereyeho 35% mbere yo gukaraba.
Gukaraba intoki ukoresheje isabune yonyine, byongera inshuro zirenze eshatu ubwandu bw'indwara zandura. Kugereranya gukaraba intoki ukoresheje umuti wa alcohol n'igihe cy'iminota 30 ugereranyije no gukaraba intoki ukoresheje isabune ya antibacterial, byerekana ko gukaraba intoki ukoresheje alcohol bigabanya kwandura kw'udukoko twanduza virusi ku kigero cya 26% ugereranyije no gukaraba ukoresheje isabune ya antibacterial.
Ariko isabune n'amazi biruta cyane imiti yo gukaraba intoki ikoreshwa mu kuvura abantu bafite ibicurane bya H1N1 na Clostridium difficile. Mu ngamba zo guteza imbere isuku y'intoki mu bigo by'ubuzima, harimo kwigisha abakozi gukaraba intoki, kongera ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki bikoreshwa mu buvuzi, no kwibutsa abakozi mu nyandiko no mu mvugo.
Hakenewe ubundi bushakashatsi ku birebana n'imiti ikoreshwa mu nzego zinyuranye z'ubuvuzi.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, gukaraba intoki n'isabune bifatwa nk'uburyo bw'ibanze kandi buciriritse bwo kugera ku buzima bwiza, ndetse no ku mirire myiza.
Ariko, kubura amazi yizewe, isabune cyangwa uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki mu ngo z'abantu, mu mashuri no mu kazi, bituma kugera ku ngeso yo gukaraba intoki ku isi yose biba ikibazo.
Urugero, mu bice byinshi by'icyaro muri Afurika, usanga hari uduce duto cyane dufite imisarani yo gukaraba intoki hafi ya buri bwiherero cyangwa ubwogero rusange, nubwo haba hari uburyo bworoshye bwo kubaka aho gukarabira intoki.
Ariko kandi, kuba intoki zidakaraba neza bishobora kuba biterwa n'akamenyero umuntu yari afite, aho kuba byatewe no kubura isabune cyangwa amazi.
Gushyigikira no gushyigikira gukaraba intoki n'isabune bishobora kugira uruhare mu gufata ibyemezo by'imyanzuro, kongera ubumenyi ku nyungu zo gukaraba intoki no guhindura imyitwarire y'abaturage mu gihe kirekire.
Kugira ngo ikore neza, ni ngombwa kugenzura no kugenzura.
Isesengura ry'imikorere ry'ubushakashatsi 70 ryagaragaje ko uburyo bushingiye ku baturage bugira ingaruka nziza mu kongera gukaraba intoki mu bihugu bifite abaturage bake, mu gihe ubukangurambaga bwo kwamamaza mu rwego rw'imibereho y'abaturage budafite ingaruka nziza. Urugero rwo kwamamaza gukaraba intoki mu mashuri ni "inzira y'inyenyeri eshatu" y'ishami rya UNICEF ishishikariza ibigo by'amashuri gufata ingamba zoroshye, zidahenze kugira ngo abanyeshuri bakoreshe isabune mu gukaraba intoki hamwe n'ibindi bikenewe mu isuku.
Iyo ibisabwa by'ibanze byujuje ibisabwa, amashuri ashobora guhabwa inyenyeri kuva kuri 1 kugeza kuri 3.
Gushyiraho sitasiyo zo gukaraba intoki bishobora kuba kimwe mu bikorwa byo gukaraba intoki mu rwego rwo kurwanya indwara no kugabanya impfu z'abana.
Umunsi Mpuzamahanga wo Gukaraba Intoki ni urundi rugero rw'ubukangurambaga bwo gukangurira abantu guhinduka mu myitwarire. Mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya Koronavirusi cya 2019-20, UNICEF yashyizeho gahunda yo gukangurira abantu gukoresha agace ka emoji kavuga ko umuntu agomba gukaraba intoki.
Hari inyigo zimwe na zimwe zasuzumye agaciro rusange ko gukaraba intoki mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere mu rwego rwo kwirinda DALYs.
Icyakora, isuzuma ryakozwe ryerekanye ko gukaraba intoki ukoresheje isabune ari byo by'ingenzi cyane kurusha gukoresha andi mazi n'isuku.
Akamaro ko gukaraba intoki ku buzima bw'abantu - cyane cyane ku bantu bafite ibibazo bikomeye, nk'ababyeyi babyaye cyangwa abasirikare bakomeretse mu bitaro - bwa mbere bwemejwe n'abavugizi babiri b'isuku y'intoki mu kinyejana cya 19 rwagati: umuganga w'Umunya-Hongiriya witwa Ignaz Semmelweis wakoreye i Vienne, muri Otirishiya na Florence Nightingale, Umwongereza "uwashinze ubuforomo bw'ubuforomo bwa none".
Icyo gihe abantu benshi batekerezaga ko indwara ziterwa n'impumuro mbi cyane yitwa miasmus.
Mu myaka ya 1980, indwara ziterwa n'ibiribwa n'ubwandu bwa virusi byateye ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) gushyira ingufu mu gusukura intoki nk'uburyo bwo kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Icyorezo cya Swine Flu mu 2009 n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu 2020 byatumye ibihugu byinshi byongera ubumenyi ku kamaro ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune mu kwirinda indwara zandura nk'izi.
Urugero, amasanamu y'amafoto yerekana "uburyo bukwiye bwo gukaraba intoki" yashyizwe ku bwiherero bw'abantu benshi mu Budage, mu nzu z'ibiro n'ahantu ho gukarabira intoki ku kibuga cy'indege.
Imvugo ngo " gukaraba intoki " mu kintu, yumvikanisha ko umuntu atemera ko afite icyo ari cyo cyose cyamuteye gukora icyo cyaha cyangwa kuba yaragikoze.
Ni amagambo yo muri Bibiliya, ahereye ku gice cyo muri Matayo aho Ponsiyo Pilato yirengagije umwanzuro wo kubamba Yesu Kristo, ariko yaje kuba amagambo akoreshwa cyane mu miryango y'Icyongereza.
Muri Macbeth ya Shakespeare, Lady Macbeth atangira gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'agashinyaguro agerageza kwihanaguraho ikizinga cy'igihimbano kigaragaza umutimanama we umujyaho urubanza ku byaha yakoze no ku cyatumye umugabo we akora ibyo byaha.
Nanone, byagaragaye ko abantu bakaraba intoki kenshi cyane kurusha abandi, nyuma yo kwibuka cyangwa gutekereza ku bikorwa by'ubwiyandarike, kandi bagashyiraho uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki kurusha abandi.
Byongeye kandi, abantu bemerewe gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gutekereza gutya, ntibashobora gukora indi mirimo y'ubwitange yo "gukaraba" nk'ubwitange ku bushake.
Amadini atangaza ko gukaraba intoki ari ngombwa haba mu rwego rw'isuku ndetse no mu rwego rw'ikigereranyo. Gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo ukoresheje amazi adafite isabune ni kimwe mu bigize umuhango wo gukaraba intoki uvugwa mu madini menshi, harimo idini rya Baha'i, idini ry'Abahindu, Tewhila n'Abategiteri Yadayim mu idini ry'Abayuda, Lavabo mu idini rya Gikristo, na Wazu mu idini rya Isilamu.
Mu idini ry'Abahindu, Abayahudi n'Abayisilamu, gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero ni itegeko.
Kandi, mu idini ry'Abahindu, Ababuda, Abasiki, Abayahudi n'Abisilamu, gukaraba intoki mbere yo kurya na nyuma yo kurya ni itegeko.
Gucunga ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19 ku kazi
Uburyo bwo kurwanya ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19 mu kazi ni uburyo bwo gukoresha ubuziranenge n'ubuziranenge mu kazi mu kwirinda no gukumira icyorezo cya Koronavirusi 2019 (COVID-19).
Uburyo bwo kugenzura ibyago byo kwandura indwara ku kazi bushingiye ku kazi n'ibikorwa, hashingiwe ku isesengura ry'ibyago by'abanduye, ku buremere bw'indwara mu baturage, no ku mpamvu zitera abantu kwibasirwa na COVID-19.
Nk'uko bitangazwa n'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe umutekano n'ubuzima ku kazi (OSHA), ibikorwa birimo ibyago byo guhura n'abandi bifite aho bihuriye n'abandi, kandi mu gihe bikenewe, ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura z'abantu ni izi zikurikira: gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, gukurikiza amabwiriza yo guhumeka, no gusukura no kuvura buri gihe ahantu bakorera.
Akazi gashobora guteza ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19 ni ako umuntu agomba guhura kenshi cyangwa akabana n'abantu batazi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba baranduye COVID-19, ariko bashobora kuba baranduye kubera ko bakwirakwizwa mu baturage cyangwa se bitewe n'ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Muri abo harimo abakozi bahura n'abaturage, urugero nko mu mashuri, ahantu hakorerwa imirimo irimo abantu benshi, n'ahandi hakorerwa imirimo y'ubucuruzi.
Uretse ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu, ingamba zo kurwanya ibyago muri iri tsinda zirimo: kwanduza hakoreshejwe indorerwamo z'umwuka zifite ubushobozi buhambaye, gukoresha udukingirizo tw'ubwirinzi, no gushyiraho ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku buryo umuntu ashobora kwiyahura mu gihe ahuye n'umuntu wanduye COVID-19.
OSHA ivuga ko abashinzwe ubuzima n'abakora mu nzu y'ubutabazi bw'abapfuye bafite ibyago byinshi byo guhura n'umuntu ufite cyangwa ukekwaho kuba arwaye COVID-19, kandi ko ibyo bishobora kwiyongera mu gihe abo bakozi bakora ibikorwa byo gukwirakwiza umwuka ku muntu ufite cyangwa ukekwaho kuba afite COVID-19, cyangwa bakorakoranya cyangwa bagakoresha ibizamini kuri uwo muntu.
Mu nzego z'umutekano zifite akamaro kuri aba bakozi harimo inzego z'ubwubatsi, urugero nk'icyumba cy'amagare y'umuriro n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku kazi.
Ingaruka z'icyorezo cya COVID-19 ku kazi zishobora kuba nyinshi.
Abakozi bashobora gusiba akazi bitewe n'uburwayi, gukenera kwita ku bandi cyangwa gutinya ko bashobora guhura n'abandi.
Imyambarire y'ubucuruzi ishobora guhinduka bitewe n'ibintu bicyenewe n'uburyo bwo kubigeraho (urugero nko kugura ibintu mu gihe ibyifuzwa ari bike cyangwa gutanga cyangwa se kugura ibintu binyuze mu buryo bw'itumanaho).
Icya nyuma, ni uko urujya n'uruza rw'ibintu biva mu turere two mu turere twugarijwe cyane na COVID-19 rushobora guhungabana. Gutegura n'igikorwa cyo guhangana n'indwara y'ubwandu bishobora gukoreshwa mu kuyobora ibikorwa byo kwirinda.
Izo gahunda zireba ibyiciro by'ibyago by'akazi bitandukanye n'imirimo y'akazi, harimo ibyago bituruka ku masoko y'ibyago, ibyago bituruka mu ngo no mu miryango, n'ibyago ku bakozi ku giti cyabo nk'iza bukuru cyangwa indwara zidakira.
Nanone kandi, bagaragaza ingamba z'ubutabazi n'ingamba zo guhangana n'imimerere ishobora kuvuka bitewe n'icyorezo.
Gahunda zo kwitegura no guhangana n'indwara zandura zishobora kuba zigengwa n'amabwiriza y'igihugu cyangwa y'akarere.
Intego z'ibisubizo ku cyorezo ni izi zikurikira: kugabanya ikwirakwizwa ry'indwara mu bakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara, gukomeza ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku bindi bice bigize umurongo w'ubucuruzi.
Uburemere bw'indwara mu baturage aho umukozi akorera, bugira ingaruka ku buryo abantu babyifatamo.
Urutonde rw'ubugenga bw'ibyago ni uburyo bukoreshwa cyane mu gukusanya ingufu z'ibyago mu rwego rw'ubuziranenge mu by'ubuzima n'umutekano ku kazi.
Mu gihe ibyago bya COVID-19 bidashobora gukurwaho, uburyo bwiza bwo kubirwanya ni ugukurikirana ubuhanga, gukurikirwa n'ubuyobozi, hanyuma n'ibikoresho birinda umuntu.
Ingengabihe y'ubwubatsi ikubiyemo gutandukanya abakozi n'akaga kabaho mu gihe bakora akazi batitaye ku myitwarire y'abakozi, kandi ishobora kuba ari bwo buryo buhendutse bwo kubishyira mu bikorwa.
Amabwiriza y'ubuyobozi ni impinduka mu mikorere y'akazi cyangwa mu mikorere isaba ko umukozi cyangwa umukoresha agira icyo akora.
Ikoreshwa ry'ibikoresho birinda umuntu (PPE) ridahuje n'ubuyobozi n'ubwubatsi, ariko bishobora gufasha mu gukumira abantu bamwe na bamwe.
Abakozi bagomba kumenya uburyo bwa PPE bukoreshwa, bakagena uburyo bukoreshwa bitewe n'akaga, bakambara neza (urugero: imashini z'ubuhumekero), bakambara buri gihe kandi neza, bakagenzurwa buri gihe, bagakoreshwa neza, bakagurwa igihe cyose bibaye ngombwa, bakagirwa isuku, bakagirwa neza, bakagirwa ibikoresho byiza, bakagirwa ibikoresho byiza, bakagirwa ibikoresho byiza.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe umutekano n'ubuzima (OSHA), akazi gatuma umuntu atagerwaho n'ubushyamirane mu kazi, ni akazi katuma umuntu atagerwaho n'abantu cyangwa n'abandi bakozi.
Ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura zasabwe ahantu hose hakorerwa imirimo harimo: gukaraba intoki kenshi kandi neza, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, gushyiraho uburyo bwo guhumeka buzibuza umuntu guhumeka no gukorora, gutanga imitobe y'amatembabuzi n'imyanda, gutegura imyenda yo guhanahana cyangwa iy'amabara mu gihe bibaye ngombwa, guca intege abakozi gukoresha ibikoresho n'ibikoresho by'abandi, no guhora basukura no gusukura neza aho bakorera.
Kumenya no gushyira mu kato abantu bashobora kwandura ku kazi hakiri kare ni intambwe y'ingenzi mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abashyitsi n'abandi.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara no kuzirinda (CDC) gitanga inama y'uko abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara yo guhumeka bakomeza kuguma mu rugo igihe cyose bamaze nibura amasaha 24 badafite ibisebe, ibimenyetso by'umuriro cyangwa ibindi bimenyetso, nta miti cyangwa ibindi bikoresho bigabanya umuriro, kandi ko politiki z'ikiruhuko cyo kubura akazi ari nziza, ko abakozi bemerewe kuguma mu rugo kugira ngo bite ku muntu wo mu muryango urwaye, kandi ko abakozi bamenyeshwa izo politiki.
Nk'uko OSHA ibivuga, ibikorwa birimo ibyago byo guhura n'abantu byiganjemo ibikorwa bisaba guhura kenshi cyangwa hafi y'abantu bari muri metero esheshatu (1.8m) batazi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba bafite COVID-19, ariko bashobora kuba baranduye SARS-CoV-2 kubera ko bakwirakwije mu baturage hafi y'aho bakorera, cyangwa kubera ko uwo muntu aherutse kujya mu mahanga ahantu hakwirakwizwa COVID-19.
Muri ibyo harimo abakozi bafite aho bahurira n'abaturage nka za kaminuza, aho bakorera hari umubare munini w'abaturage, ndetse n'ibigo by'ubucuruzi bifite ibiciro byinshi. Ku bantu bafite ibyago byo kwandura iyi ndwara, gushyira filtere z'umwuka zifite ubushobozi bwinshi mu nzego z'ubwubatsi, kongera ingano y'abanduye, gushyiraho inzitizi z'umubiri nk'urukuta rw'isuku rw'isuku rw'ibyuma bibuza abantu kwinjira mu nzu, no gushyiraho amadirishya yo mu rugo kugira ngo abakiriya babone aho bajya. Ku bantu bafite ibyago byo kwandura iyi ndwara, gushyiraho inzego z'ubuyobozi mu nzego z'ubuyobozi, gushishikariza abakozi barwaye kuguma mu rugo, gushyiraho udupfukamunwa, gushyiraho udupfukamunwa, kwirinda ingendo zidakenewe mu bice bya COVID-19, gushyiraho gahunda yo gutangiza amakuru, gushyiraho uburyo bwo guhangana n'abantu bafite ibyago byo kwandura iyi ndwara, gushyiraho uburyo bwo guhangana n'imikoranabuhanga bwo kwirinda COVID-19 cyangwa gukoresha uburyo bushya bw'imikoranabuhanga, guha abakozi bafite ibyago by'ubuzima bwite, gukoresha ibikoresho byo gukingira no gukingira abantu, guha abakiriya myenda, gukoranabuhanga n'imyitonde, ndetse no guha abakozi uburyo bwo kwihanganira, gukingira no gukoresha ibikoresho by'isuku, ndetse n'imyenda bikoreshwa n'abandi.
Abakozi bo muri iki cyiciro cy'abantu bafite ibyago, ni gake cyane baba bakeneye gukoresha ibyuma bibarinda guhumeka.
Iyo umuntu arwaye mu ndege, ingamba z'umutekano ku bw'umutekano w'abakozi n'abandi bagenzi zigomba kuba zirimo: kumushyira kure y'abandi bagera kuri metero 6, gushyiraho umuntu wo mu ndege kugira ngo amwiteho, no kumuha agapfukamunwa cyangwa kumusaba ko yakwipfuka mu kanwa no mu mazuru igihe arwaye.
Abakozi bagomba kwambara imyenda y'ubuvuzi ikoreshwa igihe bita ku mukerarugendo urwaye cyangwa igihe bakoreye ku mazi y'umubiri cyangwa ku bintu bishobora kuba byanduye, kandi bashobora kwambara ibindi bikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku giti cyabo mu gihe umurwayi afite umuriro, agakunda gukorora cyangwa akabirirwa guhumeka.
Impuguke mu by'impanuka zirinda abantu kurwara, guhagarika ingendo igihe barwaye, kwitarura abandi no guhita babimenyesha ikigo cy'ubuvuzi iyo umuntu yagize umuriro cyangwa ibindi bimenyetso by'indwara mu gihe bari mu bwato.
Ubusanzwe, gukurikirana kwa muganga bigomba gukorwa mu cyumba cy'umuntu wahawe akato. Ku mashuri n'ibigo nderabuzima, CDC isaba ko habaho gufunga by'igihe gito kugira ngo umuntu aruhuke cyangwa yanduze niba umuntu wanduye yari mu nyubako y'ishuri itarimo ubwandu bw'icyorezo.
Iyo ubwandu bw'agakoko bwabayeho ku rugero rwo hasi cyangwa rwo hagati, ingamba zo guhana intera zishobora gukurikizwa, nko gusura ahantu hamwe, guteranira hamwe no guteranira hamwe mu yandi materaniro manini, nko gusiba amasomo y'imyitozo ngororangingo cyangwa guteranira hamwe mu byumba by'ishuri cyangwa mu nzu yo kuriramo, kongera intera hagati y'ameza, guhuza amasaha yo kwinjira n'ayo gusohoka, kugabanya abaza mu nzu batabikeneye cyane, no gukoresha ahantu hatandukanye ho mu biro by'ubuzima ku bana bagaragaza ibimenyetso nk'ibi by'ibicurane.
Igihe mu baturage hari ubwandu buhagije, gahunda yo kwagura amasomo ashobora gusuzumwa, hiyongereyeho ingamba zo kwirinda. Ku bakozi bashinzwe kubahiriza amategeko bakora imirimo ya buri munsi, ibyago by'ubuzima CDC ibona ko ari bike.
Abapolisi bagomba guhura n'abantu bagaragayeho cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19 basabwa gukurikiza amabwiriza nk'ayahabwa n'abaganga b'ibanze, harimo no kwambara imyenda y'ubwirinzi.
Niba hari aho bahuriye cyane mu gihe bafata, abakozi bagomba gusukura no guhagarika imiti bakoresheje imiti yo mu rugo, bakoresha imiti yo guhanagura cyangwa imyanda, mbere yo kongera gukoresha imyenda yabo n'imyambaro, kandi bagakurikiza uburyo bwo gukora bwemewe bwo gukaraba no guteka PPE zakoreshejwe.
OSHA ivuga ko bamwe mu bakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima n'abakora mu by'ubutabazi bw'abapfuye bari mu byiciro by'abantu bafite ibyago byo kwandura indwara z'ubuhumyi cyangwa se ibyago byo kwandura indwara z'ubuhumyi bikabije.
Mu mirimo ifite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura harimo gutanga ubuvuzi, gufasha, abakozi bo muri laboratwari n'abakozi bo mu ngendo z'abaganga bahura n'abarwayi bazwiho cyangwa bakekwaho kuba barwaye COVID-19.
Aba bantu baba bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura cyane iyo abakozi bakora ibikorwa byo gukusanya cyangwa gutwara ibipimo ku barwayi bazwi cyangwa bikekwaho kuba bafite COVID-19.
Imikorere ituma habaho umwuka woherezwa mu kirere, ni nk'imiti yo mu muhogo, gutwikira mu mazuru, gukoresha ikoranabuhanga rya bronchoscopy, bimwe mu bikorwa by'amenyo n'ibizamini, cyangwa gufata icyitegererezo binyuze mu gusya.
Ibikorwa byo gupima imirambo bifite ibyago byinshi byo guhura na byo bikubiyemo abantu batunganya imibiri y'abantu bafite ibimenyetso bizwi cyangwa bikekwa ko banduye COVID-19 igihe bapfaga; iyo bapimwe, baba bafite ibyago byinshi byo guhura. Ibindi byiciro by'ubugenzuzi bw'ubwubatsi ku bantu bafite ibyago, harimo no gutunganya ibyumba byo gutandukanya abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazwi cyangwa bikekwaho ko banduye, harimo no gukora ibikorwa by'ubugenzuzi bw'imirasire y'izuba.
Mu bigo bimwe na bimwe by'ubuzima n'ubutabazi, hashobora gukoreshwa uburyo bwihariye bwo guhererekanya ibikomere.
Ibipimo bigomba gukoreshwa mu bwitonzi n'ubwirinzi bwo mu rwego rw'ubuziranenge 3.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ryategetse ko abarwayi binjira mu bitaro bagomba gushyirwa mu byumba bitandukanye bitewe n'uko bakekwaho COVID-19. Usibye PPE, OSHA itegeka ko abantu bakora mu birometero 6 by'abarwayi bazwiho cyangwa bakekwaho kwandura SARS-CoV-2, n'abakora ibikorwa by'ubwirinzi bw'umwuka, bagomba kwambara imyanya y'ubuhumekero.
Muri Amerika, N95 Filter Facepiece Breathing Machine cyangwa iyirushijeho yemewe na NIOSH igomba gukoreshwa mu gihe hari gahunda yo gukingira guhumeka, yanditswe, ikubiyemo gupima, amahugurwa no gusuzumwa kwa muganga.
Ubundi bwoko bw'imashini z'ubuhumekero zishobora gutanga umutekano mwinshi kandi zikongera ubudahangarwa bw'abakozi. OMS ntiyamamaza imashini z'ubuhumekero, kubera ko COVID-19 ari indwara y'ubuhumekero aho gukwirakwizwa n'imyanda.
OMS isaba ko abashinzwe gupima abarwayi mu gihe binjiye mu gihugu bambara agapfukamunwa kamwe.
Ku bantu bakusanya, bitaho cyangwa batwara ibipimo by'ubwonko ku barwayi ba COVID-19 badafite uburyo bwo kubonesha umwuka, WHO isaba ko bambara udukingirizo tw'ubuvuzi, udukingirizo tw'amaso, amakoti n'utubati.
Iyo habayeho igikorwa cyo guhumura hakoreshejwe umwuka, agapfukamunwa gashobora gusimbuzwa akandi gakoreshwa nk'imashini yo guhumura N95 cyangwa FFP2.
Bamaze kubona ko ibyo ku isi bidahagije, OMS isaba ko hakorwa telemedicine, hakagendeye ku nzitizi z'umubiri nk'amadirishya y'izuba, abantu bari mu buryo bwo kwita ku barwayi gusa bakemererwa kwinjira mu cyumba kimwe n'umurwayi wa COVID-19, hakakoreshwa PPE ikenewe gusa mu gihe cy'akazi, hakoreshwa impuguke imwe idakoreshwa mu gihe cy'abarwayi benshi bafite uburwayi bumwe, hakagendewe ku kugenzura no guhuza aho PPE igeze, hakanahagarikwa gukoresha udupfukamunwa ku barwayi bakomeje kwihishira.
