Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) ni ingirabuzimafatizo ifitanye isano n'uruhu rw'inyuma rw'ingirabuzimafatizo (urwungano rw'ingirabuzimafatizo) mu bihaha, mu mitsi, mu mutima, mu mpyiko no mu mara.
ACE2 ihindura imikorere ya enzymes zihindura angiotensin (ACE) mu kugabanya ingano ya angiotensin-II no kongera angiotensin (1-7), bigatuma iba umuti wizewe mu kuvura indwara z'umutima. ACE2 ikora kandi nk'ahantu koronavirus zimwe zinjirira mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Abantu bakoresha iyo poroteyine yitwa hACE2.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 ni meteloenzyme irimo zinc iri mu nda no ku zindi ntanga z'ingirabuzimafatizo.
ACE2 ifite N-terminal peptidase M2 domain na C-terminal collectrin kidney amino acid transporter domains.
ACE2 ni poroteyine yo mu bwoko bwa I ikurura iboneza ifite ahantu ikora ibintu by'ubwoko bwa enzymes, ikorera ku turemangingo tw'ibice by'umubiri bita epithelium, mu bihaha no mu bindi bice by'umubiri.
Agace ka ACE2 ko mu ngingo kavanwa mu kindi gice cy'ingirabuzima kitwa Shadease, maze kavanamo poroteyine zikomoka muri ako gace, zikajya mu maraso, amaherezo zikajya mu musarani.
ACE2 iba mu bice by'umubiri hafi ya byose: ACE2 iba mu bice by'umubiri by'umwihariko mu gice cy'umutsi w'umwingo w'umwingo wa II w'ibice by'umubiri by'umwingo by'ibihaha, mu maraso y'utwugingo tw'umwimerere duto, mu bice by'umwingo by'umwimerere w'umwimerere w'amaraso, mu bice by'umwimerere by'umwimerere w'amaraso, mu bice by'umwimerere by'amaraso, mu mitsi y'umwimerere w'umwimerere w'umwimerere w'amaraso no mu bice by'umwimerere w'umwimerere w'umwimerere w'umwimerere w'umwimerere.
ACE2 mRNA igaragara mu gice cy'ubwonko, mu gice cyo mu nda, mu gice cy'iburyo cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'iburyo cy'ubwonko cyitwa hypothalamus no mu gice cy'ubwonko cyitwa column.
Icyambere ACE2 ikora ni ugukomeza ACE.
ACE ihindura ingufu za angiotensin I zikaba ingufu za angiotensin II.
ACE2 isambura karboksil-terminal amino acide phenylalanine ikayivana muri angiotensin II (Asp -Arg -Val -Tyr -Ile -His-Pro -Phe) ikayivana mu mazi ikayivana mu gikora nk'umuyoboro w'amaraso (angiotensin) (1-7), (H -Asp -Arg -Val -Tyr -Ile -His -Pro -OH).
ACE2 [des-Arg9] - bredicainine ishobora kandi gusenya izindi peptides nyinshi zirimo epelin, neurotensin, dinorphin A na ghrelin.
ACE2 kandi igenzura uburyo ubwandu bwa SLC6A19 buhererekanya amine acide ya transport, ikaba yaragaragaye mu ndwara ya Hartnup.
Nk'imyororokere, ACE2 ikora nk'ahantu h'ingenzi hakwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo za virusi zimwe na zimwe za koronavirusi, harimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (agakoko gateye SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (agakoko gatera COVID-19).
By'umwihariko, ikoranabuhanga rya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 ryo guhuza poroteyine ya S1 n'ubuso bw'ingirabuzima bwa ACE2 ku isura y'ingirabuzima, bituma virusi na za enzymes byombi bihinduka endosomes ziboneka mu ngirabuzima nkoranya kandi zigakora endositosis.
Ubwo buryo bwo kwinjira mu mubiri bukenera ko S protein igenda itera imbere binyuze mu ntungamubiri yitwa serine protease TMPRSS2, ubu buryo bwo kuyihagarika ubu aribwo bugenzurwa nk'uburyo bwo kuvura bushobora kuba bwiza. Kubera iyo mpamvu, bamwe batekereje ko kugabanya urugero rwa ACE2 mu mubiri bishobora gufasha mu kurwanya ubwandu.
Icyakora, inzego z'ubuvuzi n'inzego z'ubugenzuzi nyinshi zasabye ko hakomeza gukoreshwa imiti isanzwe yitwa ACE inhibitors na ARBs.
Isuzuma ryakozwe mu buryo bw'imikorere n'ubusesenguzi bw'ibisobanuro by'ibanze, byasohotse ku itariki ya 11 Nyakanga 2012, byagaragaje ko "gukoresha ACE inhibitors byaragabanutseho 34% mu birebana n'ibyago byo kurwara indwara y'umwijima, ugereranyije no kugenzura".
Byongeye kandi, "Umugera wa pneumonia na wo waragabanutse mu barwayi bavurwaga n'ibiyobyabwenge bya ACE, bari bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara pneumonia, cyane cyane mu barwaye indwara yo guhinda umushyitsi no kutagira umutima.
Gukoresha ACE inhibitors na byo byajyaniranye no kugabanya impfu ziterwa n'indwara z'impumuro, nubwo ingaruka zabyo zagabanutse ugereranyije n'ibyago byo kurwara indwara y'impumuro".
Igisonga cy'umuntu ACE2 (rhACE2) kifatwa nk'ubuvuzi bushya bwo kuvura imyanya y'ubuhumekero, kandi cyagaragaye ko cyatumye impinja z'ingurube zifite indwara y'ubuhumekero bukomeye iterwa na lipopolysaccharide, zongera guhumeka neza mu bihaha no kongera umwuka wa oxygène.
Muri abantu, igice cy'ubuzima cy'ubwoko bwa rhACE2 ni nk'amasaha 10 kandi itangira gukora mu minota 30, ikora mu gihe cy'amasaha 24.
Ibisubizo byinshi byerekana ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti mwiza ku bantu bafite ubwiyumanganye ku bibuza RAS (Ranin-angiotensin-system inhibitors) cyangwa indwara z'imitsi z'imitsi zifite ingano y'ibice by'ingenzi by'umubiri (Angioinsufficiency II). rhACE2 y'umwimerere yagiye igeragerezwa mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi mu kuvura indwara z'ubuhumekero.
Porogaramu za COVID-19 ni porogaramu zigendanwa zakozwe mu rwego rwo gufasha mu buryo bwo kumenya abantu bashobora kuba barahuye n'umuntu wanduye, mu rwego rwo guhangana n'icyorezo cya Koronavirusi 2019-20.
Hari porogaramu z'ikoranabuhanga zagiye zikorwa cyangwa zitezwa imbere muri za pariki no mu turere zimwe na zimwe zifashishijwe inkunga ya leta.
Hari uburyo bw'imiterere bwashyizweho mu rwego rwo kubaka porogaramu yo gushakisha abahuye n'umuntu.
Hari impungenge z'ibanga, cyane cyane ku birebana n'uburyo bwo gukurikirana aho abakoresha porogaramu bari.
Uburyo bwo kugenzura budafite aho buhuriye cyane n'ubwo bwa mbere, ni ugukoresha ibimenyetso bya Bluetooth kugira ngo umenye aho umuntu ari hafi y'undi muntu.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byatangaje ko bizashyira hamwe ubushobozi bwo gufasha izi porogaramu za Bluetooth mu buryo bworoshye, binyuze mu buryo bwa Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, leta y'Ubushinwa yashyizeho porogaramu ifatanyije na Alipay, ituma abaturage bashobora kugenzura niba barigeze guhura n'umuntu urwaye COVID-19.
Ikoreshwa mu mijyi irenga 200 yo mu Bushinwa. Muri Singapore, porogaramu yitwa TraceTogether iri gukoreshwa.
Porogaramu yakozwe n'umuryango wa IT wo muri ako gace, yashyizwe ku isoko igatangwa ku mugaragaro, kandi izahabwa leta. Macedonia y'Amajyaruguru yatangije porogaramu ikoresha Bluetooth "StopKorona!" kugira ngo igaragaze abantu bashobora kuba baranduye, kandi itange igisubizo ku nzego z'ubuzima.
Iyi porogaramu yakozwe na Minisiteri y'itumanaho n'ikoranabuhanga na Minisiteri y'ubuzima.
Kugeza ku ya 14 Mata 2020, iyi porogaramu yari itegereje ko Google Play Store na Apple App Store biyemeza kuyikoresha.
Ku ya 12 Mata, Guverinoma yavuze ko porogaramu ya contact tracing iri mu cyiciro cy'iterambere, kandi ko izatangira gukoreshwa mu byumweru bike. Porogaramu nk'iyo ("StopCovid") yakoreshejwe muri Ireland no mu Bufaransa.
Australia na New Zealand zombi zirimo gutekereza kuri porogaramu ya TraceTogether yo muri Singapore na BlueTrace Protocol. Uburusiya burashaka gushyiraho porogaramu ya geofencing ku barwayi ba COVID-19 baba i Moscou, yagenewe kubabuza kuva mu rugo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu wigisha iby'umutekano wa mudasobwa muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge, yagaragaje ibibazo byinshi bishobora kubaho ku ikoreshwa rya porogaramu, harimo no kubura uburyo bwo gukora neza iyo porogaramu ikoreshwa n'abantu bake.
Mu rwego rwo gukemura impungenge ku ikwirakwizwa rya porogaramu za "coronavirus" zangiza cyangwa zangiza, Apple yashyizeho amategeko agena ubwoko bw'imiryango ishobora gushyira porogaramu zifitanye isano na coronavirus muri App Store yayo, ikayegera gusa imiryango "yemewe" cyangwa icyubahwa.
Google na Amazon na byo byashyizeho ingamba nk'izo.
Abakangurambaga mu by'ibanga bagaragaje impungenge ku bijyanye n'ingaruka zo kugenzura abantu benshi bakoresheje porogaramu za Koronavirusi, cyane cyane niba ibikorwaremezo by'igenzura byashyizweho mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya Koronavirusi bizasenywa igihe iyi mpanuka izaba imaze gushira.
Amnesty International n'indi miryango isaga 100 yasohoye itangazo rivuga ku mipaka y'ubwo bugenzuzi.
Imiryango yashyize mu bikorwa bya Leta ibintu umunani:
Igenzura rigomba kuba "ryemewe, rikenewe kandi rifite aho rihuriye n'ibikwiriye";
Kuba hari ingingo ya nyuma igaragaza ibisobanuro birambuye by'ubugenzuzi n'igenzura;
Gukoresha amakuru bigomba kuba bigenewe gusa ibijyanye n'ubwandu bwa COVID-19;
Umutekano w'amakuru n'ubusobanuro bw'amazina bigomba kurindwa kandi bigakorwaho nk'aho birinze kubera ko hari ibimenyetso bihamya ko ari byo;
Gukurikirana mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga bigomba kwirinda gushyigikira ivangura no kubangamira uburenganzira bw'abandi;
Gusangiza amakuru ku bandi, bigomba gusobanurwa n'amategeko;
Uburyo bwo kurengera uburenganzira bw'abaturage mu gihe habaye ihohoterwa n'uburyo bwo guhangana na ryo;
"Gushyira hamwe mu buryo bw'ingirakamaro" n'abo bireba bose, harimo n'abahanga mu by'ubuzima rusange n'imiryango idafite ubuzimagatozi, bizasabwa. Urutonde rw'abantu bagomba gusuzumwa rwatanzwe na The German Chaos Computer Club (CCC) na Reporters Without Borders (RSF).
Gahunda ya Google / Apple igamije gukemura ikibazo cy'igenzura ry'igihe cyose, ikuraho uburyo bwo gukurikirana ku bikoresho byabo by'imikorere igihe bidakenewe.
Ibihugu bimwe byakoresheje uburyo bwo gukurikirana aho umuntu ari aho akorera, bikuraho kuba bisaba ko umuntu akoresha porogaramu cyangwa se akirinda ko yakurikiranwa.
Muri Isirayeli, hakoreshejwe ikoranabuhanga rya interineti, byemewe.
Ibisubizo by'urusobe bifite amakuru y'ahantu y'ibanze, bishobora kugira ibibazo by'ibanga.
Icyakora, si ko buri shyirahamwe ifite mudasobwa ikora nk'ibanga ryayo bwite; hari na gahunda nyinshi z'ububiko zishinzwe gukoresha mudasobwa nk'ibanga gusa mu gushyikirana hagati yazo (reba igice kiri hasi).
Muri Koreya y'Epfo, hakoreshejwe uburyo butari porogaramu bugamije gukurikirana abo bantu.
Aho gukoresha porogaramu yihariye, iyi porogaramu yakusanyije amakuru y'ibarurishamibare, harimo amakuru y'ibarurishamibare yo ku bikoresho bya telefoni n'amakuru y'ibicuruzwa bya karita, maze iyi mikoreshereze ifatanya kugira ngo abantu bashobora kuba baranduye bamenyeshwe hakoreshejwe ubutumwa bugufi.
Usibye gukoresha aya makuru mu gukangurira abantu bashobora kuba bafite aho bahuriye n'abandi, leta yashyize ku mugaragaro amakuru y'ahantu kubera impinduka zikomeye mu mategeko agenga ibanga ry'amakuru nyuma y'uko MERS yongeye kwaduka muri icyo gihugu.
Aya makuru aboneka mu ruhame binyuze mu masosiyete n'imbuga nkoranyambaga. Ibihugu byinshi, harimo n'Ubudage, byatekereje gukoresha uburyo bwo gucunga no kurinda ubuzima bwite.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 6 Mata 2020, aya makuru yari atarajya ahagaragara.
