Muri izi porogaramu, amakuru ashobora kumenyekana ku muntu n'umwe ntajya hanze y'igikoresho, kandi yose aba ari kuri icyo gikoresho gihuye.
Itsinda rya The Privacy Group muri MIT Media Lab ririmo gukora SafePaths, urubuga rwo gukoresha ikoranabuhanga ryo kurinda ubuzima bwite mu gihe bakusanya no gukoresha amakuru y'ahantu cyangwa ahantu hahurira abantu kugira ngo barebe uko COVID-19 ikwirakwira.
Ni ubushakashatsi bushingiye ku nyandiko y'ibanze "Apps Gone Rogue: Maintaining Personal Privacy in the Epidemic" yashyizwe ahagaragara muri Werurwe 2020. Igikorwa nk'iki ni SafeTrace cyakozwe na Enigma MPC, ikigo gikora ikoranabuhanga mu gucunga ubuzima bwite, cyatangijwe mu cyiciro cya mbere muri MIT Media Lab.
SafeTrace ikoresha ikoranabuhanga rikoresha ibyuma bifitiye umutekano, rifasha abakoresha gusangira amakuru y'imyanya n'ubuzima n'abandi bakoresha n'abategetsi, batishora mu ibanga ry'amakuru.
Ku ya 5 Mata 2020, ihuriro mpuzamahanga TCN ryashinzwe n'amatsinda y'abantu benshi bahuriye ku buryo bumwe bw'imikorere n'ingamba zihariye, hagamijwe kugabanya amacakubiri, no guhuza imikoreshereze y'imikorere ya porogaramu zo gushakisha no kuburira, ari nacyo kintu cy'ingenzi mu kugera ku iterambere.
Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, Guverinoma ya Singapore yatangaje ko yafunguriye isoko ya BlueTrace ikoreshwa na porogaramu yayo yemewe ya leta.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple, ibigo bigenga Android na iOS, byatangaje gahunda yo gukurikirana, aho bavuze ko bizarinda ubuzima bwite bushingiye ku buhanga bwa Bluetooth bufite ingufu nkeya hamwe na cryptographie ibungabunga ubuzima bwite.
Yatangaje kandi imiterere y'ikoranabuhanga rikoreshwa muri iyo gahunda.
