Gusimbuza umuti indi (byitwa no gusimbuza umuti, gusubiramo cyangwa guhindura uburyo bwo kuwukoresha) ni ugusubiramo umuti wemewe kuwukoresha mu kuvura indwara cyangwa indwara itandukanye n'iyo yawutangiriyeho.
Ni uburyo bw'ubushakashatsi bwa siyansi bugamije gukora imiti itangiza COVID-19 mu buryo burambye.
Ubundi bushakashatsi burimo gukorana n'abantu kugira ngo hakorwe urukingo rwa COVID-19 no kuzana mu mubiri udukoko dutandukanye tw'imikorere y'umubiri. SARS-CoV-2 ifite poroteyine zigera kuri 66 z'ubushake, buri imwe muri zo ikaba ifite ahantu henshi ishobora guhuza udukoko.
Isesengura ry'ibyo bice by'ubuhumekero ritanga umushinga mwiza wo gukora umuti wa virusi ushobora kurinda COVID-19.
Amarote y'ingenzi SARS-CoV-2 yibasiye ni amarote y'igitsina kimwe, RNA ishingiye kuri RNA polymerase, helicase, poroteyine S na ADP ribophosphate.
Hussain n'abandi bakoze ubushakashatsi ku nkingo nyinshi z'inkingo, nyuma zongera gukoreshwa no gusesengurwa ku bijyanye n'uburyo zimeze nk'iz'imiti yemewe kugira ngo zikoreshwe mu buryo bwihuse mu iterambere ry'umuti wa SARS-CoV-2 mu bushakashatsi bwa mbere bw'igerageza kugira ngo haboneke umuti wabigirira akamaro.
Chloroquine ni umuti urwanya malaria, ukoreshwa kandi mu kurinda abantu indwara z'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri.
Ku ya 18 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine bifitanye isano, ari mu miti ine igiye kwigwa mu bushakashatsi bw'ubuvuzi bwa Solidariity.
Guverineri wa New York, Andrew Cuomo, yatangaje ko isuzuma rya leta ya New York rya chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine rizatangira ku ya 24 Werurwe. Ku ya 28 Werurwe, FDA yemeje ikoreshwa rya hydroxychloroquine sulfate na chloroquyl phosphate mu gihe cy'ubuyobozi bwihuta bwo gukoresha (EUA).
Ubu buryo bwo kuvura ntibwemejwe n'igikorwa cyo gupima kwa muganga cya FDA, kandi bwemewe n'amategeko ya EUA nk'uburyo bwo kuvura mu gihe cy'impanuka ku barwayi bari mu bitaro ariko badashobora kuvurwa mu igeragezwa rya muganga.
CDC yavuze ko "ikoreshwa, ingano y'imiti cyangwa igihe cya hydroxychloroquine mu kwirinda cyangwa kuvura SARS-CoV-2" bitaragaragara.
Abaganga bavuze ko bakoreshaga iyo miti "igihe nta yandi mahitamo bari bafite".
Itsinda ry'abashakashatsi bo muri Turukiya bo muri Istanbul barimo gukora ubushakashatsi ku mikorobe ikoreshwa mu gupima chlorokuyini ihuje na zinc, vitamini A, vitamini C na vitamini D.
Hari n'ubushakashatsi bukomeye cyane bukorwa muri Kaminuza ya Duke na Kaminuza ya Oxford.
Ishuri ry'ubuvuzi rya NYU Langone ririmo gukora isuzuma ry'umutekano n'imikorere y'imikoreshereze y'urukingo rwa hydroxychloroquine mu kwirinda.
Ibizamini byo mu Bushinwa byakozwe i Wuhan na Shenzhen byatangaje ko "Favipiravir" igira ingaruka nziza.
Mu mujyi wa Shenzhen, abarwayi 35 bagaragaye ko batanduye mu gihe cy'iminsi 4, mu gihe abarwayi 45 batanduye igihe cyo kurwara cy'iminsi 11.
Mu bushakashatsi bwakorewe ku barwayi 240 bafite indwara y'umwotsi w'amaraso mu mujyi wa Wuhan, kimwe cya kabiri cy'abarwayi bahawe umuti witwa favipiravir, abandi bahawe umuti witwa omifenovir.
Ikigo cy'Ubutaliyani gishinzwe imiti cyibukije abaturage ko ibimenyetso bihari byo gushyigikira uyu muti ari bike kandi ko ari ibya none.
Ku ya 2 Mata, u Budage bwatangaje ko buzakura imiti mu Buyapani kugira ngo ibike, kandi bukoresha ingabo kugira ngo iyo miti yoherezwe mu bitaro bya kaminuza, aho iyo miti izajya ikoreshwa mu kuvura abarwayi ba COVID-19.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'ikinyamakuru South China Morning Post, Shinzo Abe yohereje igitekerezo ku butegetsi bwa Trump cyo kugura uwo muti. Uyu muti ushobora kuba udakora neza cyane mu ndwara zikomeye, aho virusi iba yaramaze kwiyongera.
Ntibyemewe ko umugore utwite cyangwa ugerageza gutwita abyitwaza.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku muti uvura indwara witwa lopinavir/ritonavir (Calatra), wakoragamo umuti uvura indwara uvura indwara witwa lopinavir na ritonavir, bwageze ku mwanzuro w'uko "nta nyungu iboneka".
Iyo miti ikoze mu buryo bwo guhagarika virusi ya SIDA kugira ngo itagenda yikurura binyuze mu guhuza na protease.
Itsinda ry'abashakashatsi bo muri Kaminuza ya Colorado barimo kugerageza guhindura imiti kugira ngo babone ikinyabutabire kizatuma SARS-CoV-2 ikora nk'urwego rwa protease. Mu muryango wa siyansi harimo kunegurwa ko gukoresha umutungo mu buryo bwo kongera gukoresha imiti irimo gukorwa, cyane cyane ku barwayi ba virusi itera sida.
OMS yashyize Lopinavir/Ritonavir mu igerageza mpuzamahanga rya Solidarity.
Remdesivir yakozwe kandi iterwa imbere na Gilead Sciences mu rwego rwo kuvura indwara ya Ebola na virusi ya Marburg. Nyuma yaho Gilead Sciences yaje kumenya ko Remdesivir ifite ibikorwa byo kurwanya virusi by'umwanda byo mu rwego rwo kurinda virusi nyinshi nka filo-, pneumo-, paramix-o na korona.
Ikibazo kimwe mu byo kurwanya virusi ni ukwiyongera kw'ubwihangange buturuka ku mutation zishobora gutera indwara zikomeye no kuyandura.
Hari inyigo zimwe na zimwe z'ibanze zigaragaza ko hari ibyago byinshi byo kuba umuti wa Remdesivir ushobora kugira inzitizi zikomoka ku gitsina. Hari n'ubushakashatsi bukorwa, harimo n'ubundi bushakashatsi bwakozwe n'Ibitaro bya Kaminuza ya Cleveland; bumwe bugamije gusuzuma abantu barwaye indwara yoroheje, ubundi bugamije gusuzuma abantu barwaye indwara zikomeye.
