Ubwanditsi bw'izindi koronavirusi butuma ubwirinzi bushoboka bitewe n'imiterere yabwo, ariko hari abantu bagaragaye basuzumwe ko banduye koronavirusi nyuma yo gukira COVID-19.
Iyi mibare ifatwa nk'aho ari yo y'ubwandu bw'ubwandu butarakira aho kuba ubwandu bwongeye kwiyongera.
Iyi virusi ifite inkomoko ituruka ku nyamaswa, ikaba ishobora kuba yaranduye mu buryo bw'ibanze, kandi ishobora kuba yaranduye abantu.
Inkomoko nyayo ntizwi ariko kugeza mu Ukuboza 2019 ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu ryari ryiganjemo ubwandu bw'abantu ku bantu.
Mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi 41 ba mbere b'icyorezo cya COVID-19 bemejwe, bwasohotse muri Lancet muri Mutarama 2020, bwagaragaje ko itariki ya mbere y'ukwezi kwa 12 k'umwaka wa 2019 ari yo tariki ibimenyetso byatangiriyeho.
Impapuro za OMS z'ibanze zivuga ko ibimenyetso byatangiye kugaragara ku itariki ya 8 Ukuboza 2019.
Hari uburyo bwinshi bukoreshwa mu kumenya umubare w'abahitanwa n'icyorezo.
Iyi mibare ihinduka bitewe n'akarere ndetse n'igihe, kandi igenda ishingiye ku mubare w'abari bapimwe, ireme ry'urwego rw'ubuvuzi, uburyo bwo kuvura, igihe cy'icyorezo cyatangiye, n'ibintu biranga abaturage, urugero nk'imyaka, igitsina n'ubuzima muri rusange.
Mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2019, OMS yashyizeho kode y'indwara ya ICD-10 y'ubuvuzi y'ibanze U07.1 ku bantu bapfuye bazize ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bwemejwe na laboratwari, na kode y'indwara U07.2 ku bantu bapfuye bazize COVID-19 yabonetse mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi cyangwa bw'icyorezo idafite SARS-CoV-2 yemejwe na laboratwari.
Dukurikije imibare y'ishami rya kaminuza rya Johns Hopkins, kugeza ku ya 17 Mata 2020, umubare w'abanduye n'abamaze gupfa ku isi wari 6.9% (153,822/2,240,191).
Ibindi bipimo ni urugero rw'umubare w'abapfa (CFR), rugaragaza umubare w'abantu bapfuye bazize indwara runaka, n'umubare w'abapfa bazize indwara (IFR) ugaragaza umubare w'abantu bapfuye bazize indwara runaka (abamaze no batarabipimwa).
Iyi mibare ntabwo ishingiye ku gihe kandi ikurikira abantu runaka kuva banduye kugeza igihe bagaruye.
Nubwo abantu bose banduye batagira ubudahangarwa, kuba hari ubwirinda bishobora gutanga amakuru y'abantu benshi banduye.
Mu mujyi muto wa Castellione d'Aida, mu Butaliyani, ahari ihuriro ry'icyorezo, mu mudugudu muto w'abaturage 4600, 80 (1.7%) bamaze gupfa.
Muri Gangelt, iyi ndwara yakwirakwijwe n'ibirori bya Karneval no mu rubyiruko, bituma umubare w'abahitanwa na yo ugabanuka, kandi impfu zose za COVID-19 zishobora kuba zitari zarashyizwe mu byiciro.
Byongeye kandi, ubuvuzi bwo mu Budage si bwo buteye imbere.
Mu Buholandi, nk'uko byagaragajwe n'abatanga amaraso, abantu bagera kuri 3% bashobora kuba barwanyijwe.
Imibereho y'abantu 69 (0.004% by'abaturage) bapfuye bishwe na COVID-19.
Ingaruka z'icyorezo n'iz'urupfu zigira ku bagabo n'abagore, ziratandukanye.
Mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu Bushinwa no mu Butaliyani, abagabo ni bo bafite impfu nyinshi.
Abagabo bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara iyo barengeje imyaka 50, kandi itandukaniro riri hagati y'abagabo n'abagore rigabanuka gusa iyo bageze ku myaka 90.
Mu Bushinwa, umubare w'abapfa wari 2.8% ku bagabo na 1.7% ku bagore.
Impamvu nyayo zituma habaho itandukaniro ry'ibitsina ntizizwi neza, ariko ibiterwa n'imiterere y'umubiri n'imyitwarire bishobora kuba ari byo bitera iryo tandukaniro.
Amakimbirane mu mikurire y'umubiri, kudakoresha itabi cyane mu bagore no kuba abagabo bafite ibibazo by'uburwayi nk'umuvuduko w'amaraso uri hasi ugereranyije n'abagore, bishobora gutuma abagabo bapfa cyane.
Mu Burayi, 57% by'abanduye ni abagabo naho 72% by'abahitanywe na COVID-19.
Kugeza muri Mata 2020, leta ya Amerika ntiri gukurikirana imibare ihuje igitsina ku banduye COVID-19.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko indwara z'ibyorezo nka Ebola, HIV, ibicurane na SARS zigira ingaruka zitandukanye ku bagabo no ku bagore.
Umubare munini w'abakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima, cyane cyane abaforomokazi, ni abagore, kandi bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura iyi virusi.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, OMS yatangaje ko izina ry'iyi ndwara rizaba "COVID-19".
Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, umuyobozi wa OMS, yavuze ko CO isobanura Corona, VI isobanura virusi, D isobanura indwara, naho 19 isobanura umwaka icyorezo cyatangiye kumenyekaniraho, ni ukuvuga tariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019.
Iri zina ryatoranyijwe kugira ngo hirindwa ko habaho ahantu runaka (nk'u Bushinwa), ubwoko bw'ibinyabuzima cyangwa itsinda ry'abantu, ibyo bikaba bihuje n'amabwiriza mpuzamahanga agenga amazina agamije gukumira ko abantu bakomereka.
OMS ikoresha kandi amagambo "COVID-19 virus" na "virus iteza COVID-19" mu itumanaho rusange.
Bombi, indwara na virusi, bakunze kubyita "Coronavirus".
Mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya mbere cyibasiye umujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, virusi n'indwara byiswe "Coronavirus" na "Wuhan coronavirus".
Muri Mutarama 2020, OMS yatanze amazina y'igihe gito ya virusi n'indwara by'indwara z'ubuhumekero za 2019-nCov na 2019-nCoV, ibyo bikaba byubahirije amabwiriza yo mu 2015 yo kudakoresha imyanya mu mazina y'indwara n'indwara.
Izina rya COVID-19 na SARS-CoV-2 ryatanzwe ku mugaragaro ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020.
Kubera ubushobozi buke mu byiciro by'ibicuruzwa, bamwe mu bahanga bakoresha ikoranabuhanga barimo gucapa ibikoresho by'isuku, urugero nk'imashini zikoresha umuyoboro w'umura n'ibice by'ibikoresho by'ubutabazi.
Urugero, igihe ibitaro byo mu Butaliyani byari bikeneye indangamirwa mu guhumeka, kandi abatanga ibikoresho ntibashoboye kuzibaha mu gihe cyihariye, isosiyete itangira gukora ibintu byo mu karere kacu yakoze uburyo bwo guhinduranya indangamirwa 100 mu ijoro rimwe.
Nyuma y'icyorezo cya COVID-19, habayeho guhimba ibitekerezo, ikinyoma n'amakuru y'ibinyoma ku nkomoko, ubukana, kwirinda, kuvura n'ibindi byerekeranye n'iyi ndwara.
Abantu basa n'aho bafite ubushobozi bwo kwanduza izindi nyamaswa virusi.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko nta bimenyetso by'uko virusi ishobora kwanduza ingurube, amadubu n'inkoko.
Nta miti cyangwa imiti byemewe yo kuvura iyi ndwara.
Ubushakashatsi mpuzamahanga ku nkingo n'imiti ya COVID-19 burimo gukorwa n'imiryango ya leta, amatsinda y'abanyeshuri n'abashakashatsi bo mu nganda.
Muri Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangije "Igeragezwa ry'Ubumwe" rigamije gusuzuma ingaruka zo kuvura imiti ine ya virusi ifite icyizere cyo gukora neza.
Kugeza ubu nta rukingo ruraboneka, ariko inzego zitandukanye zirimo gukora inkingo z'ubwandu.
Imirimo yari yarakozwe mbere kuri SARS-CoV irimo gukoreshwa kubera ko SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 byombi bikoresha ACE2 receptors kugira ngo byinjire mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'abantu.
Hari uburyo butatu bwo gukingira abantu burimo kugeragezwa.
Icya mbere, abashakashatsi bafite intego yo gukora urukingo rwuzuye.
Gukoresha virusi nk'iyi, yaba idakora cyangwa ipfuye, bigamije gutuma umubiri w'umuntu utangira guhangana n'ubwandu bushya bwa COVID-19.
Ubundi buryo, ari bwo bwo rukingo rwa subunit, bugamije gukora urukingo rwica udukingirizo tw'umubiri ku bice by'ingenzi bigize virusi.
Ku byerekeye SARS-CoV-2, ubu bushakashatsi bwibanze kuri poroteyine ya S-contact ifasha virusi kwinjira mu gikoresho cy'indwara ya ACE2.
Uburyo bwa gatatu ni ukoresha inkingo za nucleic acid (nk'inkingo za ADN cyangwa za RNA, ubwo bukaba ari uburyo bushya bwo gukingira).
Inzoga z'ubushakashatsi muri ubwo buryo bwose zigomba kubanza kugeragezwa kugira ngo zibone ubuziranenge n'ubuziranenge. Ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020, isuzuma ry'ubu bushakashatsi rya mbere ry'urukingo rwatangiye muri Seattle, rwarimo abantu bane.
Urukingo rufite kode y'igicamare idafite akaga, yiganjemo virusi itera indwara. Kwongera kwishingikiriza ku myanya y'umubiri byavuzwe ko ari ikibazo gishobora kubaho mu ikorwa ry'urukingo rwa SARS-COV-2, ariko ni ikibazo cy'impaka.
Kugeza muri Mata 2020, ibizamini byo kwa muganga birenga 300 byatangiye gukorwa.
Ibikorwa birindwi byasuzumaga uburyo bwo kuvura malaria bwamaze kwemerwa, harimo bine byakozwe kuri hydroxychloroquine cyangwa chloroquine.
Mu bihugu byinshi, ibyinshi mu bushakashatsi bwo mu Bushinwa burimo gukorwa ku miti ya virusi itera indwara ishobora gusubirwamo, aho hari amagerageza y'icyiciro cya gatatu (Phase III) icyenda ku miti ya Remdesivir, biteganyijwe ko azatangwa mu mpera za Mata.
Kugeza muri Mata 2020, hari isuzuma ry'ibikorwa rishinzwe iterambere ry'imiti n'imiti ishobora gukingira COVID-19. Imiti myinshi ya anti-virusi irimo gusuzumwa mu kuvura COVID-19, harimo Remdesivir, Chloroquine na Hydroxychloroquine, Lopinavir/Ritonavir ifatanyije na Interferon beta na Lopinavir/Ritonavir ifatanyije na Interferon beta.
Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, hari ibimenyetso by'ubushakashatsi ku mikorere ya Remdesivir.
Abarwayi bavurwaga bakoresheje imiti itemewe ya Remdesivir, bagaragaje ko iyi miti yabafashije.
Icyiciro cya III cy'igeragezwa ry'ubuvuzi kiri gukorwa muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, mu Bushinwa no mu Butaliyani. Cloroquine, ubu ikoreshwa mu kuvura malaria, yatangiye kwigwaho mu Bushinwa mu kwezi kwa kabiri mu 2020, ariko ku ikubitiro nta gihamya igaragara.
Icyakora, hari abagiye basaba ko hakorwa ubushakashatsi ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe n'abandi.
Abayobozi b'ubuzima muri Koreya y'Amajyepfo n'u Bushinwa, batanga inama yo gukoresha umuti witwa chloroquine.
Ariko kandi, ikigo cyo muri Wuhan gishinzwe iby'indwara z'imitsi yo mu mubiri, cyatanze inama yo gukoresha ikigero cy'igarama imwe ku munsi, kivuga ko incuro ebyiri z'icyo kigero ari zo ziteje akaga gakomeye kandi ko zishobora kwica.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe 2020, FDA yatanze uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihutirwa kuri hydroxychloroquine na chloroquine ku bushake bw'abaganga bavura abantu bafite COVID-19. Amabwiriza y'Ubushinwa yo mu cyiciro cya 7 harimo kandi interferon, ribavirin cyangwa umifenovir ikoreshwa mu kurinda COVID-19.
Imibare ya mbere igaragaza ko ibipimo biri hejuru bya ribavirin bikenewe mu guhashya SARS-CoV-2 mu buryo bw'imikorere.
Nitasoxanide yakiriweho gukorerwa ubundi bushakashatsi mu binyabuzima nyuma yo kugaragaza ko ifite ubushobozi bwo guhashya SARS-CoV-2. Ubushakashatsi bwerekanye ko gutangiza poroteyine ya konti ya mbere ikoreshwa na transmembrane protease serine 2 (TMPRSS2) ari ngombwa kugira ngo SARS-CoV-2 yinjire mu mubiri binyuze mu gukorana n'umurwayi ACE2.
Ubushakashatsi ku miti ya chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine, yaba iriho cyangwa itariho azithromycin, bugira ibibazo bikomeye, byatumye abaganga bareka gukoresha iyi miti nta bushakashatsi bw'inyongera. Oseltamivir ntishobora guhashya SARS-CoV-2 kandi nta ruhare ruzwi ifite mu kuvura COVID-19.
Kwiyongera k'umurengera wa cytokine bishobora kuba ikibazo gikomeye mu bihe bya nyuma bya COVID-19.
Hari ibimenyetso byerekana ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora kuba ifite ubushobozi bwo gukumira ko cytocaine itera kwiyongera. Tokilizumab yashyizwe mu mabwiriza y'ubuvuzi na Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Igihugu y'u Bushinwa nyuma yo gusoza inyigo nto.
Iri koranabuhanga riri mu igeragezwa rya kabiri ritagendanye n'igihe mu Butaliyani, nyuma yo kugaragara ko rifite ingaruka nziza ku bantu bafite uburwayi bukomeye.
Iyo ikoreshejwe yifashishije ibipimo bya serum ferritin by'amaraso kugira ngo hamenyekane ko hari ibipimo bya cytokine byazamutse, ibi bigamije guhangana n'ibimenyetso by'ubwiyongere bw'amaraso, bizwiho kuba ari byo bitera urupfu kuri bamwe mu bantu bayanduye.
Interleukin-6 anti-reagis anti yakiriwe na FDA mu 2017, hashingiwe ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe mbere ku kuvura indwara yo kutakira sitokine ituma udakoresha imiti, iterwa n'imiti ikoreshwa mu kuvura indwara ituma udasohora mu mubiri (steroid refractory cytokine deprivation syndrome) iturutse ku kuba hari indi mpamvu, CAR T cell therapy.
Kugeza ubu, nta bihamya bifatika, by'urusobe, byerekana ko tocilizumab ari umuti uvura neza indwara ya CRS.
Kwanduza abantu bakira COVID-19 bakoresheje ubwirinzi bw'umubiri, maze bakagenda babwanduza abantu babukeneye, ni uburyo bugenda bugenzurwa mu buryo butari ubw'ikingira.
Ubwo buryo bwakoreshejwe kuri SARS ariko nta musaruro wabaye.
Gukomeza kwanduza virusi ni uburyo bushoboka bwo gukingira SARS-CoV-2.
Icyakora, izindi nzira, urugero nk'imikorere y'amaraso mu mubiri, ishobora gutuma habaho cytotoxicity na/cyangwa phagocytosis.
Ubundi buryo bwo kuvura hakoreshejwe abasirikare b'umubiri, urugero nko gukoresha ubwirinzi bw'umubiri bwitwa monoclonal, burimo burashyirwaho.
Ubusanzwe, serium z'ingirakamaro zirimo igice cy'amaraso y'abarwayi bakize kandi bafite ubwirinzi bwihariye kuri iyi virusi, zishobora gutangwa mu buryo bwihuse.
